In addition, it is involved in the import of construction and building materials; and exploration and development of nickel mines. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. CITIC Resources Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of CITIC Group Corporation.

Technovator International Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides smart energy management products, solutions, and integrated services primarily in the People's Republic of China. The company's Smart Transportation segment offers a series of proprietary software and hardware products, and integrated supervision and control system for rail transit; and building automation systems for use in rail transit and safety door systems, as well as provides integrated solutions comprising planning, procurement, installation, commissioning, and aftersales services. Its Smart Building and Complex segment provides integrated intelligence solutions and efficiency management services, including integrated energy consumption monitoring, energy-saving consultation, and reformation services, as well as full life-cycle services; and supplies and integrates intelligence systems for buildings. The company's Smart Energy segment offers regional energy planning, integrated utilization of industrial waste heat recovery, heat pump, independent temperature and humidity control, and variable air rate technologies for energy cascade utilization, as well as optimization and transformation of energy systems. This segment also provides urban heating network technologies, including distributed variable frequency heating, cooling and heating network balancing, and combined multi-heat sources heating, as well as heating network and source monitoring, and optimal regulation technologies. The company also offers digital video urban surveillance systems for multi-level remote surveillance in the finance, electricity, security, and road traffic industries; and fire alarm systems, which offers online fire control solutions for city authorities and commercial users. The company was formerly known as Technovator Int Private Ltd. and changed its name to Technovator International Limited in September 2011. Technovator International Limited was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Singapore.

SRE Group Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the real estate development and investment activities primarily in Mainland China. The company's Property Development segment develops and sells residential and commercial properties. Its Property Leasing segment leases offices and commercial properties. SRE Group Limited is also involved in hospital operations; and the provision of real estate agency, factoring, property management, and construction and procurement management services, as well as the development of technology for housing. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Admiralty, Hong Kong.

MMG Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the exploration, development, and mining of copper, zinc, gold, silver, nickel, and lead deposits worldwide. It operates through Las Bambas, Kinsevere, Dugald River, Rosebery, and Other segments. The company operates the Las Bambas open-pit copper and molybdenum mine located in Cotabambas, Apurimac region of Peru; and the Kinsevere open-pit copper mine in the Katanga province of the Democratic Republic of the Congo. It also operates the Dugald River underground zinc mine located near Cloncurry in North West Queensland; and the Rosebery underground polymetallic base metal mine located on Tasmania's west coast. The company was formerly known as Minmetals Resources Limited and changed its name to MMG Limited in September 2012. MMG Limited was incorporated in 1988 and is headquartered in Southbank, Australia.

Christine International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates a chain of bakeries in the People's Republic of China. It produces and sells bakery products, including breads and cakes, moon cakes, pastries, and other products. The company operates a multi-channel retail network that comprises neighbor stores, subway stores, flagship stores, and European style fresh-bake stores. It operates approximately 586 stores. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.

Lifestyle International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates mid to upper-end department stores and other retailing formats in Hong Kong. The company operates its stores under the SOGO brand. It owns and operates two SOGO department stores that offer daily necessities to luxury products, as well as personal care services, such as beauty salons in Hong Kong. The company is also involved in property development, investment, holding, and leasing; and financial investment, advertising, and financing activities. In addition, it provides property security and management services; and operates restaurant and club. The company was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong.

Mobicon Group Limited, an investment holding company, trades in and distributes electronic components, automation parts, and equipment in Hong Kong and other Asia-Pacific countries, South Africa, Europe, and internationally. The company operates through Electronic Trading Business, Computer Business, and Cosmetic and Online Retail Business segments. It is also involved in the trading and distribution, and retail of computer products and mobile accessories; and provision of information technology outsourcing and solution services. In addition, the company engages in the retail sale of cosmetic products. Mobicon Group Limited was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in San Po Kong, Hong Kong.
Kai Yuan Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, owns and operates hotels in Hong Kong and France. It is also involved in money lending business. The company is based in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

Zhongyuan Bank Co., Ltd. provides corporate and personal deposits, loans and advances, settlement, financial market, and other banking services in Henan province, China. It operates through Corporate Banking, Retail Banking, Financial Markets Business, and Others segments. The company's Corporate Banking segment provides corporate loans and advances, trade financing and deposit taking, agency, consulting and advisory, remittance and settlement, and guarantee services to corporations, government agencies, and financial institutions. Its Retail Banking segment offers a range of financial products and services, including personal loans, deposits, bank cards, personal wealth management services, and remittance services to retail customers. Its Financial Markets Business segment offers inter-bank money market transactions, repurchase transactions, investments, trading in debt securities, and issuance of debts services. As of December 31, 2018, the company operated 18 branches, 2 direct sub-branches, and 457 total outlets, including 301 county-level branches and 156 township-level sub-branches. Zhongyuan Bank Co., Ltd. was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Zhengzhou, China.

China Innovation Investment Limited invests in equity-related securities and debt instruments in listed and unlisted companies in Hong Kong and the People's Republic of China. It also engages in transactions comprising options and futures that are traded on recognized securities or futures exchanges and for the purpose of hedging. The company invests in information technology, telecommunications, manufacturing, service, property, infrastructure, life science, and environmental sectors. China Innovation Investment Limited, formerly nown as Sino Technology Investments Company Limited, was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.
address1: No. 9 Des Voeux Road West Road

longBusinessSummary: Easyknit International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the investment, development, and management of properties in Hong Kong. The company operates through Property Investment, Property Development, Investment in Securities, and Loan Financing segments. Its investment properties primarily include residential, commercial, industrial, and retail properties. The company is also involved in securities investment and loan financing businesses. Easyknit International Holdings Limited was founded in 1981 and is based in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong.

Zhidao International (Holdings) Limited, an investment holding company, provides construction and engineering services in Hong Kong and Macau. It also trades in aluminum products, as well as supplies aluminum products for construction projects; provides money lending service; and manufactures and trades in aluminum windows and gates, as well as provides development, engineering, and construction services for a mining project. The company was formerly known as Ocean Grand Holdings Limited and changed its name to Zhidao International (Holdings) Limited in June 2012. Zhidao International (Holdings) Limited was incorporated in 1997 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

Sino Hotels (Holdings) Limited, an investment holding company, operates and manages hotels in Hong Kong. It operates hotels under the Royal Pacific Hotel, Island Pacific Hotel Hong Kong, City Garden Hotel Hong Kong, The Olympian Hong Kong, Hong Kong Gold Coast Hotel, and The Pottinger Hong Kong names in Hong Kong; and The Fullerton Hotel and The Fullerton Bay Hotel names in Singapore. The company also operates clubs under the Gold Coast Yacht & Country Club name; restaurants and bars under the Pierside Bar & Restaurant, Satay Inn, and Yuè names; and cafes and delis under the Café on the PARK name. In addition, it engages in the provision of catering and nominee services; and share investment activities. The company is based in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.

Wang On Group Limited, together with its subsidiaries, primarily engages in the property development and investment activities in Hong Kong, Mainland China, Macau, and internationally. It operates through five segments: Property Development, Property Investment, Fresh Markets, Pharmaceutical, and Treasury Management. The company develops properties; and invests in car parking spaces, industrial and commercial premises, and residential units for rental or for sale. It is also involved in the management and sub-licensing of fresh markets; production and sale of Chinese and Western pharmaceutical and health food products; and provision of finance and investments in debt and other securities. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong.

Symphony Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily operates as a retailing company. The company is involved in the retailing and provision of sourcing services for branded apparel, swimwear, and accessories; and development and management of PONY trademarks. It also operates outlet malls, duty free shops, and fashion stores; provides financial services, including securities brokerage, margin financing, underwriting and placing, financial consulting, and money lending services; and invests in and holds properties. In addition, the company offers IT, corporate, and portfolio management services; accountancy, legal, secretarial, and cruiser services; and online trading platform support services. Further, it engages in the trading, retailing, and distribution of swimming apparel and accessories; sub-licensing of trademark rights; trading and wholesaling of sportswear; and manufacturing and trading of health supplement products. Symphony Holdings Limited operates in the People's Republic of China, other Asian countries, the United States, and internationally. The company was formerly known as Liang Shing (Holdings) Limited and changed its name to Symphony Holdings Limited in 1997. Symphony Holdings Limited was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in North Point, Hong Kong.

C C Land Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, invests in and develops properties in the United Kingdom, Australia, Hong Kong, and Mainland China. The company operates through two segments, Property Development and Investment; and Treasury Investment. It also invests in securities and notes receivable; and provides financial services. The company was formerly known as Qualipak International Holdings Limited and changed its name to C C Land Holdings Limited in January 2007. C C Land Holdings Limited was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

China Investment and Finance Group Limited is an equity fund launched and managed by China Everbright Securities (HK) Limited. The fund invests in the equity markets of Greater China. China Investment and Finance Group Limited was formed on April 26, 2002 and is domiciled in Cayman Islands.
longName: China Investment and Finance Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: National Investments Fund Limited is an equity mutual fund launched and managed by Enerchine Investment Management Limited. It invests in equity markets. The fund seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in a diversified portfolio of listed and unlisted companies. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Hang Seng Index. National Investments Fund Limited was formed on June 28, 2002 and is domiciled in the Cayman Islands.

Nan Nan Resources Enterprise Limited, an investment holding company, mines, sells, and distributes coal in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Coal Mining Business and Renewable Energy Business segments. It owns mining right in the Kaiyuan Open Pit Coal Mine and an exploration right in the Zexu Open Pit Coal Mine in Xinjiang. The company also provides renewable energy solutions and solar farm development services in Malaysia. In addition, it provides information technology outsourcing, consultancy, and technical services in Hong Kong. The company was formerly known as International Resources Enterprise Limited and changed its name to Nan Nan Resources Enterprise Limited in September 2011. Nan Nan Resources Enterprise Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Admiralty, Hong Kong. Nan Nan Resources Enterprise Limited is a subsidiary of Ascent Goal Investments Limited.

Yashili International Holdings Ltd, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells dairy and nourishment products in the People's Republic of China and internationally. It operates through three segments: Production and Sale of Milk Powder Products; Production and Sale of Dissolvable Products; and Other Operations. The company provides infant milk formula products under the Yashily, Dumex, Reeborne, Doraler, and Arla Baby & Me brand names. It also offers adult milk powder products under the Mengniu and Youyi brand names; milk formula for the middle-aged and elderly under the Yourui brand name; and milk powder for kids growth under the Future Star brand name. In addition, the company provides various dissolvable products, such as nutritional rice cereal, soymilk powder, and paediatric rice flour under the Yashily brand name; and oatmeal under the Zhengwei brand name. Further, it is involved in the wholesale and retail of dairy products. The company was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in Chaozhou, the People's Republic of China. Yashili International Holdings Ltd is a subsidiary of China Mengniu International Company Limited.

Newton Resources Ltd, an investment holding company, mines, processes, and sells iron concentrates in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through three segments: Iron Concentrate Business, Gabbro-Diabase and Stone Business, and Trading Business. It also supplies and trades in iron ores, coals, and other commodities. In addition, the company mines, processes, and sells railway ballast, highway crushed stone, and gabbro-diabase products. The company is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Golden Wheel Tiandi Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, owns, develops, and operates integrated commercial and residential properties in Mainland China and Hong Kong. The company operates in three segments: Property Development, Property Leasing, and Hotel Operation. It develops and sells properties; and offers property leasing services, including the lease of self-owned properties and sub-lease of rented properties, as well as hotel services. The company also develops and operates shopping malls and integrated commercial projects in Jiangsu and Hunan provinces; and provides property management and decoration services. As of December 31, 2018, the company had a land bank of approximately 1,682,319 square meters. Golden Wheel Tiandi Holdings Company Limited was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Nanjing, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Golden Wheel Tiandi Holdings Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Times China Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the property development business in the People's Republic of China. The company's Property Development segment is involved in the development and sale of residential and commercial properties. Its Urban Redevelopment Business segment engages in sale of land held for development and other related activities. The company's Property Leasing segment offers development, leasing, and sub-leasing of commercial properties owned by the company or independent third parties. Its Property Management segment provides property management services. Times China Holdings Limited is also involved in the garden landscape design and architecture, property decoration, and elevator installation and maintenance activities; provision of information technology and money lending services, as well as manufacturing of metals and plastics; and production and sale of fodder. The company was formerly known as Times Property (Holdings) Co., Limited and changed its name to Times China Holdings Limited in February 2018. Times China Holdings Limited was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, the People's Republic of China.

China Lilang Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the manufacture and wholesale of branded menswear and related accessories in the People's Republic of China. The company designs, sources, manufactures, and sells business and casual apparel for men under the LILANZ brand name across a distribution network covering 31 provinces, autonomous regions, and municipalities. It also provides management services. As of December 31, 2018, it had a total of 2,670 retail stores operated through distributors and sub-distributors. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Jinjiang, the People's Republic of China. China Lilang Limited is a subsidiary of Xiao Sheng International Limited.

Travel Expert (Asia) Enterprises Limited, an investment holding company, provides travel agency services in Hong Kong and the People's Republic of China. It operates through Travel and Travel/Wedding Related Business, Rental Income from Investment Properties, and Treasury Activities segments. The company engages in the provision of services relating to the sale of air tickets, hotel accommodation, and other travel/wedding related products and services; and package tours, property investment, and investment in treasury activities. It also provides meeting, incentive, conference, and exhibition trips planning and management services. In addition, the company engages in the travel and travel related, study tours, and property holding and marketing businesses, as well as provision of management services. As of March 31, 2019, it operated a total of 37 retail shops in Hong Kong under the Travel Expert and Premium Holidays brands. The company was founded in 1986 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. Travel Expert (Asia) Enterprises Limited is a subsidiary of Colvin & Horne Holdings Limited.

China Environmental Technology and Bioenergy Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells outdoor wooden products in the People's Republic of China, North America, Europe, other Asia Pacific, and Australasia. The company operates through three segments: Manufacturing and Sales of Wooden Products; Retail Business; and Manufacturing and Sales of Renewable Energy Products. It produces and sells timber houses, and related parts and structures. The company offers timber villas for leisure resort clubs, tourist scenic spots, and parks; non-residential timber sheds for leisure or storage purposes, including pavilions and gazebos, etc.; and timber logs. It also provides recreational products, such as play swings, sand tables, and outdoor rocking chairs for children; outdoor furniture products comprising tables and chairs; indoor furniture products that include beds and cabinets; landscape garden products, such as flower carts, railings, and litter bins for use in gardens, scenic spots, courtyards, and parks; and pet-home products consisting of bird houses, dog homes and playhouses, rabbit hutches, hamster cages, etc. In addition, the company trades in timber; recycles and produces renewable energy products, such as biomass pellet fuels; and undertakes projects for providing design and installation services for outdoor wooden products. Further, it is involved in the retail sale of outdoor wooden products through self-operated retail shops; and manufacture and sale of electronics products. The company was formerly known as Merry Garden Holdings Limited and changed its name to China Environmental Technology and Bioenergy Holdings Limited in July 2016. China Environmental Technology and Bioenergy Holdings Limited was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Zhangping, China.
longName: China Environmental Technology and Bioenergy Holdings Limited

longBusinessSummary: Powerlong Real Estate Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, invests in, develops, and manages properties in the People's Republic of China. It develops large-scale commercial and residential properties. The company also operates hotels; and provides construction and decoration services. As of December 31, 2018, it had a land bank with a total gross floor area of 21.2 million square meters; and developed, owned, and operated 114 real estate projects. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.

Teamway International Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, manufactures, and sells packaging products and structural components in the People's Republic of China. The company offers expanded polystyrene and expanded polyolefin packaging products for packaging consumer electrical appliances, such as televisions, air conditioners, washing machines, and refrigerators. It is also involved in the property investment and money lending businesses. In addition, the company provides corporate secretarial, consultancy, and business valuation services, which include accounting and internal control matters consultancy, corporate secretarial, business valuation, loan facilitation, strategic planning, and ad-hoc strategic consultancy, as well as property, transaction, and project agency services. It serves the consumer electrical appliance manufacturers. The company was formerly known as Jin Bao Bao Holdings Limited and changed its name to Teamway International Group Holdings Limited in September 2017. Teamway International Group Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.

CNQC International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a property developer and contractor in Singapore. The company primarily engages in the development and sale of executive condominiums and condominiums in the Outside Central Region of Singapore; and the provision of construction services as main contractor for governmental authorities and private property developers. It also undertakes foundation works; and provides ancillary services with specialization in piling works, as well as superstructure construction services in Hong Kong and Macau. In addition, the company undertakes construction projects in Malaysia, Indonesia, and Vietnam. Further, it is involved in the rental of machinery and construction equipment; general wholesale trade business; provision of information technology services; trading and letting of tools and equipment; lease of workers dormitory; and provision of general contracting, and building and civil engineering services. The company is based in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong. CNQC International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Guotsing Holding Group Co. Ltd.

Shuanghua Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and sells auto air-conditioner parts and components in the People's Republic of China, other Asian countries, the United States, Canada, and internationally. It also manufactures and sells heaters, intercoolers, liquid-gas separators, evaporators, condenser cores, pipes, and thermostats. In addition, the company is involved in the sale of automotive lubricants; the wholesale and retail of mechanical and electrical equipment; and the import and export of goods and technology. It offers its products under the Shuanghua and Youshen brand names to domestic OEM and international aftermarket customers. The company was formerly known as Shanghai Shuanghua Autoparts Co., Ltd. Shuanghua Holdings Limited was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.

Wang On Properties Limited, an investment holding company, invests in, develops, and sells residential and commercial properties in Hong Kong. It operates through two segments, Property Development and Property Investment. The company engages in the acquisition of land to develop property, as well as the acquisition of existing buildings to be demolished and rebuilt into new property; and acquires of ready-made property for long-term investments. It also engages in the investment of car parking spaces; rental or sale of industrial and commercial premises; and provision of management and financial services. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong. Wang On Properties Limited is a subsidiary of Earnest Spot Limited.

Niraku GC Holdings, Inc., an investment holding company, operates pachinko and pachislot halls in Japan. It also operates the Koriyama City Hotel, a business hotel with approximately 84 guest rooms; a Spanish restaurant franchise under the LIZARRAN brand; and 55 pachinko halls. In addition, the company engages in the property investment and cleaning service businesses. Further, it operates entertainment and amusement facilities; and wholesales computer games, and sporting and other recreational goods. The company was formerly known as Niraku Global Community Holdings Inc. and changed its name to Niraku GC Holdings, Inc. Niraku GC Holdings, Inc. was founded in 1950 and is headquartered in Koriyama, Japan.

Boill Healthcare Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, undertakes contracts for foundation piling in Hong Kong and Mainland China. It operates through four segments: Foundation Piling, Property Development, Investment Securities, and Healthcare Holiday Resort Development and Operation. The company develops and sells properties, as well as provides property management services. In addition, it trades and invests in securities; and provides elderly home care, healthcare, and leisure services. The company was formerly known as Ngai Shun Holdings Limited and changed its name to Boill Healthcare Holdings Limited in September 2017. Boill Healthcare Holdings Limited was founded in 1983 and is based in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.

Miko International Holdings Limited engages in the design, manufacture, and sale of children's and infant apparel, footwear, and accessories in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company sells its products through distributors; and self-operated stores under the redkids brand. As of December 31, 2018, it had 209 redkids branded retail stores operated by its distributors; and 74 self-operated stores. Miko International Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Quanzhou, the People's Republic of China. Miko International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Think Wise Holdings Investment Limited.

Tonly Electronics Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, researches and develops, manufactures, and sells audio-visual products and related components. The company offers audio products, including smart voice speakers, wireless speakers, soundbars, home theatres, and mini speakers; video products, such as DVD and BD players, OTT set top boxes, and other products; and IoT related products comprising smart plugs, smart gateways, and other IoT products; and ancillary products, such as plastic injection structural parts, speakers, wireless modules, and other components. It is also involved in the development of software; and trading of audio-visual products and components. It operates in the United States, Japan, Europe, the People's Republic of China, South Korea, and internationally. Tonly Electronics Holdings Limited was founded in 2000 and is based in Sha Tin, Hong Kong. Tonly Electronics Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of T.C.L. Industries Holdings (H.K.) Limited.

Beijing Enterprises Clean Energy Group Limited engages in the investment, development, construction, operation, and management of photovoltaic power plants in Mainland China. The company develops and constructs distributed photovoltaic power stations; and provides engineering, procurement, construction, and technical consultancy services for photovoltaic and wind power-related projects, and clean heat supply projects, as well as trades in equipment related to photovoltaic power business. It also engages in the infrastructure development and operation of wind power plants and clean energy projects, as well as in the property investment business. The company was formerly known as Jin Cai Holdings Company Limited and changed its name to Beijing Enterprises Clean Energy Group Limited in June 2015. Beijing Enterprises Clean Energy Group Limited was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong.
longName: Beijing Enterprises Clean Energy Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: SPT Energy Group Inc., an investment holding company, provides integrated oilfield services in the People's Republic of China, Kazakhstan, the Middle East, Turkmenistan, Canada, Indonesia, and internationally. It operates through three segments: Drilling, Well Completion, and Reservoir. The Drilling segment offers drilling rig, work over rig, work over and fishing, and geological steering services, as well as vertical drilling, horizontal drilling, side tracking, underbalanced drilling, fine managed pressure drilling technology, and cementing services. The Well Completion segment manufactures and trades in well completion tools; and provides well completion project design, and stimulation and fracturing services. The Reservoir segment offers geology research and oil reservoir research, dynamic monitoring, oil testing and recovery, oil and gas operations maintenance, and oil extraction process services, as well as coiled tubing service and repair service of surface production devices. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

China Tianrui Group Cement Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the excavation of limestone; and production, distribution, and sale of clinker and cement in the People's Republic of China. The company offers clinker to produce various cement products; and cement products that are used in real estate construction, as well as a range of infrastructure projects, including highways, railways, tunnels, bridges, and high-rise buildings. It also provides packing bags, concrete, construction materials, and slag powder. In addition, the company exports its products. The company sells its cement products under TIANRUI brand. It serves real estate developers, concrete manufacturers, etc. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Ruzhou, the People's Republic of China. China Tianrui Group Cement Company Limited is a subsidiary of Yu Kuo Company Limited.
longName: China Tianrui Group Cement Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: China Greenland Broad Greenstate Group Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides landscape and project management services in the People's Republic of China. The company offers design and planning, design refinement, construction, seedlings cultivation, and maintenance services. The company undertakes municipal and city level landscape projects. It also offers plant cultivation, soil improvement, and water ecological treatment services; and gardening and related services. China Greenland Broad Greenstate Group Company Limited primarily serves local governments and state-owned enterprises. The company was formerly known as Broad Greenstate International Company Limited and changed its name to China Greenland Broad Greenstate Group Company Limited in November 2016. China Greenland Broad Greenstate Group Company Limited was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.
longName: China Greenland Broad Greenstate Group Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: S. Culture International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the trading of footwear and healthcare products, and provision of financial services in Hong Kong, Macau, Taiwan, Mainland China, and Australia. The company operates through Trading of Footwear Products, Trading of Healthcare Products, and Financial Services segments. It is involved in the wholesale and retail of footwear products; and property holding activities. The company offers products of various brands comprising Clarks & Clarks Original, Josef Seibel, The Flexx, Petite Jolie, and other brands. As of December 31, 2018, it operated 47 retail outlets in Hong Kong and 2 retail outlets in Macau under the Clarks, Clarks Originals, Josef Seibel, Scoops, S.Culture, and shoe mart names. In addition, the company provides securities advisory services, investment management services, and corporate finance advisory services. S. Culture International Holdings Limited was founded in 1974 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong.

China Everbright Greentech Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the design, construction, operation, and maintenance of integrated biomass and waste-to-energy projects in China. It generates electricity and heat through biomass raw materials. The company operates environmental remediation for restoration of industrial contaminated sites, contaminated farmland, mines and landfills; treatment of industrial gas emission, integrated oil sludge, river/lake sediments, and industrial sludge; and construction and operation of wetland parks, environmental stewardship services and anti-seepage at landfill sites. It also operates seven solar energy projects and two wind power projects in Jiangsu Province, Anhui Province, Shanxi Province, and Germany generation capacity of 125.9 MW to local power grid companies. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong. China Everbright Greentech Limited is a subsidiary of China Everbright International Limited.

China Nonferrous Mining Corporation Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the exploration, mining, ore processing, leaching, smelting, and sale of copper cathodes, blister copper, copper anodes, and sulfuric acid. It offers copper concentrate for use as raw materials for copper smelter; blister copper for use as raw materials for electrolytic copper plant; copper cathode for use in the production of wires and cables, electrical and electronic products, industrial machinery and equipment, etc.; and sulfuric acid for producing chemical fertilizers. The company also engages in the farming activities. It has operations in Mainland China, Hong Kong, Switzerland, Singapore, Africa, and Luxemburg. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Beijing, China. China Nonferrous Mining Corporation Limited is a subsidiary of China Nonferrous Mining Development Limited.

Future Development Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells personal care products. The company operates in Personal Care Products, Money Lending, Operation of Online Platform, Trading of Commodities, and Securities Investment segments. The company provides skin care, body and hair care, oral care, diaper, and tissue products under the Frog Prince brand name, as well as manufactures OEM products; and offers advertising services. It also engages in the provision of unsecured and secured loans to customers, as well as marketing, marketing consulting, and promotional services; e-commerce business; and retail of children, babies, and parents products. The company was formerly known as China Child Care Corporation Limited and changed its name to Future Development Holdings Limited in June 2014. Future Development Holdings Limited is headquartered in Zhangzhou, the People's Republic of China.

Wonderful Sky Financial Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides financial public relations and international roadshow services in Hong Kong and internationally. It offers corporate positioning, media relations management, listing events and celebration functions management, press release and speech writing, IPO advertising plan, design and production of corporate marketing material, crisis management, maintenance and development of public relation, and events coordination services. The company also provides global investor summit and forum, one-on-one meeting, investor relation conference, research report monitoring, proxy, shareholder identification, investors targeting, and investor polling services. In addition, it offers international roadshow services consisting of overall project management, logistics arrangement, and roadshow desk supporting function. Further, the company offers financial printing services, such as IPO prospectus, financial reports, prospectus cover design, translation, copywriting and editing, typesetting services, announcements, corporate brochures and marketing collaterals, and compliance documentations. Additionally, it provides outdoor billboard, neon billboard, public transportation promotion, print media promotion, TV promotion, network platform promotion, and pop up ads or banners on mobile application, as well as three-dimensional display, mobile showroom, etc. The company also offers executive recruitment services, such as headhunting talent, human resource outsourcing and consulting, compensation research, and capital introduction services; equity investment services; ESG report services; and asset management services, as well as statutory and commercial insurance products. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.
longName: Wonderful Sky Financial Group Holdings Limited

longBusinessSummary: Labixiaoxin Snacks Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells jelly, confectionary, fruit and vegetable beverage, and other snack products in the People's Republic of China. The company offers jelly snacks and jelly beverages; lollipops, milk candies, gummy candies, and chocolates; and powdered milk tea, dried bean curd, and baked and beverages products under the Labixiaoxin, Sunshine City, Humor, and Xiangdoufang brands. The company was formerly known as China Lifestyle Food and Beverages Group Limited and changed its name to Labixiaoxin Snacks Group Limited in June 2012. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Jinjiang, the People's Republic of China. Labixiaoxin Snacks Group Limited is a subsidiary of Alliance Food and Beverages (Holding) Company Limited.

PC Partner Group Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and sells computer electronics. The company offers video graphics cards for desktop PCs; and computer related products, such as motherboards, mini-PCs, and other computer related products. It also trades in computer parts and accessories, and computers; and provides technical support services. In addition, the company offers electronics manufacturing services to the providers of point-of-sales and automatic teller machine systems, storage devices, consumer products, etc. The company markets its products under the ZOTAC, Inno3D, and Manli brands in the Asia Pacific, North and Latin America, the People's Republic of China, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, and India. PC Partner Group Limited was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Shatin, Hong Kong.

Tianjin Jinran Public Utilities Company Limited engages in the operation and management of gas pipeline infrastructure, and the sale and distribution of piped gas to industrial and commercial users, and residential users in Mainland China. It operates through four segments: Sales of Piped Gas; Gas Connection; Gas Transportation and Rent; and Sales of Gas Appliances and Others. The company also provides piped gas connection services in Tianjin City and Jining, Inner Mongolia; leases pipelines; transports gas; and sells and installs gas appliances. In addition, it engages in the investment, urban gas operation, import and export, pipeline project, investment consultation, and mining investment activities. The company was formerly known as Tianjin Tianlian Public Utilities Company Limited and changed its name to Tianjin Jinran Public Utilities Company Limited in June 2012. The company is headquartered in Tianjin, the People's Republic of China. Tianjin Jinran Public Utilities Company Limited is a subsidiary of Tianjin Gas Group Company Limited.
longName: Tianjin Jinran Public Utilities Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Xiwang Special Steel Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells electric arc furnace-based special steel products in China. The company operates through four segments: Ordinary Steel, Special Steel, Trading of Commodities, and By-Products. It produces ordinary steel products, such as rebars primarily for use in building construction and infrastructure projects; and ribbed and plain wire rods for use in making of coil, spring, electronic, and precise machinery parts. The company offers carbon structural steel products, including steel billets, bars, and wires primarily for buildings and infrastructures; alloy structural steel products for machineries; bearing steel wires and bars for manufacturing rollers or ball bearings for the automobile industry; and steel ingot. It trades in commodities, including iron ore dust, pellets, steel billets, and coke; and sells by-products, such as steel slag, steel scrap, steam, and electricity. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Binzhou, China. Xiwang Special Steel Company Limited is a subsidiary of Xiwang Investment Limited Company.

China MeiDong Auto Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as an automobile dealer in the People's Republic of China. The company is involved in the sale of new passenger cars and spare parts; and the provision of service and survey. It also provides after-sales services, such as auto registration, insurance, auto financing mortgage, auto parts, repair and replacement, sales and maintenance of automotive supplies, etc. In addition, the company engages in the trading of used vehicle and finance leasing activities. Its dealership stores cover various automobile brands comprising BMW, Lexus, Toyota, Hyundai, and Porsche. As of December 31, 2018, it operated 49 4S dealership stores in Guangdong, Hunan, Hubei, Fujian, Jiangxi, Anhui, Beijing, Hebei, and Gansu. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Dongguan, the People's Republic of China. China MeiDong Auto Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Apex Sail Limited.
address1: Unit A1, Tian An Tech Industry Building

longBusinessSummary: China First Capital Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the automotive parts, education operation, and financial services businesses in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, Singapore, Italy, and internationally. It researches, develops, manufactures, and sells automobile shock absorber and suspension system products to the automobile market of original automobile manufacturers and the secondary market of the automobile industry. The company also provides financial services, such as dealing in securities, underwriting and placing of securities, financing consultancy, merger and acquisition agency, financial advisory, asset management, private equity fund management, credit financing, franchising, and overseas education/migration financial services. In addition, it offers schooling services, including kindergarten, and academic and vocational education services, as well as management and consultancy services to educational institutions. Further, it engages in the educational investment and property development businesses. The company was formerly known as China Vehicle Components Technology Holdings Limited and changed its name to China First Capital Group Limited in September 2015. The company was founded in 1951 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Langham Hospitality Investments Limited, an investment holding company, engages in property investment business in Hong Kong. The company owns and invests in a portfolio of hotels under The Langham, Cordis, and Eaton names. It also engages in the provision of administrative, financing, and treasury management services. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Wanchai, Hong Kong. Langham Hospitality Investments Limited is a subsidiary of LHIL Assets Holdings Limited.

Grand Ming Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the building construction, property leasing, and property development businesses in Hong Kong. Its Construction segment constructs residential and commercial buildings, as well as data centers. The company's Property Leasing segment is involved in the lease of data centers and office premises. Its Property Development segment develops and sells residential properties. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong. Grand Ming Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Chan HM Company Limited.

Datang Environment Industry Group Co., Ltd. provides environmental protection and energy conservation solutions to coal-fired power generation enterprises in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Environmental Protection and Energy Conservation Solutions; Renewable Energy Engineering; Thermal Power Engineering; and Other Businesses segments. The Environmental Protection and Energy Conservation Solutions segment engages in the flue gas desulfurization and denitrification facilities concession operation business for coal-fired power plants; the manufacture and sale of denitrification catalysts; engineering business for coal-fired power plants, including the engineering of denitrification, desulfurization, dust removal, ash and slag handling, other environmental protection facilities, and industrial site dust management related engineering; water treatment business; and energy conservation business, such as energy conservation engineering and energy management contract. The Renewable Energy Engineering segment provides engineering general contracting services for newly-built wind power plants, biomass power plants, and photovoltaic power plants. The Thermal Power Engineering segment offers engineering, procurement, and construction services for thermal power plants. The Other Businesses engages in the fiberglass chimney anti-corrosion, air cooling system engineering general contracting, and coal yard monitoring system upgrade. The company was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China. Datang Environment Industry Group Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of China Datang Corporation Ltd.
longName: Datang Environment Industry Group Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: Hong Kong Finance Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides property mortgage loans to individuals and corporations under the Hong Kong Finance brand name in Hong Kong. It also offers personal loans for HOS and public housing homeowners through online to finance children's overseas education; and loans for SMEs. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Admiralty, Hong Kong. Hong Kong Finance Group Limited is a subsidiary of Tin Ching Holdings Limited.

Kinetic Mines and Energy Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the extraction and sale of coal products. The company focuses on the development of its Dafanpu Coal Mine with a concession area of approximately 9.6 square kilometers located in Zhunge'er Banner, Erdos City, Inner Mongolia, China. It also engages in the coal mining, trading, washing, loading, and transportation; and the sale of mineral products. Kinetic Mines and Energy Limited was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

China New Town Development Company Limited engages in planning and developing new towns in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Land Development, Urbanization Development, Property Leasing, and Others segments. The company provides land infrastructure development services; constructs ancillary public facilities; and invests in new town projects. It also offers property leasing and management, real estate and enterprise investment consultation, asset and fund management, investment and asset development, investment management, and engineering management services. The company was founded in 2002 and is based in Yau Ma Tei, Hong Kong.
longName: China New Town Development Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Huiyin Smart Community Co., Ltd., an investment holding company, engages in the retail and bulk distribution sale of household appliances; and e-commerce and import merchandise businesses in the People's Republic of China. It operates through two segments, Traditional Business and New Retail Business. The company is involved in the bulk distribution of air-conditioners, general merchandise, and food products; trading of food and other merchandise; and provision of after-sales, installation, and maintenance services for household appliances. It sells its household appliances merchandise by bulk distribution to retailers and distributors. The company also operates a chain of retail stores for selling household appliances, and import and general merchandises. In addition, it sells its products through an online platform. Further, Huiyin Smart Community Co., Ltd. provides community, logistics, and warehouse services. The company was formerly known as Huiyin Household Appliances (Holdings) Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Huiyin Smart Community Co., Ltd. in July 2015. Huiyin Smart Community Co., Ltd. was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Yangzhou, the People's Republic of China.

LongiTech Smart Energy Holding Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in smart and solar energy, and public infrastructure construction businesses in the People's Republic of China. The company offers smart energy comprehensive utilization services, which include multi-energy complementation, smart operation, energy trade, energy efficiency analysis, and consultancy management. It also engages in distributed solar power plant business comprising operation of industrial and commercial distributed power stations, and home photovoltaic systems. In addition, the company invests in and operates a power distribution grid and an urban centralized heat supply project. The company was formerly known as Long Ji Tai He Holding Limited and changed its name to LongiTech Smart Energy Holding Limited in August 2016. LongiTech Smart Energy Holding Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Glory Sun Financial Group Limited engages in the automation, financial services, manufacturing, property investment and development, and securities investment businesses. The company offers financial services, including wealth management, asset management, global securities and futures, corporate finance, precious metals trading, financial planning and credit, private fund, finance leasing, etc.; and invests in property development and investment, new energy, innovative technology, and healthcare industries. It also produces SMT assembly and semiconductor packaging equipment and other services. The company was formerly known as China Goldjoy Group Limited and changed its name to Glory Sun Financial Group Limited in May 2019. Glory Sun Financial Group Limited was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Admiralty, Hong Kong.

Accel Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides electrical and mechanical engineering services in Hong Kong. It engages in the supply, installation, and maintenance of mechanical, ventilation, and air-conditioning systems; electrical systems; and swimming pool, fountain, and plumbing and drainage systems on a project-by-project basis. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong.

Jiashili Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells biscuits under the Jiashili brand in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company offers breakfast, crisp, sandwich, wafer, soda, and mooncake biscuits series products; and confectioneries. It is also involved in the wholesale and retail of pre-packaged food products. The company was founded in 1956 and is headquartered in Kaiping, the People's Republic of China. Jiashili Group Limited is a subsidiary of Kaiyuan Investment Limited.

Impro Precision Industries Limited manufactures and sells high-precision casting and machined components in the United States, Europe, China, and internationally. It operates in four segments: Investment Casting, Precision Machining, Sand Casting, and Surface Treatment. The company offers investment casting products that include tooling design and manufacturing, metal refining and crystallizing, and heat treatment; machine programming; and cleanliness requirement. It also provides precision machining products for machining process, precision grinding, finishing, special deburring, and cleanliness requirement. In addition, the company offers sand casting products, such as molding, metallurgy, finishing, and machining process. Further, it provides surface treatment products, which comprise process design, testing, electro liquid mix, and temperature mix. The company serves end-markets, including passenger car, commercial vehicle, high horsepower engine, hydraulic equipment, aerospace, construction equipment, agricultural equipment, recreational boat and vehicle, medical, and energy. Impro Precision Industries Limited was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

Agricultural Bank of China Limited provides corporate and retail banking products and services in the Mainland China and internationally. The company operates through Corporate Banking, Personal Banking, and Treasury Operations segments. Its deposit products include demand, call, foreign currency time, foreign currency call, time or demand optional, foreign exchange demand, foreign exchange call, savings, foreign exchange time, agreed-term, and negotiated deposits; and loans comprise housing, consumer, business, fixed asset, working capital, real estate, and entrusted syndicated loans, as well as trade finances, guarantees and commitments, and loans with custody of export rebates accounts. The company also provides credit card, debit card, payment and settlement, private banking, cash management, investment banking, custody, financial market, and financial institution services, as well as trading and wealth management services. In addition, it offers agro-related personal and corporate banking products and services; personal and online, telephone, mobile, self-service, and SMS banking services; financial leasing services; and life, health, and accident insurance, as well as reinsurance products. As of December 31, 2018, the company had 23,381 branches in China; and 13 overseas branches and 4 overseas representative offices. Agricultural Bank of China Limited was founded in 1951 and is based in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Wuxi Sunlit Science and Technology Company Limited engages in the research and development, design, manufacture, equipment supply, installation, testing, repair, and maintenance of production lines for manufacturing steel wire products in the People's Republic of China. Its products include brass electroplating wire production lines, intermediate wire heat treatment lines, wire rod pretreatment lines, double-twist stranding machines, and wet drawing machines, as well as other machines, such as grinding mills, angle grinders, grinding machines, chemical corrosion-resistant troughs, steel wire surface induction heating diffusion equipment, and heat-treatment lead pots. The company is also involved in the trading of machinery products; and software development and software patent rights trading activities. Its products are used in various industries, including radial tire cords, bead wires, sawing wires, hose wires, precision steel wires, and others. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Wuxi, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Wuxi Sunlit Science and Technology Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: China Huirong Financial Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, financing and wealth management services to small and medium sized enterprises, and individuals in the People's Republic of China. It offers short-term loans secured by collateral, such as real estate, equity interests, and personal property; guaranteed loans; and unsecured loans. The company also provides management and marketing consulting; pawnshop; micro-financing and guarantee; factoring; and technology development and consulting services. It operates a pawn sales network of 13 branches. China Huirong Financial Holdings Limited has a strategic cooperation agreement with Suzhou Asset Management Co., Ltd. China Huirong Financial Holdings Limited was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Suzhou, the People's Republic of China.

Changan Minsheng APLL Logistics Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, provides supply chain management services for automobiles and automobile raw materials, components, and parts in Mainland China. It is involved in the integrated transportation of domestic and foreign spare parts; transportation of bulk cargo and large equipment; provision of suppliers warehouse management, production-distribution, modular subpackage, commercial vehicle warehouse management and shipment, after-sales parts warehouse and shipment, bonded warehousing, logistics solution designing, logistics advisory and training, and other services; and packaging of knocked down kits. The company also engages in the sale of packaging materials, as well as processing of tires. In addition, it offers sea, air, river, railway, and road transport services for import and export of cargos, as well as conducts door-to-door services. The company was formerly known as CMA Logistics Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Changan Minsheng APLL Logistics Co., Ltd. in December 2006. Changan Minsheng APLL Logistics Co., Ltd. was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.
longName: Changan Minsheng APLL Logistics Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: Grand Baoxin Auto Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the sale and service of motor vehicles primarily in Mainland China. The company also provides after-sales services, such as maintenance, repair, and vehicle customization, as well as sells related auto parts; sells accessories and other automobile related products, as well as used cars; and provides auto insurance services. In addition, it offers finance leasing, insurance agency, real estate, services. As of December 31, 2018, Grand Baoxin Auto Group Limited operated 113 stores, including 91 luxury and ultra-luxury brand dealing stores, 17 mid-to-high brand dealing stores and 5 independent after-sales service stores. The company was formerly known as Baoxin Auto Group Limited and changed its name to Grand Baoxin Auto Group Limited in April 2017. Grand Baoxin Auto Group Limited was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.

Guodian Technology & Environment Group Corporation Limited provides environmental protection and energy conservation solutions, and renewable energy equipment manufacturing and solutions in the People's Republic of China. Its Environmental Protection segment offers sulphur oxide and nitrogen oxide control technologies, desulphurization and denitrification facilities rental, ash removal with filer bag, and water treatment related technologies and products. The company's Energy Conservation Solutions segment offers energy saving products and services, including plasma and micro-oil ignition equipment; gas turbine improvement services; and energy-efficient power plants construction services. Its Wind Power Products and Services segment produces and sells wind turbine and its components; and offers system solutions and services to wind power operators. The company's Solar Power Products and Services segment produces and sells solar cells, solar modules, and other solar products; and constructs solar power stations, as well as provides related system solutions and services to solar power operators. It also offers desulphurization and other environmental protection engineering services; produces and sells selective catalytic reduction catalyst; constructs and operates water treatment projects; designs and installs sewage treatment equipment; researches, develops, and sells wind turbine technology; and provides energy conservation engineering services. The company produces and sells steam turbines, igniters and other electric equipment, variablepitch control systems for wind turbine, electric power related products, and thermal energy equipment; and researches and develops technology. The company was formerly known as Guodian Technology & Environment Group Limited Liability Company and was changed to Guodian Technology & Environment Group Corporation Limited. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Guodian Technology & Environment Group Corporation Limited

longBusinessSummary: Sinosoft Technology Group Limited, an investment holding company, primarily provides software development and system integration services in the People's Republic of China. It operates through four segments: Tax Software and Related Services, Low Carbon & Ecology Software and Related Services, Government Big Data Software and Related Services, and System Integration Solutions. The company offers export tax software products, consultation services, and training courses. It also provides e-government solutions and products that are used by government agencies at various administrative levels, including the ministerial, provincial, municipal, and district levels. In addition, the company offers carbon management solutions that enable government agencies or enterprises to audit, calculate, and control their greenhouse gas emissions and energy consumption. Further, it provides system integration solutions to government agencies, including information systems consultation and feasibility analysis; sourcing of systems and equipment; LAN and Web-based network design and implementation; analysis, planning, and design of integrated wiring and network systems; design and implementation of video conferencing and multimedia education systems; and system management and supervision, as well as services comprising system architectures, intuitive graphical and multimedia user interfaces, Web services, and other Internet technologies. Additionally, the company sells computer products, as well as offers related services; provides investment and advisory services; and holds properties. Sinosoft Technology Group Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Nanjing, China.

Yunnan Energy International Co. Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the distribution of analytical and laboratory instruments, and life science equipment in the People's Republic of China and internationally. It also provides related repair and maintenance services. The company offers scientific instruments, such as chromatographs, spectrophotometers, electronic microscopes, and life science and general laboratory instruments. It serves businesses and institutions that include universities, research institutions, companies in industrial sector, and government agencies. The company was formerly known as Techcomp (Holdings) Limited and changed its name to Yunnan Energy International Co. Limited in December 2018. Yunnan Energy International Co. Limited was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Yunnan Energy International Co. Limited is a subsidiary of Baodi International Investment Company Limited.

AIA Group Limited provides insurance products and services. The company offers life, medical, accident protection, critical illness protection, and disability income protection insurance products, as well as savings plans for individuals; and employee benefit, Asia benefits network, credit insurance, and retirement solutions for businesses. It also distributes investment and other financial services products. The company distributes its products and services through agents; distribution partners; other intermediated channels, including independent financial advisers, brokers, private banks, and specialist advisers; and direct channel. It operates in Hong Kong, Macau, Thailand, Singapore, Brunei, Malaysia, China, Korea, Australia, Indonesia, New Zealand, the Philippines, Sri Lanka, Taiwan, Vietnam, India, Myanmar, and Cambodia. AIA Group Limited was founded in 1919 and is headquartered in North Point, Hong Kong.

Trigiant Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells feeder cables, optical fiber cables and related products, flame-retardant flexible cables, electronic components, and others for mobile communications and telecommunication equipment. The company's Feeder Cable Series segment offers cables used in transmitting and receiving radio signals, as well as components for telecommunications transmission equipment; and leaky cables primarily used for wireless mobile communications, wireless remote control, and wireless alarm systems for transmitting radio frequency signals, as well as sending and receiving antenna data for areas of weak signal coverage, such as subways, tunnels, underground passages, and interior of buildings. Its Optical Fibre Cable Series and Related Products segment provides cables for use in long haul telecommunication transmission in fixed and wireless telecommunications networks. The company's Flame-Retardant Flexible Cable Series segment offers cables that are used as internal connection cables for power systems or mobile cable transmission, and distribution systems, as well as communications switch systems requiring uninterrupted power. Its New-Type Electronic Components segment provides sensing products; optical splitters; jumpers for connection of wireless antennas with feeder cables and various communications equipment; and connectors for connection of radio frequency circuits to radio equipment and electronic devices, and antenna lightning arresters installed between a high frequency device and a feeder cable. The company's Others segment provides couplers, combiners, feeder wall plates, adjustable stands, waterproof clay, insulating tape, cable ties, and feeder hoisting grips. It operates in the People's Republic of China, as well as exports its products to Brazil, India, Russia, the Middle East, South East Asia, etc. The company was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Yixing, the People's Republic of China.

D&G Technology Holding Company Limited engages in the research and development, design, manufacture, distribution, and leasing of asphalt mixing plants in the People's Republic of China and internationally. Its products include conventional hot-mix asphalt mixing plants and recycling hot-mix asphalt mixing plants. The company also engages in selling spare parts and components; and provides equipment modification services, including modifying conventional plants, installing components with recycling functions, upgrading control systems, and other customized services. In addition, it offers machinery finance services; and bitumen, bitumen tanks, and equipment. The company was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong. D&G Technology Holding Company Limited is a subsidiary of Prima Dg Investment Holding Company Limited.

LifeTech Scientific Corporation, an investment holding company, develops, manufactures, and trades in interventional medical devices for cardiovascular and peripheral vascular diseases and disorders. The company operates through Structural Heart Diseases Business, Peripheral Vascular Diseases Business, and Cardiac Pacing and Electrophysiology Business segments. Its products include LAmbre left atrial appendage closure systems, as well as CeraFlex, Cera, and Heart congenital heart defect occluders; Ankura thoracic aortic aneurysm and abdominal aortic aneurysm stent graft systems; delivery systems, such as FuStar steerable and SteerEase introducers; Aegisy vena cava filters; Cera vascular plug systems; AcuMark sizing balloons; LawMax dilators; and SeQure snare systems, as well as HeartTone pacemakers. The company is also involved in the trade of medical devices; and biomedical research and development, as well as consulting activities. It has operations in the People's Republic of China, India, rest of Asia, South America, Africa, and internationally. The company has a cooperation framework agreement with Sorrento Therapeutics, Inc. for the research and development, production, and commercialization of water-soluble cannabidiol and other water-soluble cannabinoids products. LifeTech Scientific Corporation was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China.

Huili Resources (Group) Limited, an investment holding company, engages in mining, processing, and selling mineral ores in the People's Republic of China. It operates through three segments: Mining, Financial Services, and Engineering Services. The Mining segment primarily explores for gold, nickel, copper, lead, and zinc; and holds two mining and three exploration permits in Xinjiang. The Financial Services segment provides finance leasing services. The Engineering Services segment offers engineering services for exploiting oil, natural gas, and coal-bed methane, as well as pre-drilling engineering and other related services; and trades in materials for oil and gas exploration. Huili Resources (Group) Limited also provides management and investment consultation services. The company was formerly known as Realty Resources (Group) Limited and changed its name to Huili Resources (Group) Limited in May 2010. Huili Resources (Group) Limited was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

Wai Chi Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the manufacture and trading of light-emitting diode (LED) backlight and LED lighting products to business corporations and public utilities in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and internationally. It offers backlight products, such as TFT backlights for consumer electronics products, including mobile devices, laptops, digital frames, digital cameras, etc.; industrial backlight products for industrial instruments, household electrical appliances, medical instruments, electrical appliances, office equipment, measuring equipment, etc.; automotive LED backlights; and light guide plate for TV backlight. The company also provides LED commercial, industrial, and special lighting products. In addition, it provides energy management and LED lighting installation services; and operates a fund center. The company was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. Wai Chi Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of Rexell Technology Company Limited.

SITC International Holdings Company Limited, a shipping logistics company, provides integrated transportation and logistics solutions in Mainland China, Hong Kong, Taiwan, Japan, Southeast Asia, and internationally. It operates in two segments, Container Shipping and Logistics; and Dry Bulk and Others. The Container Shipping and Logistics segment offers container transportation, freight forwarding, shipping agency, depot and warehousing, etc. The Dry Bulk and Others segment provides dry bulk vessel and land leasing, as well as air-freight forwarding services. As of December 31, 2018, the company operated a fleet of 79 vessels with a total capacity of 107,269 TEU, including 52 self-owned vessels with a capacity of 68,806 TEU and 27 chartered vessels with a capacity of 38,463 TEU. It also offers vessel and shipping insurance brokerage, container and vessel holding, storage and terminal, and technology services. The company was founded in 1991 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong. SITC International Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of Resourceful Link Management Limited.

HKBN Ltd., an investment holding company, provides fixed telecommunications network, international telecommunications, and mobile services to residential and enterprise markets primarily in Hong Kong. The company offers a range of information and communications technology services, such as broadband, Wi-Fi, mobile, data connectivity, cloud, data processing/center, information security, business continuity, system integration, and voice communications solutions and services. It provides entertainment, music streaming, and administrative support services; e-business services; outsourcing; property investment; engages in the sale of various products; and holding of licenses, as well as distributes email and related products. The company was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong.

Tongfang Kontafarma Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the manufacture and sale of cement, clinker, and slag in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Medical, and Pharmaceutical and Health Business; Fitness Business; and Cement Business segments. The company also manufactures and sales prescription drugs and laboratory related products; operates fitness centers and franchise business; and provides consultation services for fitness and health activities. In addition, it trades in cement and clinker, and laboratory related products; researches and develops medical products; and offers corporate advisory and energy contracting services. The company was formerly known as Allied Cement Holdings Limited and changed its name to Tongfang Kontafarma Holdings Limited in August 2016. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong. Tongfang Kontafarma Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of China Health Management Investment Limited.

China Resources Cement Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells cement, concrete, and related products and services in Mainland China and Hong Kong. The company engages in the excavation of limestone; and production, sale, and distribution of cement, clinker, and concrete. It offers Portland, ordinary Portland, composite Portland, and slag Portland cement under the Runfeng name. The company's products are primarily used in the construction of infrastructure projects, such as railways, highways, subways, bridges, airports, ports, dams, and hydroelectric and nuclear power stations, as well as high-rise buildings, and suburban and rural area development. It also trades in cement products and construction materials; provides environmental protection engineering, and building materials testing and consultancy services; and holds properties. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong. China Resources Cement Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of CRH (Cement) Limited.

Tsui Wah Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates a chain of restaurants and bakery shops. As of March 31, 2019, the company operated 83 restaurants, which comprise 44 in Hong Kong, 35 in Mainland China, 3 in Macau, and 1 in Singapore under the Tsui Wah brand; and 6 sub-brands, including Nijuuichi Don, BEAT Bakery, Chez Shibata, Maomao Eat, Senbadou, and Deli Blossom. It also provides food catering services under the Supreme Catering and delivery services under the Tsui Wah Delivery names. In addition, Tsui Wah Holdings Limited offers management services; operates a food factory; owns trademarks; and holds properties. The company was founded in 1967 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong. Tsui Wah Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Cui Fa Limited.

Nexteer Automotive Group Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and distributes steering and driveline systems and components for automobile manufacturers and other automotive-related companies. The company offers electric power steering (EPS) products, such as column, pinion, and rack assist; EPS remanufacturing products, intermediate shafts, and modular power packs; and hydraulic power steering products, such as magnetic torque overlay, smart flow pumps, power steering pumps and reservoirs, rack and pinion steering gears, and recirculating ball steering gears. It also provides steering columns products, including power tilts and telescopes, power rakes and telescopes, one-touch adjustable columns, manual rakes and telescopes, non-adjustable columns, intermediate shafts, and transmission shifters, as well as electronics, modules, and sub-assemblies. In addition, the company offers front and rear wheel halfshafts, intermediate drive shafts, and propeller shaft constant velocity joints. Further, it provides advanced driver assistance systems and automated driving technologies comprising Steering on Demand system, Quiet Wheel Steering, and high availability EPS for resilient operational availability, as well as offers customer support and engineering center services. Nexteer Automotive Group Limited operates in North America, the Asia Pacific, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, and South America. The company was founded in 1906 and is headquartered in Auburn Hills, Michigan. Nexteer Automotive Group Limited operates as a subsidiary of Pacific Century Motors.

China Maple Leaf Educational Systems Limited, together with its subsidiaries, operates bilingual private schools and preschools in the People's Republic of China and Canada. The company offers dual-diploma curriculum, such as British Columbia curriculum and Chinese curriculum; and bilingual education services. It operates bilingual private schools and preschools under the Maple Leaf brand name. As of October 15, 2018, the company operated 92 schools, including 14 high schools, 23 middle schools, 24 elementary schools, 28 preschools, and 3 foreign national schools. It also provides construction services. China Maple Leaf Educational Systems Limited was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Dalian, the People's Republic of China.
