longName: China Maple Leaf Educational Systems Limited

longBusinessSummary: Oi Wah Pawnshop Credit Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the provision of secured financing services to high net worth customers in Hong Kong. It offers mortgage and pawn loans, and money lending services, as well as consulting services. The company was founded in 1975 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Oi Wah Pawnshop Credit Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Kwan Lik Holding Limited.
longName: Oi Wah Pawnshop Credit Holdings Limited

longBusinessSummary: China New City Commercial Development Limited, an investment holding company, principally engages in commercial property development, leasing, and hotel operations in Mainland China. It operates through four segments: Commercial Property Development, Property Rental, Hotel Operations, and Others. The company develops, owns, operates, and sells integrated commercial complexes in sub-city centers of second-tier cities in the Yangtze River Delta region. It also leases investment properties, including offices and shopping malls; and provides property management services comprising management and security services to commercial properties. In addition, the company owns and operates three hotels, which include the Holiday Inn Hangzhou Xiaoshan, Hangzhou Qiandao Lake Bright Resort Hotel, and Huaibei Bright Hotel. Further, it engages in education and agricultural development, health, film, television and culture, hospitality, and cultural tourism activities; and investment, theater, and hospital management businesses. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Hangzhou, the People's Republic of China. China New City Commercial Development Limited is a subsidiary of Ideal World Investments Limited.
longName: China New City Commercial Development Limited

longBusinessSummary: Newtree Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the money lending, household consumables, coal, digital technology, and education businesses. The company is involved in the wholesale and retail of household consumables; design and development of three-dimensional animations, as well as augmented reality technology and e-learning Web applications; trading of coal products; provision of educational technology solutions through online education programs, as well as English language proficiency tests; and money lending activities. It sells its products primarily in Hong Kong, the United Kingdom, and the People's Republic of China. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

Luxxu Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures, trades in, and sells watches and jewelries in the People's Republic of China, rest of Asia, and Europe. The company offers diamond watches, tourbillon watches and luxury jewelry accessories, OEM watches, and third-party watches. It markets its products under the Time2U, Jonquet, and Color brands, as well as sells new branded Extreme, prestige, and high-end watches; and designs, produces, and assembles watches for its OEM customers. The company was formerly known as Time2u International Holding Limited and changed its name to Luxxu Group Limited in August 2019. Luxxu Group Limited was founded in 1994 and is based in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong.

Goldstream Investment Limited, an investment holding company, provides customer relationship management (CRM) outsourcing services to companies in various service-oriented industries in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through CRM Services Business and Investment Management Service (IMS) Business segments. The CRM Services Business segment provides inbound services, including a range of customer hotline services, such as general enquiry, technical support, broadband connection arrangement, service installation, account activation, subscriber details update, account enquiry, account termination, order placement, member registration, built-in secretary, and super secretarial services. This segment also offers outbound services comprising telesales and market research services. The IMS Business segment provides advisory services on securities and asset management; and securities trading services. The company also offers services relating to information and telecommunications system network technology; data communications technology services; and marketing and technical support services for telecommunications companies. It serves telecommunications service providers; and non-telecommunications industries, such as realty development, food and beverage, slimming and beauty shops, social welfare, education, information technology, and banking industries. The company was formerly known as International Elite Ltd. and changed its name to Goldstream Investment Limited in July 2019. Goldstream Investment Limited was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Beijing Capital Grand Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the development of commercial properties in the People's Republic of China. The company primarily focuses on the development, operation, and management of outlets-backed commercial integrated and non-outlets retail property projects. It develops residential/commercial/office buildings; and invests in properties. The company was formerly known as Beijing Capital Juda Limited and changed its name to Beijing Capital Grand Limited in June 2017. The company is headquartered in Beijing, China. Beijing Capital Grand Limited is a subsidiary of BECL Investment Holding Limited.

Dynagreen Environmental Protection Group Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the investment, technical consulting, construction, operation, and maintenance of municipal waste-to-energy (WTE) plants in the People's Republic of China. The company engages in the waste treatment and power generation activities. It is also involved in the technological research in environmental protection industries, including waste-incineration, as well as design, development, and systematic integration of relevant equipment; and management of waste treatment projects, as well as the provision of technological services and associated technological consultation. The company was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China. Dynagreen Environmental Protection Group Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of Beijing State-owned Assets Management Co., Ltd.
longName: Dynagreen Environmental Protection Group Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: China Touyun Tech Group Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and sells packaging products in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, Europe, North and South America, and internationally. It operates through three segments: QR Code Business, Packaging Products, and Treasury Investment. The QR Code Business segment provides QR code on product packaging and solutions; and online advertising display services. The Packaging Products segment manufactures watch boxes, jewelry boxes, eyewear cases, bags and pouches, and display units. The Treasury Investment segment invests and trades in securities, as well as offers money lending services. The company is also involved in business intelligence information technology solutions; and the provision of corporate management services. The company was formerly known as China Opto Holdings Limited and changed its name to China Touyun Tech Group Limited in January 2017. China Opto Holdings Limited was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

China Zhongwang Holdings Limited, through its subsidiaries, develops, manufactures, and sells aluminum extruded products in the People's Republic of China, Germany, Italy, the United States, the Netherlands, and internationally. It operates through Aluminium Alloy Formworks, Aluminium Extrusion Products for Industrial Markets, Aluminium Further-Fabricated Products, Aluminium Extrusion Products for Construction Markets, and Aluminium Flat Rolled Products segments. The company offers high precision, large-section, and value-added industrial aluminum extrusion products for use in ecological construction, transportation, machinery and equipment, and electric power engineering sectors; and aluminum flat rolled products. It is also involved in the manufacture of machinery, and special vehicle and parts; trading of aluminum ingots, rods, and other materials; and manufacture of aluminum extrusion molds, alloy formworks, vehicle compartments, furniture, and vessels, as well as provision of investment consulting services. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Liaoyang, the People's Republic of China. China Zhongwang Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Zhongwang International Group Limited.

Sheen Tai Holdings Group Company Limited, an investment holding company, primarily manufactures and sells cigarette-related and non-cigarette-related packaging materials in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through five segments: Manufacturing and Sales of BOPP Films; Sales of Sub-processing Cigarette Films; Properties Development and Related Services; Generation of Photovoltaic Power; and Cloud-related Business. It offers cigarette-related packaging materials comprising anti-counterfeiting films and other cigarette films; and BOPP and BOPP ULT thermal sealing films, and laser base films for packaging non-cigarette-related products. The company is also involved in the trading of imported and sub-processed cigarette films; development and sale of properties; provision of property management services; generation and sale of photovoltaic power; development of cloud computing related software; outsourcing of cloud platforms; and provision of cloud computing solutions and related services. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Sheen Tai Holdings Group Company Limited is a subsidiary of Sheen Tai Group Holding Limited.
longName: Sheen Tai Holdings Group Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Razer Inc. designs, develops, and sells gaming hardware, software, and services under the Razer brand for gamers worldwide. The company operates through four segments: Peripherals, Systems, Software and Services, and Others. It offers hardware products, including high-performance gaming peripherals for PC and console platforms; and Razer Blade gaming laptops. The company's software platform includes Razer Synapse, an Internet of Things platform; Razer Chroma, a proprietary RGB lighting technology system; and Razer Cortex, a game optimizer and launcher. It also provides Razer Gold, a virtual credit services for gamers; and Razer Fintech, an online-to-offline digital payment networks in SE Asia. The company sells its products through a network of distributors and retailers. Razer Inc. was founded in 2005 and has dual headquarters in San Francisco, California and Singapore.

BaWang International (Group) Holding Limited, together with its subsidiaries, designs, manufactures, trades in, and distributes Chinese herbal products in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, Singapore, Thailand, and Malaysia. It operates through Hair-Care Products, Skin-Care Products, and Other Household and Personal Care Products segments. The company offers shampoo, hair-care, skin-care, household cleaning, and shower gel products, as well as laundry detergents under the Bawang, Royal Wind, Herborn, Litao, and Little King brands through distributors and retailers; and through online. It also manufactures, markets, and trades in household and personal care products, as well as offers advertising agency services. The company was founded in 1994 and is based in Guangzhou, China. BaWang International (Group) Holding Limited is a subsidiary of Fortune Station Limited.

The People's Insurance Company (Group) of China Limited, an investment holding company, primarily engages in the insurance business in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Non-Life Insurance, Life Insurance, Health Insurance, Asset Management, and Others segments. The company offers property and casualty insurance products, including motor vehicle, commercial property, liability, credit, accidental injury and health, cargo, agricultural, and other insurance products. It also provides life insurance products comprising general life and health insurance, participating life insurance, universal life insurance, and accident insurance; and health insurance products, such as illness, medical, disability losses, nursing care, accidental injury, and participating endowment insurance products. In addition, the company engages in asset management, agent, reinsurance brokerage, claim handling agency, and Internet finance activities. The People's Insurance Company (Group) of China Limited was founded in 1949 and is based in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
longName: The People's Insurance Company (Group) of China Limited

longBusinessSummary: Huisheng International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in breeding, farming, and slaughtering hogs in the People's Republic of China. The company offers various pork products, including fresh pork, chilled and frozen pork, and side products, as well as processed pork products, such as cured pork and sausages. It is also involved in breeding, farming, and selling piglets and porkers; investment in properties; and provision of administrative services. The company was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in Changde, the People's Republic of China.

Hao Tian International Construction Investment Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the rental of construction machinery in Hong Kong and Macau. The company rents construction machinery, such as crawler cranes, aerial platforms, and foundation equipment; and trades in new or used construction machinery, construction materials, and spare parts, as well as provides repair and maintenance services for the machinery rented. It also offers transportation services, including local container delivery, site construction delivery, and heavy machinery transport services. In addition, the company is involved in the provision of commodities, future, and securities brokerage services, as well as provides property mortgage, machinery, and personal loans. It primarily serves construction work companies that are engaged in public or private construction projects. The company was formerly known as Clear Lift Holdings Limited and changed its name to Hao Tian International Construction Investment Group Limited in May 2017. The company was founded in 1962 and is based in Wanchai, Hong Kong. Hao Tian International Construction Investment Group Limited is a subsidiary of Hao Tian Management (China) Limited.
longName: Hao Tian International Construction Investment Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: China Pioneer Pharma Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, markets, promotes, and sells pharmaceutical products and medical devices primarily in the People's Republic of China. It has a portfolio of pharmaceutical products, such as ophthalmology, pain management, cardiovascular, respiratory, gastroenterology, immunology, gynecology, and other therapeutic areas, as well as medical devices, including ophthalmology, orthopedics, odontology, and wound care products. The company sells its products to hospitals and other medical institutions, and pharmacies. It also leases ancillary tools and accessories; and sells dental devices. In addition, China Pioneer Pharma Holdings Limited engages in the sale of imported in-licensed prescription products. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China. China Pioneer Pharma Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Pioneer Pharma (BVI) Co., Ltd.

Hua Hong Semiconductor Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells semiconductor products. It primarily focuses on the research and manufacturing of semiconductors on 200mm wafers for specialty applications, including embedded non-volatile memory (eNVM) and power discrete. The company offers eNVM, power management integrated circuits, power discrete, radio frequency, standard logic and mixed-signal, and automotive solutions; and process technologies, such as RFCMOS, analog and mixed signal, PMIC, and MEMS. It also offers foundry services; and design services comprising standard and customized IP development, full-custom layout design, and customer-specific integrated solutions, as well as design support and tape out services. In addition, the company provides multi-project wafer services; mask making services; and backend services, such as in-house testing, backside processing and dicing, and backend turnkey services, as well as wafer probing, assembly, and testing. Its products are used in consumer electronics, communications, computing, industrial, and automotive markets in the People's Republic of China, the United States, Europe, Japan, and other Asian countries. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China. Hua Hong Semiconductor Limited is a subsidiary of Shanghai Alliance Investment Ltd.

Quali-Smart Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the manufacture of toys on OEM/ODM basis in Hong Kong and internationally. The company operates through Manufacturing and Sales of Toys; and Financial Services segments. It focuses on the manufacturing of toy products for infants aged three or below. It is also involved in principal investments, institutional sales, financial products, research, and corporate access activities, as well as advises on corporate finance and asset management. In addition, the company provides securities brokerage, securities margin financing, and investment advisory and fund management services. Further, it is involved in the trading and investment of securities, debts, and funds. Quali-Smart Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong.

Shanghai Fudan-Zhangjiang Bio-Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, researches, develops, manufactures, and sells bio-pharmaceutical products. It offers genetic technical platform drugs, including recombinant human TNF receptor 2-Fc fusion protein mutant, which completed Phase I clinical trials for the treatment of arthritis; CD30-MMAE, which has obtained approval for clinical trial for tumors; Trop 2 Antibody-drug conjugates that is in pre-clinical studies for tumors; and Avastin, which has obtained approval for clinical trial for tumors. The company also provides photodynamic technical platform drugs, such as Hemoporfin for port wine stain, which is Phase IV clinical trial; Deuteroporphyrin that is in Phase II clinical trials for tumors; Aminolevulinic acid, which is in Phase II clinical trials for cervical diseases infected by HPV; and Aminolevulinic acid that is in Phase I clinical trials for acne, as well as is in pre-clinical studies for brain gliomas and basal cell carcinoma. In addition, it offers Nano technical platform drugs comprising Nanoparticle Albumin-bound Paclitaxel that is in pre-clinical studies for tumors, as well as developing Doxorubicin liposome for tumors. Further, the company offers Oral solid preparation technology, which includes Obeticholic acid for Hepatobiliary disease; and JAK1 inhibitor that is in pre-clinical study for autoimmune diseases. Additionally, it researches and develops pharmaceutical projects and medical instruments; medical diagnostic products; provides related services; and sells daily necessities. It also engages in the provision of medical investment management, health industry management, projects investment, assets management, investment and business consultation, medical and enterprise management consultation activities, business consultation, and marketing services. The company was founded in 1996 and is based in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.

Legend Strategy International Holdings Group Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the hotel operation activities in the People's Republic of China. The company also engages in the money lending; and hotel consultancy and management service, and other related businesses. As of December 31, 2018, it had four leased-and-operated hotels. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Legend Strategy International Holdings Group Company Limited is a subsidiary of Hehui International Development Limited.
longName: Legend Strategy International Holdings Group Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Meitu, Inc., an investment holding company, designs, develops, and sells hardware in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and internationally. It operates in two segments, Internet Services and Smart Hardware. The company offers Internet services, including online advertising, Internet value added services, and e-commerce services; and M, V, and T series of smartphones under the Meitu brand. It also develops photo and community applications, including BeautyCam, Meipai, MakeupPlus, MeituBeauty, PartyNow, Airbrush, and BeautyPlus, as well as SelfieCity. In addition, the company engages in the provision of information technology services. It offers its products and services directly to end customers, as well as through distributors and retailers. Meitu, Inc. has a strategic cooperation agreement with Xiaomi Corporation. Meitu, Inc. was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Xiamen, China.

PW Medtech Group Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a medical device company in the People's Republic of China. It manufactures and sells infusion sets, such as non-PVC-based infusion sets, precision filter infusion sets, light resistant infusion sets, and intravenous cannula products. The company was formerly known as Pyholding Limited. PW Medtech Group Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

China Cinda Asset Management Co., Ltd. acquires, manages, invests in, and disposes financial and non-financial institution distressed assets in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in three segments: Distressed Asset Management Business, Financial Investment and Asset Management Business, and Financial Services Business. It is also involved in receivership; foreign investment; securities and futures dealing; financial bond issuance; inter-bank borrowing and lending; commercial financing for other financial institutions; approved asset securitization business; financial institutions custody; and closing and liquidation of business. In addition, the company engages in consulting and advisory business on finance, investment, and legal and risk management; asset and project evaluation; banking business; insurance; fund management; asset management; trust; financial leasing services; and real estate and industrial investments and other businesses. Further, it is involved in securities brokerage, life insurance, real estate development, property leasing, hotel management, and aircraft leasing activities. The company serves customers through 33 branches. China Cinda Asset Management Co., Ltd. was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
longName: China Cinda Asset Management Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: NOVA Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, organizes exhibitions, trade shows, and events in the People's Republic of China. The company also provides ancillary services for trade shows, exhibitions, and events. In addition, it is involved in the provision of brand identity design services; bar and club membership, wine and liquor promotion, event planning, and consulting services; brand management and related downstream services; contracting and entertainment equipment solution services; software and technology services; bar brand services; and personal and corporate loans, money financing, finance leasing, and credit factoring for clients in cultural and entertainment industries. Further, the company engages in the supplying and installation of equipment and facilities used in cultural and entertainment industries; and provision of ad-hoc consultancy services for the clients in cultural and entertainment industries. The company was formerly known as Mega Expo Holdings Limited and changed its name to NOVA Group Holdings Limited in June 2019. NOVA Group Holdings Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Admiralty, Hong Kong.

361 Degrees International Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and sells adults and children sporting goods in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in two segments, Adults and Kids. It offers professional footwear, apparel, and accessories under the 361 core brand name for adults, as well as under the 361 Kids brand name for children; and skiing, cycling, and other outdoor activities sporting products under the ONE WAY brand. The company also manufactures and trades in shoes soles; trades in children sporting goods; and operates a gas station. As of December 31, 2018, it operated a network of 5,539 stores under the 361 core brand name. The company also sells products through its 361sport.com Website; other e-commerce platforms, including Tmall, Taobao, and JD; and authorized retailers and distributors. 361 Degrees International Limited was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Xiamen, the People's Republic of China.

SiS Mobile Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, distributes and sells mobile phones and related products in Hong Kong. It primarily distributes mobile phones of various brands, including Samsung, Blackberry, Acer, Asus, Lenovo, Alcatel One Touch, Lenovo, Honor, Nexstgo, ZTE, etc. to wholesale customers, telecommunications services operators, and chain retailers. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. SiS Mobile Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of SiS International Holdings Limited.

CT Environmental Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides industrial wastewater treatment and water supply services in the People's Republic of China. It is involved in the planning, construction, operation, and maintenance of the environmental protection facilities. The company designs, constructs, operates, and maintains wastewater and solid waste treatment plants; and provides sludge and solid waste, and hazardous waste disposal and treatment services, as well as wastewater processing and heating, urban and domestic waste detoxification, and environmental inspection services. CT Environmental Group Limited also engages in the electricity generation. As of December 31, 2017, it operated approximately 14 water treatment plants, comprising 7 industrial wastewater treatment plants, 3 municipal wastewater treatment plants, and 4 industrial water supply plants. The company was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong. CT Environmental Group Limited is a subsidiary of Keen Vast Holdings Limited.

China Rundong Auto Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the sale and service of motor vehicles in Mainland China. The company's brand portfolio includes 9 luxury brands, which comprise BMW, MINI, Jaguar, Land Rover, Alfa Romeo, Audi, Lexus, Cadillac, and Chrysler; 2 ultra-luxury brands, such as Maserati and Ferrari; and 14 mid- to high-end brands consisting of Buick, Hyundai, Ford, Chevrolet, Shanghai-Volkswagen, Kia, Dongfeng Honda, GAC-Honda, FAW-Toyota, GAC-Toyota, Toyota, Dongfeng Nissan, Zhengzhou Nissan, and FAW-Volkswagen. It also provides after-sale services; and sells spare parts and accessories. In addition, the company engages in the brokerage of automobile insurance; and provision of automobile financing and leasing services. As of December 31, 2018, it operated 85 stores, which included 62 stores located in Jiangsu Province, 14 stores in Shandong Province, and 6 stores in Shanghai, as well as 1 store each in the provinces of Zhejiang, Anhui, and Liaoning. The company was formerly known as China Greenland Rundong Auto Group Limited and changed its name to China Rundong Auto Group Limited in February 2017. China Rundong Auto Group Limited was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Shanghai, China.

Jiangnan Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and trades in wires and cables in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Power Cables, Wires and Cables for Electrical Equipment, Bare Wires, and Special Cables segments. The company offers power cables primarily for the use in power transmission and distribution systems; and wires and cables for use in the supply and distribution of electricity for various applications, such as industrial machinery, instruments, meters, and household appliances, as well as wires in the buildings. It also provides bare wires, including aluminum reinforced wires, aluminum conductor steel reinforced wires, and aluminum alloy conductors that are used as overhead power lines for power transmission; and special cables and wires for the ship building, wind power generation, and mining industries, as well as rubber, fire proof, and other cables. In addition, the company is involved in the trading of copper conductors, and wires and cables; and engineering, procurement, and construction of electric power related projects. Its products are used in power and general industries, including metals and mining, oil and gas, transportation, shipbuilding, and construction industries. Jiangnan Group Limited also exports its products to approximately 100 countries. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in Shatin, Hong Kong. Jiangnan Group Limited is a subsidiary of Power Heritage Group Limited.

SFund International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides apparel supply chain management services in Hong Kong, Mainland China, the United States, and internationally. The company's services include sourcing of raw materials and third-party manufacturers, sample creation, product design and development, production management, merchandising, quality control, logistics management, and social compliance monitoring for woven wear, such as shirts, pants, jeans, and jackets; and accessories. It also trades in apparel products; and offers property investment, asset management and advisory, securities investment and brokerage, fund management, money lending, and management services. The company was formerly known as Hanbo Enterprises Holdings Limited and changed its name to SFund International Holdings Limited in December 2017. SFund International Holdings Limited was founded in 1991 and is based in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

Xtep International Holdings Limited engages in the design, development, manufacture, sale, and marketing and brand management of sports footwear, apparel, and accessories. The company sells its products primarily under the XTEP brand. It is also involved in the trading of sportswear products. The company manages an extensive distribution network with exclusive distributors that operate approximately 6,200 stores covering 31 provinces, autonomous regions, and municipalities in the People's Republic of China. It also offers its products online. The company was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Xiamen, the People's Republic of China. Xtep International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Group Success Investments Limited.

Aowei Holding Limited, through its subsidiaries, engages in the exploration, mining, processing, and sale of iron ore products in the People's Republic of China. The company's principal products include iron ores, preliminary concentrates, and iron ore concentrates. It owns and operates four iron ore mines, including Gufen Mine covering an area of approximately 1.3821 square kilometers located in Shuibao Village, Laiyuan County; Wang'ergou Mine that covers an area of approximately 1.5287 square kilometers situated in Zoumayi Village, Laiyuan County; Shuanmazhuang Mine, which covers an area of approximately 2.1871 square kilometers located in Zoumayi Village, Laiyuan County; and Zhijiazhuang Mine covering an area of approximately 0.3337 square kilometers situated in Yangjiazhuang Village, Laiyuan County. Aowei Holding Limited also provides hospital management services; establishes specialist clinics; and supplies medical consumables and nursing services. In addition, it is also engaged in supply chain business. The company was formerly known as Hengshi Mining Investments Limited and changed its name to Aowei Holding Limited in November 2017. Aowei Holding Limited was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

China LotSynergy Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides technology and operation services for lottery systems, terminal equipment, and game products in the lottery market in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company offers video lottery systems, computer-generated ticket games (CTG), and KENO-type lottery systems. It is also involved in the research, development, and manufacture of lottery ticket scanners and terminal equipment, as well as lottery systems and equipment; and research, development, and operation of sales platform for high frequency lottery systems. In addition, the company provides treasury management services, as well as develops lottery transaction and management systems. It provides its CTG terminals primarily to Welfare Lottery and Sports Lottery authorities. China LotSynergy Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

Bisu Technology Group International Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the development, production, and sale of automotive engines in the People's Republic of China and Hong Kong. The company operates in two segments, Automotive Engines Business, and Civil Engineering and Construction Business. It is also involved in the provision of civil engineering, and building construction and maintenance works; and leasing of equipment for construction works. The company was formerly known as Excel Development (Holdings) Limited and changed its name to Bisu Technology Group International Limited in February 2017. Bisu Technology Group International Limited was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Bisu Technology Group International Limited is a subsidiary of Youth Force Asia Ltd.

International Housewares Retail Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the retail sale and trading of housewares products. The company operates its stores under the Japan Home Centre, Japan Home, 123 by ELLA, City Life, and Epo Gifts & Stationery brands. It has a retail network comprising 365 stores in Hong Kong, Singapore, Macau, East Malaysia, Cambodia, Australia, and Vietnam. The company is also involved in licensing of franchise rights; and the provision of management services. In addition, it engages in the manufacture and export of housewares products; property investment activities; and retail sale of gifts and accessories. The company was founded in 1991 and is headquartered in Wong Chuk Hang, Hong Kong.

Central China Securities Co., Ltd., a securities company, engages in the brokerage, investment banking, investment management, proprietary trading, and offshore businesses. It trades in stocks, funds, bonds, and commodity and financial futures on behalf of its clients. The company also provides futures trading and brokering, and futures information advisory and training services; margin trading and securities lending services; and investment banking services, such as corporate finance and financial advisory to institutional clients, as well as trades in financial products. In addition, it offers investment and asset management services, such as investments and funds related businesses; portfolio management and maintenance; and investment advisory and transaction execution services. Further, the company offers margin financing, trading and investment, and financial planning and advisory services, as well as engages in treasury and micro-credit operations. Central China Securities Co., Ltd. was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Zhengzhou, China.

China Hongqiao Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells aluminum products in the People's Republic of China and Indonesia. The company's products include molten aluminum alloys, aluminum alloy ingots, aluminum busbars, and aluminum alloy processing products. It also engages in the research, development, and trading of bauxite; produces and sells electricity; and provides financial leasing services. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Zouping, the People's Republic of China. China Hongqiao Group Limited is a subsidiary of China Hongqiao Holdings Limited.

Canvest Environmental Protection Group Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the development, construction, operation, and management of waste-to-energy plants in the People's Republic of China. It also provides environmental hygiene and related services. As of March 25, 2019, the company had 22 operating, secured, announced, and managed projects. In addition, it provides municipal solid waste handling, human resources and administrative, transportation, and consultancy services. The company was founded in 2003 and is based in Kowloon, Hong Kong. Canvest Environmental Protection Group Company Limited is a subsidiary of Best Approach Developments Limited.
longName: Canvest Environmental Protection Group Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Pacific Textiles Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the manufacturing and trading of textile products. The company is involved in the knitting, dyeing, printing, and finishing of fabrics. Its fabrics are used in a range of garments, including men's, women's, and children's clothing, as well as sportswear, swimwear, and inner-wear. The company operates in the People's Republic of China, Vietnam, Hong Kong, the United States, Indonesia, Cambodia, Thailand, Sri Lanka, India, Haiti, Africa, and internationally. Pacific Textiles Holdings Limited was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong.

Suncity Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in property development, leasing, and management business in the People's Republic of China Macau, Hong Kong, Japan, Cambodia, and Vietnam. It operates through Property Development; Property Leasing; Hotel and Integrated Resort Management and Consultancy Services; and Travel Related Products and Services segments. The company develops and sells office premises, and residential and retail properties, as well as leases commercial properties in Guangdong, Liaoning, and Anhui provinces. It also provides management and consultancy services to hotels and integrated resorts in Vietnam; operates and manages casino in Vietnam and Cambodia; and offers travel agency services, as well as engages in the sale of travel related products. The company was formerly known as Sun Century Group Limited and changed its name to Suncity Group Holdings Limited in May 2017. The company is based in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China. Suncity Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Fame Select Limited.

Shanghai Fudan Microelectronics Group Company Limited engages in designing, developing, and selling products of application specific integrated circuits (ICs) in Mainland China, rest of the Asia Pacific, and internationally. It offers security and identification products, including contact and contactless memory ICs, NFC tag and channel ICs, HF RFID tag ICs, contactless CPU card, chips, contact dual interface, CPU card chips, secured encryption chips, and HF readers. The company also provides smart meters ASIC chips, ultra-low general purpose MCU, and ePLC solutions; NVM products, such as EEPROM, SPI NOR Flash, SPI and parallel NAND Flash, and ASNVM; and specific analog circuits, including earth leakage protection device, lighting circuit, auto and motorcycle circuit, communication circuit, consumer electronics, etc. In addition, it offers bank, smart meter, social security, and smart transportation card solutions. Further, the company designs, develops, and sells IC testing software and products; produces probe cards; offers research and consultancy services of IC technology; and provides testing services for IC products. The company was formerly known as Shanghai Fudan Microelectronics Company Limited and changed its name to Shanghai Fudan Microelectronics Group Company Limited. Shanghai Fudan Microelectronics Group Company Limited was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Shanghai, Hong Kong.
longName: Shanghai Fudan Microelectronics Group Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Vestate Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, develops and retails a range of footwear products. The company sells products through acupuncture, ARTEMIS, COUBER.G, FORLERIA, A+A2, TRU-NARI, MY WALKER, and WALACI brands through its self-managed retail shops, concession points in department stores, and franchised stores in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and Taiwan. As of March 31, 2019, it operated 61 concession points in the People's Republic of China; 12 self-managed shops and 1 concession point in Hong Kong; and 7 concession points in Taiwan. The company was formerly known as Walker Group Holdings Limited and changed its name to Vestate Group Holdings Limited in February 2017. Vestate Group Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong.

China Dili Group, an investment holding company, engages in the operation of agriculture wholesale markets in the People's Republic of China. The company leases and manages agriculture wholesale market. It operates 10 wholesale markets in Harbin, Shenyang, Shouguang, Guiyang, Qiqihaer, Mudanjiang, and Hangzhou covering total land parcels of approximately 2.12m sq.m with total gross floor area of approximately 1.56m sq.m. The company was formerly known as Renhe Commercial Holdings Company Limited and changed its name to China Dili Group in June 2019. China Dili Group was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Central, Hong Kong.

Embry Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, researches, develops, manufactures, trades in, and sells ladies brassieres, panties, swimwear, and sleepwear. The company sells its lingerie products primarily under the Embry Form, Fandecie, Comfit, E-BRA, Iadore, IVU, and LIZA CHENG brands. It also holds trademark and invests in properties. As of December 31, 2018, the company had 1,837 retail outlets comprising 1,557 concessionary counters and 280 retail stores in Mainland China, Hong Kong, and Macau. It also operates an online shop. The company was founded in 1975 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong.

Major Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the sale and distribution of premium wine and spirits in Hong Kong. It offers red wine, white wine, sparkling wine, sake, champagne, wine accessory products, and other products. The company is also involved in trading of wine, as well as provides wine storage and consignment services. It offers products through its retail shops; and through a network of distributors, retail organizations, five-star hotels, and private clubs. The company was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.

Hidili Industry International Development Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the coal mining, and manufacture and sale of raw coal and clean coal in the People's Republic of China. It also offers clean coal washing services. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Panzhihua, the People's Republic of China. Hidili Industry International Development Limited is a subsidiary of Sanlian Investment Holding Limited.

ELL Environmental Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, constructs, operates, and manages wastewater treatment facilities in the People's Republic of China, Indonesia, and Hong Kong. The company operates two wastewater treatment facilities that handle municipal and industrial wastewater in Jiangsu Province. It also engages in palm kernel oil production; and the generation of electricity from biomass power plants. The company serves local government authorities. ELL Environmental Holdings Limited was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Rugao, the People's Republic of China.
address1: Rugao Hengfa Municipal and Industrial Wastewater Treatment Facility

longBusinessSummary: Hydoo International Holding Limited, together with its subsidiaries, develops, operates, and sells commercial trade and logistics centers, and residential properties in the People's Republic of China. The company's trade centers are used for the wholesale and retail sale of a range of products, including hardware, electric tools, building materials, furniture and home furnishings, home electronics, apparel, and small goods. It is also provides property management, investment management, and finance leasing services. Hydoo International Holding Limited was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China. Hydoo International Holding Limited is former subsidiary of Most Trend Holdings Limited.

Baguio Green Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides environmental and related services in Hong Kong. It operates through four segments: Cleaning Services Business, Landscaping Services Business, Pest Management Business, and Waste Management and Recycling Business. The company offers cleaning services for commercial and industrial buildings, residential premises, and public hygiene; pest control services, such as integrated pest management, termite control, and leisure places pest control; and landscaping services, including horticultural and lawn maintenance services, as well as supplies landscape materials. It also provides landscape engineering services comprising tree survey and assessment, turfing, and landscape design; and waste management services consisting of materials recovery, as well as undertakes construction and other waste management projects. In addition, the company offers automobile repair services; and develops and explores for green technology products. It serves household clients, multinational corporations, semi-government organizations, and government departments. The company was founded in 1980 and is headquartered in Lai Chi Kok, Hong Kong. Baguio Green Group Limited is a subsidiary of Baguio Green (Holding) Limited.

Moody Technology Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, manufactures, and sells fabrics and yarns in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in two segments, Sales of Fabrics and Sales of Shoes and Clothes. It sells grey and dyed garment fabrics and trades in cloths. The company was formerly known as Wang Tai Holdings Limited and changed its name to Moody Technology Holdings Limited in August 2018. Moody Technology Holdings Limited was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Shishi, the People's Republic of China.

Cowell e Holdings Inc., an investment holding company, engages in the design, development, manufacture, and sale of camera modules for smartphones, multimedia tablets, laptops, PDAs, and other mobile devices with camera functions in the People's Republic of China, the Republic of Korea, and internationally. It also designs, develops, manufactures, and sells optical components used in various consumer electronics products. The company's optical components include CD-P, RW/ROM, DVD-P, ROM, RW/RAM, Blue-ray disk, and Blue filter products. It offers camera modules for mobile device manufacturers; and optical components to subsidiaries or affiliates of electronics companies. Cowell e Holdings Inc. was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Dongguan, the People's Republic of China.

Riverine China Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides property management services in the People's Republic of China. The company offers standard property management services, such as engineering, repair and maintenance services, customer services, security services, and cleaning and gardening services; and value-added services, including various kinds of consultancy services related to property management. It manages public properties, office buildings and hotels, commercial establishments, government properties, residential properties, and others. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Shanghai, China. Riverine China Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Partner Summit Holdings Limited.

Sinomax Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures, trades, and sells health and household products, and polyurethane foam. The company offers visco-elastic pillows, mattress toppers, and mattresses under the SINOMAX, SPA Supreme, ComforZen, Dream Serenity, Zeopedic, Customizer, and DORMEO brands, as well as various licensed brands, such as Sharper Image, awaken by Joan Lunden, and HoMedics; and polyurethane foam under the Tung Ah brand. It sells its products through a self-operated retail network comprising retail shops and concession counters in department stores, as well as e-commerce sales and wholesale channels. The company also engages in the retail and wholesale of health and household products; and provision of treasury management services. It provides its products in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and Macau; the United States, Canada, and other American countries; and Europe and internationally. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong. Sinomax Group Limited is a subsidiary of Sinomax Enterprises Limited.

Human Health Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides healthcare services in Hong Kong. The company offers general practice services, including general consultation, diagnostics and preventative health, minor procedure, vaccination, physical check-up, health education, occupational health advisory, Chinese medicine, and work injury assessment services. It also provides specialty services in the areas of general surgery, orthopedics and traumatology, ophthalmology, otorhinolaryngology, pediatrics, obstetrics and gynecology, gastroenterology and hepatology, respiratory medicine, cardiology, pediatric surgery, dermatology, geriatric medicine, psychiatry, radiology, urology, nephrology, family medicines, oncology, and public health medicine, as well as physiotherapy, clinical psychology, medical aesthetics, chiropractic, endoscopy, and medical diagnostics. In addition, the company offers dental services comprising oral examinations, dental implants, crowns and bridges, endodontics, prosthodontics, oral surgeries, bleaching, one-hour tooth whitening, orthodontics, veneers and laser dentistry, advanced oral and maxillofacial surgeries, CAD/CAM denistry, periodontal treatments, panoramic radiography, and cone-beam computed tomography. Further, it provides doctors and dentists agreements management, and medical imaging services. As of June 30, 2019, the company operated 65 medical centers and 121 service points. It serves individual and corporate customers, which comprise medical scheme management companies, insurance companies, and corporations. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. Human Health Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Treasure Group Global Limited.

Chuan Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides earthworks and related, and construction services to contractors in Singapore. The company's earthworks include land clearing, demolition, rock breaking, mass excavation, deep basement and foundation excavation, earth disposal and filling, and shore protection services. Its general construction works consist of alteration and addition works, including interior works or works affecting building systems or components, such as structural works, additions of lifts, and reinforcement works; and the construction of new buildings. The company is also involved in the rental of construction and civil engineering machinery and equipment. Chuan Holdings Limited was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Singapore.

Kingbo Strike Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the construction, operation, and sale of solar power station projects in the People's Republic of China. The company is involved in the supply and installation of solar photovoltaic parts and equipment. It also engages in the provision of electrical engineering services for public residential projects in Singapore; finance business; and trading of consumer products and accessories. The company is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Bright Smart Securities & Commodities Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides financial services in Hong Kong. It operates through three segments: Securities Broking, Commodities and Futures Broking, and Bullion Trading. The company offers securities, commodities, and futures and stock options brokerage services; margin financing services; initial public offering brokerage and financing services; and forex and bullion trading services. It is also involved in the provision of asset management and administrative services; and production and broadcast finance programs. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Bright Smart Securities & Commodities Group Limited operates as a subsidiary of New Charming Holdings Ltd.
longName: Bright Smart Securities & Commodities Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: Suchuang Gas Corporation Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the distribution and sale of piped natural gas to industrial, commercial, and residential users in the People's Republic of China. It also provides natural gas transmission services; operates as a contractor for the construction and installation of gas pipelines; and constructs and operates natural gas filling stations. As of December 31, 2018, the company operated five compressed natural gas (CNG) and liquefied natural gas (LNG) refuelling stations, including three stations in Guangyuan; one station in Taicang; and one station in Suzhou. It serves 584 commercial and industrial customers, and 240,000 residential customers. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Suzhou, the People's Republic of China.

YuanShengTai Dairy Farm Limited, a dairy farming company, engages in the production and sale of raw milk in the People's Republic of China. As of December 31, 2018, it had six farms in Heilongjiang Province and one farm in Jilin Province with a total of 63,644 cows. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Qiqihar, the People's Republic of China.

China Shengmu Organic Milk Limited, an investment holding company, produces and distributes raw milk and dairy products in the People's Republic of China. China Shengmu Organic Milk Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Bayannur, the People's Republic of China.

Mobile Internet (China) Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells paper-based packaging products in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in two segments, Mobile Gaming Business and Packaging Business. It offers flexo-printed cartons; and offset-printed cartons, including traditional paper-based and stone-paper based cartons. The company also provides free-to-play mobile, browser, and client-based online games. Its products are used in the packaging of various products, such as food and beverage, glass and ceramics articles, metal hardware, chemicals products, shopping bags, and bamboo articles; and other products, including stationary, energy, electronic, textile, and pharmaceutical products. The company was formerly known as China Packaging Holdings Development Limited and changed its name to Mobile Internet (China) Holdings Limited in July 2017. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Yichun, the People's Republic of China. Mobile Internet (China) Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Novel Blaze Limited.

Fulum Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, owns and operates various restaurants in the People's Republic of China. As of March 31, 2019, the company operated 73 restaurants covering 29 restaurants under the Fulum brand name, 11 restaurants under the Sportful Garden brand name, and 33 restaurants under the Fulum Concept line in Hong Kong; and 4 restaurants in Mainland China. It also processes, sells, and distributes food products; provides management services; trades in kitchen utensils and other operating items; owns trademarks; lends money; and holds properties. Fulum Group Holdings Limited was founded in 1992 is headquartered in San Po Kong, Hong Kong.

Hung Fook Tong Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the production, retail, wholesale, and distribution of bottled drinks and other herbal products in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and internationally. It offers Chinese herbal drinks and other drink products, Chinese-style soups, herbal tortoise plastron jelly, and other food products under the Hung Fook Tong brand name; and snacks, desserts, rice, noodles, and food products for Chinese festivals and other occasions. The company is also involved in manufacturing, trading, importing, wholesaling, and distributing bottled drinks; the property investment, coupons wholesaling, catering, and plastics bottles manufacturing activities; providing training courses; and offering logistics and trading services. In addition, it engages in the restaurant management activities; and import and export of general merchandise. As of December 31, 2018, the company operated 115 retail shops in Hong Kong. It also sells its wellness drinks to distributors in Macau, the United States, Canada, Malaysia, Australia, Singapore, Taiwan, the Philippines, New Zealand, Britain, the Netherlands, Spain, etc. Hung Fook Tong Group Holdings Limited was founded in 1986 and is based in Tai Po, Hong Kong.
longName: Hung Fook Tong Group Holdings Limited

longBusinessSummary: SFK Construction Holdings Limited engages in the construction and maintenance of building and civil engineering projects primarily in Hong Kong. It operates through three segments: General Building, Civil Engineering, and Others. The company also undertakes construction projects in Macau under the SFK brand. It offers engineering services for substructure or superstructure of building structures and infrastructure facilities; and maintenance, repair, and alteration services to building structures and infrastructure facilities, as well as additions to building structures. In addition, the company provides housing and property management services, such as cleaning and security management, and building information modeling services, as well as electrical and mechanical engineering, and consultancy services. It serves customers in the public and private sectors. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong. SFK Construction Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Sun Fook Kong Group Limited.

Fu Shou Yuan International Group Limited, together with its subsidiaries, primarily provides burial and funeral services in the People's Republic of China. It operates through three segments: Burial Services, Funeral Services, and Others. The Burial Services segment sells burial plots; and offers cemetery maintenance services. The Funeral services segment engages in the planning of funeral arrangement; and interment, organizing, and hosting of the funeral. The Others segment manufactures and sells cremation machines; and provides auxiliary services, such as landscape and garden design. It also offers flowers and related designing services; sales and after-sales service for cremation devices; management services to cemeteries; and consulting services to burial and cemetery maintainers. In addition, the company sells agricultural products. As of December 31, 2018, it had approximately 20 cemeteries and 22 funeral facilities. Fu Shou Yuan International Group Limited was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Fu Shou Yuan International Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: Century Sage Scientific Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily provides hardware and software application solutions. The company operates through Application Solutions, System Maintenance Services, and Sales of Self-Developed Products segments. It offers TV broadcast application solutions and integration services; and researches, develops, and sells technical products. The company is also involved in the research and development of TV broadcasting and multi-media production; equipment trading activities; and provision of turnkey solutions to Internet protocol TV and over-the-top video service operators. The company operates in Mainland China, Hong Kong, and internationally. Scientific Holdings Limited was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Beijing, China.

MS Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, produces and sells plastic bottles and baby feeding accessories. The company operates in two segments, OEM Business and Yo Yo Monkey Business. It offers plastic bottles and cups for infants and toddlers, as well as plastic sports bottles on an original equipment manufacturing (OEM) basis; and under the company's Yo Yo Monkey brand for sale to retailers and distributors. The company's OEM services include mould building, injection and blow moulding processes, physical testing, graphic design, general assembly, and packaging. The company operates in the United States, the People's Republic of China, the Netherlands, and internationally. MS Group Holdings Limited was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong.

Denox Environmental & Technology Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and sells plate-type DeNOx catalysts in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company sells its plate-type DeNOx catalysts to coal-fired power plants; engineering, procurement, and construction services providers; and boiler manufacturers. It also produces stainless steel mesh. In addition, the company develops catalysts for diesel-powered vehicles and vessels. Denox Environmental & Technology Holdings Limited was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Guolian Securities Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, provides various financial products and services in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Securities Brokerage, Credit Transaction, Investment Banking, Proprietary Trading, Asset Management and Investment, and Other Business segments. The company offers securities trading and brokering services; financial leverage services for brokerage clients, securities-backed lending services, and securities repurchase services; and corporate finance and financial advisory services to institutional clients and market maker business. It is also involved in direct investment and funds related businesses, as well as provision of management and maintenance, investment advisory, and transaction execution services; and securities and bonds underwriting and sponsorship, proprietary securities investment, asset management, introducing broker for futures companies, margin financing, and the agency sale of financial broker products. The company was formerly known as Wuxi Securities Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Guolian Securities Co., Ltd. in May 2008. Guolian Securities Co., Ltd. was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Wuxi, the People's Republic of China.

Zhou Hei Ya International Holdings Company Limited produces, markets, and retails casual braised food in China. It is also involved in property holdings and management, online business, and research and development activities. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Wuhan, China.
longName: Zhou Hei Ya International Holdings Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Jujiang Construction Group Co., Ltd. provides construction contracting services for residential, commercial, industrial, and public works in the People's Republic of China. It operates through two segments, Construction Contracting and Others. It offers architecture construction contracting services; and designing, surveying, mapping, monitoring, and consulting services in the engineering of municipal management and construction, as well as sells construction materials, building materials, machinery, and metal materials. The company is also involved in the provision of engineering exploration services; installation, disassembly, and rental of construction lifting equipment; municipal public, sports facilities construction, and landscaping activities; installation of architecture wall; and manufacture and sale of civil defense products. In addition, it engages in the building and operating of youth quality education practice base. The company was formerly known as Qitang Commune Construction Agency and changed its name to Zhejiang Jujiang Holdings Group Co., Ltd. in December 2014. Jujiang Construction Group Co., Ltd. was founded in 1965 and is headquartered in Tongxiang, the People's Republic of China. Jujiang Construction Group Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of Zhejiang Jujiang Holdings Group Co., Ltd.

ICO Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides IT application services to institutions and enterprises in Hong Kong and internationally. It operates through four segments: IT Application and Solution Development, IT Infrastructure Solutions, Secondment Services, and Maintenance and Support Services. The company engages in the design and implementation of IT applications; and procurement of third party hardware and software. It also provides IT infrastructure solutions; and sells IT infrastructure solution related hardware and software. In addition, the company offers secondment services; and maintenance and support services. It serves various industries, such as banking, finance and insurance, government departments, exchanges and regulatory bodies, telecommunication, distribution and retail, logistics and media, universities and schools, construction, manufacturing, and other. ICO Group Limited was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.

LUZHENG FUTURES Company Limited, a futures company, provides brokerage services for commodity and financial futures in the People's Republic of China. The company's Futures Brokerage segment offers futures brokerage and financial futures brokering services. Its Commodity Trading and Risk Management segment offers physical commodity trading, futures trading, and over-the-counter derivatives trading. The company's Futures Asset Management segment provides portfolio management and maintenance; investment advisory; and transaction execution services. LUZHENG FUTURES Company Limited also engages in the sale and wholesale of agricultural, metal, mining, and chemical products, as well as edible oil; import and export activities; and provision of investment consultancy and risk management services. In addition, it offers software development, system integration, and information technology services, as well as sells electronic products and equipment; and registration, unified transaction payment and settlement, derivatives business clearing, warehouse receipts conversion and financing services; and financial information services. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Jinan, the People's Republic of China. LUZHENG FUTURES Company Limited is a subsidiary of Zhongtai Securities Co., Ltd.

Gold-Finance Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily provides building services in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in three segments: Investment and Asset Management Services, Property Investment and Development, and Building Services. It undertakes various engineering works, including electrical, air conditioning, and fire services installation works; and engineering projects in public and private sectors, which are related to new building development and existing building renovation. Gold-Finance Holdings Limited also provides investment and asset management, and property investment and development services. The company was formerly known as Nga Chun Holdings Company Limited and changed its name to Gold-Finance Holdings Limited in April 2016. The company was founded in 1994 and is based in Central, Hong Kong. Gold-Finance Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Gold-Finance (Hong Kong) Asset Management Limited.

Affluent Partners Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the purchase, processing, design, production, assembling, trading, and wholesale distribution of pearls and jewelry products. The company operates in two segments, Sale of Pearls and Jewellery, and Strategic Investment and Financial Services. It offers South Sea, Tahitian, and freshwater pearls; and a range of jewelry products on ODM and OEM basis. The company is also involved in real estate financial assets investment business. It has operations in Hong Kong, the United Kingdom, and the People's Republic of China. The company was formerly known as Man Sang Jewellery Holdings Limited and changed its name to Affluent Partners Holdings Limited in February 2017. Affluent Partners Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

UKF (Holdings) Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the insurance brokerage business in the People's Republic of China, Europe, and Hong Kong. It operates through Securities, Insurance Brokerage, Fur, and Other segments. The Securities segment offers securities brokerage, margin financing, underwriting, placing, and consultancy services. The Insurance brokerage segment provides insurance brokerage and wealth management services. The Fur segment engages in breeding, farming and sale of livestocks and pelted skin, fur skin brokerage, and financing services; and trading of fur skin of foxes and minks. The Other segment provides money lending services. UKF (Holdings) Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.

Get Nice Financial Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides financial services in Hong Kong. It operates through three segments: Broking, Securities Margin Financing, and Corporate Finance. The company offers securities dealing and broking, futures and options broking, and underwriting and placement services; securities margin financing; and corporate finance and advisory services. In addition, it is involved in the provision of asset management services, as well as in property and yacht holding activities. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Get Nice Financial Group Limited is a subsidiary of Get Nice Holdings Limited.

Prosper One International Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the retail and wholesale of watches in the People's Republic of China and Hong Kong. The company operates 20 retail outlets, including 11 multi-brand and 9 single brand boutique outlets. It is also involved in the sale and trading of fertilizers raw materials and related fertilizer products; and public consumption products, such as clothing and footwear, and mobile phone accessories. The company was formerly known as Tic Tac International Holdings Company Limited and changed its name to Prosper One International Holdings Company Limited in November 2017. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Prosper One International Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of Prosper One Enterprises Limited.
longName: Prosper One International Holdings Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Nissin Foods Company Limited produces and sells instant noodles in Hong Kong, the Peoples Republic of China, Canada, Australia, the United States, Taiwan, and Macau. It also produces and sells retort and frozen foods, and beverages and snacks, as well as imports, purchases, and distributes processed foods, vegetables, fruit juices, and sauces. In addition, the company manufactures packaging materials of instant noodles products; and provides administrative, human resources, and publicity services. Its brands portfolio includes NISSIN, Cup Noodles, Demae Iccho, Nupasta, Harusame, Retort Pouch, Rice Vermicelli, Mie Goreng, Donbei, UFO, Kagome, Frozen Sanuki Udon, and Fuku. The company was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Tai Po, Hong Kong. Nissin Foods Company Limited is a subsidiary of Nissin Foods Holdings Co., Ltd.

Hengtai Securities Co., Ltd provides a range of financial products and services in China. The company's Brokerage and Wealth Management segment trades in stocks, funds, bonds, and futures on behalf of the clients; and provides investment and financing solutions to high-end, professional, and institutional clients, including sale of financial products, margin financing and securities lending, and securities-backed lending. Its Investment Banking segment offers corporate finance services comprising financial advisory, equity underwriting, and debt underwriting services, as well as over-the-counter board-related services to institutional clients; and services to companies entering into National Equities Exchange and Quotations board for share quotation and transfer. The company's Proprietary Trading segment engages in trading of equities, bonds, funds, and derivatives for the group. Its Investment Management segment is involved in asset management, private equity investment, and alternative investment activities. The company is also involved in the securities investment and fund distribution, and securities sponsoring businesses; and venture capital and industrial investment businesses. In addition, it provides project investment, fund raising and management, investment advisory, and corporate management services, as well as investment, corporate management, business, and financial consulting services; and corporate asset reorganization, merger and acquisition, and marketing planning services, as well as manages equity investment funds and equity investments. The company also serves individuals and financial institutions, as well as large, small, and medium enterprises. As of December 31, 2018, the company operated 144 securities branches. Hengtai Securities Co., Ltd was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Q Technology (Group) Company Limited engages in the research and development, design, manufacture, and sale of camera and fingerprint recognition modules in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company offers high- and middle-range, and dual camera modules, as well as front facing and rear fingerprint recognition modules for the branded smart phone and tablet market. It also trades in camera modules. The company was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Kunshan, the People's Republic of China.

Yan Tat Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells printed circuit boards in Mainland China, Europe, Hong Kong, other Asian countries, North America, Africa, the Oceania, and South America. The company is also involved in the trading of printed circuit boards; and property holding business. Its products are used in cars, communication equipment, medical devices, industrial automation equipment, and consumer electronics. The company was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. Yan Tat Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Million Pearl Holdings Ltd.

U Banquet Group Holding Limited, an investment holding company, operates and franchises a chain of Chinese restaurants in Hong Kong and Mainland China. It operates through Chinese Restaurant and Wedding Business, Property Leasing Business, Securities Trading Business, and Environmental Maintenance Business segments. The company operates full-service Chinese restaurants, which offer wedding banquet and dining services, as well as catering services. It also provides environmental maintenance services, including janitorial services on streets and public areas, waste management services, and facility maintenance management. In addition, the company distributes fresh vegetables and fruit, seafood, and frozen meat; leases property; and trades in securities. As of December 31, 2018, it operated a total 10 restaurants under the U Banquet, U Kitchen, and U Pot brands. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.

C Cheng Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides architectural and building information modelling (BIM) services in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Comprehensive Architectural Services and BIM Services segments. The Comprehensive Architectural Services segment offers landscape architecture, town planning, interior design, and heritage conservation services. The BIM Services segment provides BIM consultancy, professional training, and software development services. The company also provides repair and fitting out works, as well as operates related mobile application. C Cheng Holdings Limited was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.

Best Food Holding Company Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells handbags. The company also offers backpacks and soft luggage. In addition, it provides management and administration services, as well as leasing and business services; operates Chinese fast food and hot pot restaurants chain, as well as holds properties in Thailand; and manufactures condiments. It has operations in the United States, the People's Republic of China, other Asian countries, Italy, Hong Kong, Canada, the Netherlands, other European countries, the United Kingdom, Germany, South American countries, the Middle East, and Africa. The company was formerly known as Lee & Man Handbags Holding Limited and changed its name to Best Food Holding Company Limited in October 2016. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Central, Hong Kong. Best Food Holding Company Limited is a subsidiary of Sonic Tycoon Limited.

China ZhongDi Dairy Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, operates dairy farms in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in two segments, Dairy Farming Business and Import Trading Business. It raises and breeds dairy cows; produces raw milk; and sells reproduced heifers. The company is also involved in the import and sale of cows, alfalfa hay, breeding stock, and other animal husbandry-related products, as well as the provision of import agency services. As of December 31, 2018, it owned and operated eight modern dairy farms, including Beijing ZhongDi Farm, Inner Mongolia ZhongDi Diary, Helan ZhongDi Farm, Ningxia ZhongDi Farm, Kuandian ZhongDi Farm, Langfang ZhongDi Farm, Tianzhen ZhongDi Farm, and Tianjin ZhongDi Farm. China ZhongDi Dairy Holdings Company Limited was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
longName: China ZhongDi Dairy Holdings Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Jiyi Household International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, sells and distributes building and home improvement materials and furnishings in the People's Republic of China.
