The company operates in two segments, Sale and Distribution of Merchandise, and Provision of Interior Design and Engineering Services. It offers building materials, including steel, pipes and fittings, electrical wires and cables, aluminum alloys, cement, building mortar, paint and chemicals, and glass products; home improvement materials, such as ceramics, flooring and doors, electrical materials, sanitary ware, plumbing products, and hardware and kitchen systems; and furnishings comprising lightings, furniture, textiles, electrical appliances, and home accessories. The company provides its products to customers through direct sales, tenders, and sales outlets. It has 15 sales outlets. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Meizhou, China. Jiyi Household International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Xinling Limited.

AP Rentals Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the rental of construction, electrical and mechanical (E&M) engineering, and event and entertainment equipment in Hong Kong, Macau, and Singapore. It operates through Leasing and Trading segments. The company offers equipment planning, transportation, installation, operation, refueling and maintenance, disassembly, and other technical support services, as well as various value-added services. Its rental equipment primarily comprise power and energy equipment, high-reach equipment, and material handling equipment, as well as other equipment, such as lifting, earth moving, foundation, road and transportation, tunneling, demolition, and small equipment. The company also trades and leases machinery and parts. It serves clients in the construction, E&M engineering, and event and entertainment sectors. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Tsim Sha Tsui East, Hong Kong.

PuraPharm Corporation Limited, an investment holding company, researches, develops, produces, and sells concentrated Chinese medicine granule (CCMG) and Chinese healthcare products in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, and the United States. The company operates through five segments: China CCMG, Hong Kong CCMG, Chinese Healthcare Products, Clinics, and Plantation. It offers holistic products under the PuraGold, Haveron, CardioClear, PuraPharm Lingzhi, and Arashi Kuni names; and various therapeutic products under the Nong's, Oncozac, and Immuzac names for Chinese medicine practitioners. It also provides Chinese medicine clinic management system for general clinic management; and operates Chinese medicine clinics under the Nong's name that provide Chinese medicine services and CCMG products. In addition, the company engages in the plantation and trading of raw Chinese herbs; and manufacture and sale of traditional Chinese medicine decoction pieces. Further, it researches, develops, and trades in modernized Chinese medicines; and provides Chinese medical consultation services. The company sells its products to hospitals, pharmacy chain stores, individual pharmacy stores, and medicine practitioners, as well as operates an online store. As of December 31, 2018, the company operated 62 Nong's clinics in Hong Kong and 2 Nong's clinics in China. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. PuraPharm Corporation Limited is a subsidiary of Fullgold Development Limited.

LEAP Holdings Group Limited, an investment holding company, primarily provides construction, engineering, and project management services for private sector in Hong Kong. It operates through Foundation Works and Ancillary Services, Construction Wastes Handling, Money Lending, and Investments in Securities segments. The company provides site formation, excavation and lateral support, piling construction, pile caps or footing construction, and reinforced concrete structure works; and ancillary services, such as hoarding and demolition works, as well as leases machinery. It also operates and manages public fill reception facilities, including public fill banks and temporary construction waste sorting facilities for construction and demolition materials; invests in securities; and lends money. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong. LEAP Holdings Group Limited is a subsidiary of OKC Holdings Corporation.

In Construction Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in construction and engineering activities in Hong Kong. The company undertakes foundation works and related works, including demolition, site formation, ground investigation field, and general building works. It serves building and construction industries. The company was formerly known as Crownland Construction Limited. In Construction Holdings Limited was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong.

China Reinsurance (Group) Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a reinsurance company in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company operates through Property and Casualty Reinsurance, Life and Health Reinsurance, Primary Property and Casualty Insurance, and Asset Management segments. It offers reinsurance products, including motor, commercial and household property, agricultural, liability, engineering, cargo, marine hull, specialty, credit, life, health, accident, etc.; and insurance products, such as motor, property, liability, etc. It also provides asset management, insurance brokerage, risk evaluation and management, underwriting agency, and investment management services; manages insurance funds; invests in private equities, debts/debt investment plans/trusts, equities; and issues bonds. In addition, the company is involved in the e-commerce business. It offers its insurance products for individual and corporate customers. The company was founded in 1949 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China. China Reinsurance (Group) Corporation is a subsidiary of Central Huijin Investment Ltd.

Harmonicare Medical Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates obstetrics and gynecology hospitals that provide inpatient and outpatient healthcare services. The company operates through Specialized Hospital Services, and Supply of Pharmaceuticals and Medical Devices Business segments. It also provides dental and medical beauty services, general outpatient, neonatal intensive care, infant hospitalization, breast milk nutritional analysis, intellectual evaluation and growth guidance, physical examination and assessment, maternity, and other personalized services, as well as operates child health clinics. In addition, the company supplies pharmaceuticals and medical devices. It operates its hospitals under the Harmonicare brand. As of December 31, 2017, the company owned and operated 13 hospitals in 9 first-tier and second-tier cities primarily in the People's Republic of China. Harmonicare Medical Holdings Limited was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Livzon Pharmaceutical Group Inc. engages in the research, development, production, and distribution of pharmaceutical products in the People's Republic of China. Its products primarily include Chinese and Western drug preparation products, such as Shengqi Fuzheng injection, a series of bismuth potassium citrate granules products, anti-viral granules, Urofollitropin for injection, Menotropins for injection, Ilaprazole enteric coated tablets, Voriconazole for injection, mouse nerve growth factor for injection, and Leuprorelin acetate microspheres for injection. The company's products also comprise bulk medicines and intermediates, including Pravastatin, Salinomycin, Mevastatin, Colistin, Phenylalanine, Ceftriaxone Sodium, Cefuroxime Sodium, and Cefodizime Sodium; and diagnostic reagent products, such as ELISA HIV testing reagent, MYCOII testing reagent, and TPPA testing reagent. In addition, the company provides chemical drugs, biochemical drugs, microbiological preparations, and antibiotics; polypeptide bulk medicines; human menopausal gonadotropin and human chorionic gonadotropin medicines; Omeprazole Sodium for injection; Ranitidine Bismuth Citrate tablets; Valaciclovir Hydrochloride tablets; Fluvoxamine Maleate tablet; and Perospirone Hydrochloride tablets. Further, it offers specialist bulk medicines and intermediates, as well as diagnostic reagents and equipment. Livzon Pharmaceutical Group Inc. was founded in 1985 and is based in Zhuhai, China.

China Resources Medical Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides general healthcare, and hospital management and consulting services in the People's Republic of China. The company also engages in group purchasing organization business and other hospital-derived services. In addition, it manages third-party hospitals and clinics under the invest-operate-transfer (IOT) model. In addition, it is involved in supply chain business, including the sale of pharmaceuticals, medical devices, and medical consumables and equipment. The company was formerly known as China Resources Phoenix Healthcare Holdings Company Limited and changed its name to China Resources Medical Holdings Company Limited in October 2018. The company was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
longName: China Resources Medical Holdings Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: New Century Healthcare Holding Co. Limited, an investment holding company, provides healthcare services to women and children in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in the healthcare industry specializing in pediatric, obstetric, and gynecologic services; and hospital consulting services. It operates six hospitals under the New Century Healthcare brand; and three clinics in Beijing. The company also offers marketing services; and operates canteens, and gift and groceries shops at its hospitals. New Century Healthcare Holding Co. Limited was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
longName: New Century Healthcare Holding Co. Limited

longBusinessSummary: CEFC Hong Kong Financial Investment Company Limited, an investment holding company, designs, manufactures, and trades in apparels in the United States, Canada, Hong Kong, and internationally. The company provides its products under private labels and own brands. It also provides designing, marketing, and advertising services; and money lending services. The company was formerly known as Runway Global Holdings Company Limited and changed its name to CEFC Hong Kong Financial Investment Company Limited in October 2017. CEFC Hong Kong Financial Investment Company Limited was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong.
longName: CEFC Hong Kong Financial Investment Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Frontage Holdings Corporation, a contract research organization, provides laboratory and related services to pharmaceutical and agrochemical companies, as well as bioequivalence studies in the United States and China. The company provides laboratory services that support drug discovery and development, such as drug metabolism and pharmacokinetics, safety and toxicology, and bioanalytical services, as well as chemistry, manufacturing, and controls; agrochemical services; and associated services supporting clinical studies, including early stage clinical and biometrics services. Frontage Holdings Corporation was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Exton, Pennsylvania. Frontage Holdings Corporation is a subsidiary of Hong Kong Tigermed Co., Limited.

BII Railway Transportation Technology Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, designs, implements, sells, and maintains application solutions in the People's Republic of China. The company's Intelligent Railway Transportation Services segment designs, tests, installs, debugs, integrates, upgrades, and replaces railway transportation application solutions and related systems; sells self-developed software products relating to railway transportation application solutions; sells hardware and spare parts relating to railway transportation application solution systems; and repairs and maintains application solution systems. Its products include network-level and Auto Fare Collection (AFC) route-level systems, including AFC systems, such as AFC Clearing Center, Automatic Fare Collection Network Control Centre, and Coordination and Command Centre systems; Passenger Info Systems (PIS), such as ground PIS and on-board PIS; and Environmental monitoring systems, as well as hardware and spare parts. The company's Civil Communication Transmission Services segment offers communication information transmission services to mobile operators. Its Business Development Investment segment manages the equity investments in railway transportation areas; and provides intelligent railway transportation systems related to the PIS, security and protection systems, and civil communication transmission systems. The company also leases civil communication transmission systems to telecommunication companies. The company was formerly known as China City Railway Transportation Technology Holdings Company Limited and changed its name to BII Railway Transportation Technology Holdings Company Limited in August 2017. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China. BII Railway Transportation Technology Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of Beijing Infrastructure Investment (Hong Kong) Limited.
longName: BII Railway Transportation Technology Holdings Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Plover Bay Technologies Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, markets, and sells software defined wide area network (SD-WAN) routers worldwide. It also provides software licences, and warranty and support services. The company markets and sells its products under the Peplink and Pepwave brands through a network of approximately 500 third party distributors, resellers, and system integrators. In addition, it is involved in property holding activities. The company serves public safety, retail, transportation, maritime, healthcare, machine-to-machine, education, hospitality, utilities/construction, and broadcasting markets. Plover Bay Technologies Limited was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Lai Chi Kok, Hong Kong.

Rici Healthcare Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates general hospitals, specialty hospitals, medical examination centers, and clinics in the People's Republic of China. It provides healthcare services in the areas of gynecology, obstetrics, pediatrics, postpartum rehabilitation, and obstetrics. As of December 31, 2018, it had 55 medical examination centers. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.

Zhejiang Tengy Environmental Technology Co., Ltd, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the design, development, manufacture, installation, and sale of environmental pollution prevention equipment and electronic products in Mainland China and internationally. The company offers electrostatic precipitators, bag filter precipitators, electrostatic-bag composite precipitators, and wet electrostatic precipitators. Its precipitators are installed at coal-fired power plants, metallurgical plants, paper mills, and other industrial production plants. The company also offers installation services. Its customers include project owners of power plants and industrial production plants, or contractors who undertake the construction work of power plants and industrial production plants. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Zhuji, China. Zhejiang Tengy Environmental Technology Co., Ltd is a subsidiary of Tengy Group Limited.
longName: Zhejiang Tengy Environmental Technology Co., Ltd

longBusinessSummary: Red Star Macalline Group Corporation Ltd. operates and manages home improvement and furnishings shopping malls. The company operates its shopping malls under the Red Star Macalline brand name. As of December 31, 2018, it operated a network of 308 shopping malls, including 80 portfolio shopping malls with a total operating area of 6,918,993 square meters (sq.m.); and 228 managed shopping malls with a total operating area of 12,020,347 sq.m. offering approximately 24,000 brands across 199 cities in 29 provinces, municipalities, and autonomous regions in the People's Republic of China. The company also engages in the leasing of floor areas to the tenants; retail sale of home furnishing merchandise, as well as provision of related decorating services; sale of pre-paid cards; and O2O platform business. In addition, it offers Internet home decoration, Internet retail, and logistics and delivery services; joint marketing; and shopping mall design, construction, consultation, and home design and decoration services, as well as construction site coordination and supervision services. Red Star Macalline Group Corporation Ltd. has a strategic cooperation agreement with Alibaba (China) Network Technology Co., Ltd. The company was formerly known as Shanghai Red Star Macalline Home Living and Decorating Company Limited and changed its name to Red Star Macalline Group Corporation Ltd. in 2011. The company was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China. Red Star Macalline Group Corporation Ltd. is a subsidiary of Red Star Macalline Holding Group Company Limited.
longName: Red Star Macalline Group Corporation Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: 3SBio Inc. develops, manufactures, markets, and sells biopharmaceuticals. The company provides TPIAO, a recombinant human thrombopoietin for chemotherapy-induced thrombopenia and immune thrombocytopenia; Ruisiyi, a non-steroidal aromatase inhibitor for breast cancer; EPIAO and SEPO recombinant human erythropoietins to treat anemia; Wanwei, a 5-HT3 receptor antagonist antiemetic drug for vomiting; and Intefen, a recombinant human interferon to treat lymphatic or hematopoietic malignancies and viral infections. It also offers Inleusin, a recombinant human interleukin2 for the treatment of renal cell carcinoma, melanoma, and thoracic fluid build-up; Etanercept, a recombinant human type II tumor necrosis factor receptor for rheumatoid arthritis, ankylosing spondylitis, and psoriasis; BYETTA for the glycemic control in patients with type 2 diabetes; and SPARIN, an injectable low-molecular-weight heparin calcium for the treatment of prophylaxis and deep vein thrombosis, as well as for the prevention of clotting during hemodialysis. In addition, the company provides Mandi for the treatment of male-pattern alopecia and alopecia areata; Aiyishu to treat iron-deficiency anemia; Qiming Keli for retinopathy caused by type-2 diabetes; Disu, a bidirectional immunomodulator for the prevention and treatment of chronic bronchitis, cold, and asthma; Jiannipai, a recombinant humanized anti-CD25 monoclonal antibody injection to prevent acute rejection after renal transplantation; and Humulin, a recombinant insulin for diabetes. Further, the company engages in the contract development and manufacturing, trading, project management and consultation, and provision of technology services activities. It has collaboration agreements with Toray Industries, Inc.; Refuge Biotechnologies, Inc.; Samsung Bioepis Co., Ltd.; Verseau Therapeutics, Inc.; and Taiwan Liposome Company, Ltd. 3SBio Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Shenyang, the People's Republic of China.

China Partytime Culture Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, produces, markets, and sells cosplay products and lingerie in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Wigs, and Clothing and Others segments. It offers roleplaying products, which include party costumes and roleplaying clothes, and wigs inspired by animation characters comprising popular animation, comics, cartoon, traditional fairy tale, movies, games, and party, as well as Halloween, Christmas, and holiday themes. The company markets its products under the Party Time, Secret Temptations, and Styler brand names. China Partytime Culture Holdings Limited also exports its products to approximately 30 countries and regions, including the United States, Germany, the United Kingdom, and Australia. The company was formerly known as China Animation Culture Group Holding Co., Ltd. and changed its name to China Partytime Culture Holdings Limited in April 2015. China Partytime Culture Holdings Limited was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Yichun, the People's Republic of China.

Lanzhou Zhuangyuan Pasture Co., Ltd. manufactures, markets, and sells dairy products in China. The company operates through two segments, Dairy Farming and Dairy Products Production. It offers liquid milk products comprising pasteurized milk, ultra high temperature milk, modified milk, yogurt, and other dairy products; and milk beverage products. The company markets its products to retail chains, supermarkets, and local schools through distributors, sales agents, and direct sale. Lanzhou Zhuangyuan Pasture Co., Ltd. was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Lanzhou, the People's Republic of China.

Yuk Wing Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, manufactures, and trades in down-the-hole (DTH) rock drilling tools in Hong Kong. The company operates through Manufacturing and Trading of DTH Rockdrilling Tools; Trading of Piling and Drilling Machineries; and Trading of Rockdrilling Equipment segments. It offers DTH hammers, casing systems, button bits and bit openers, drill pipes, cluster drills, and casing tubes; and technical rock drilling solutions. Its products are used in mining and quarrying, and building foundation and piling on construction sites. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong. Yuk Wing Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Colour Shine Investments Limited.

Zhong Ao Home Group Limited operates as an independent property management company in the People's Republic of China. Its Property Management business offers property management, consulting, and ancillary services to the residential properties, and commercial and government buildings. It serves property developers and owners. The company's Sale Assistance business provides cleaning, security, and maintenance services for model homes and sales centers of property developers; and general assistance to facilitate the sales process of the properties. Its Other businesses provides installation, repairing, and maintenance services primarily to the elevators of the properties under management; light-current engineering services to properties under management; and catering services, as well as operates canteens in government buildings. The company also engages in the sale of engineering spare parts to the elevator servicing companies. Zhong Ao Home Group Limited was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, the People's Republic of China. Zhong Ao Home Group Limited is a subsidiary of Qichang International Limited.

Synergy Group Holdings International Limited, an investment holding company, primarily engages in the trade of energy saving products. The company operates through Leasing Service of Energy Saving Systems, Trading of Energy Saving Products, Consultancy Service, and Building AI (Artificial Intelligence) SaaS segments. Its AI technology services include one-stop building operating system for building data acquisition, real-time monitoring, energy, and environment optimization through big data analytics and machine learning for building digital transformation. The company also provides energy management systems solutions; and leases and maintains cooling systems. It operates in Hong Kong, Japan, Australia, Malaysia, Indonesia, Singapore, Macau, and internationally. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in North Point, Hong Kong.

Left Field Printing Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides printing solutions and services in Australia. Its printing process and services include printing solution consultation, production planning and scheduling, pre-press, offset printing, digital printing, post-press, quality check, and packaging and delivery. The company's printed products comprise read-for-pleasure books, government printed matters, quick turnaround time education books, catalogues, operating manuals, and promotional leaflets. It also provides printing related services, such as warehousing and direct mailing, and call center and ancillary services through IPALM platform. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in North Point, Hong Kong. Left Field Printing Group Limited is a subsidiary of Lion Rock Group Limited.

Guangdong Join-Share Financing Guarantee Investment Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, provides credit-based financing solutions to small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) for their financing and business needs in the People's Republic of China. It operates in two segments, Guarantees and SME Lending. The Guarantees segment offers financing guarantees, such as indirect and direct financing guarantees; and non-financing guarantees, including attachment bonds, construction contract bonds, and other contract bonds. It also provides debt financing, internal control, and risk management related consulting services to the guarantee customers. This segment offers guarantees on behalf of SMEs and individual business proprietors. The SME Lending segment provides loans and related financing consulting services to the small and medium sized and micro enterprises (SME enterprises) or the owners of SME enterprises; and micro-lending to SMEs, individual business proprietors, and individuals. The company also offers investment and consulting services; and microcredit, supply chain, and factoring services. Guangdong Join-Share Financing Guarantee Investment Co., Ltd. was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Foshan, China.
longName: Guangdong Join-Share Financing Guarantee Investment Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: Design Capital Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the furniture business. Its U.S. Furniture Sales segment sources and sells furniture products under the Target Marketing Systems, TMS, Simple Living, and Lifestorey brands through third party e-commerce platforms in the United States. The company's Furniture Sales segment operates seven points of sale that offers furniture products under the Marquis, Lifestorey, and OM brands; and furniture sourcing services. Its Interior Design segment offers project-based interior design, fitting-out, and design consultancy services for showflats of residential property development projects and individual residential units in Singapore, Malaysia, and Brunei. The company was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Singapore.

Thelloy Development Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides building construction services primarily in Hong Kong. The company also offers repair, maintenance, alternation, and addition work services, as well as operates as a contractor for public works. It primarily serves government, quasi-government organizations, universities, schools, institutions, and incorporated owners of private buildings. The company was founded in 1982 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. Thelloy Development Group Limited is a subsidiary of Cheers Mate Holding Limited.

IBI Group Holdings Limited, a building contractor, provides renovation services for property projects in the private sector in Hong Kong and Macau. It offers interior fit-outs and building refurbishments, and alteration and addition projects, as well as a range of other building professional services. The company serves organizations and commercial enterprises, including multi-national banks, hotels and casino operators, racing and betting operators, and property developers. IBI Group Holdings Limited was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.

Genscript Biotech Corporation, an investment holding company, engages in the manufacture and sale of life sciences research products and services in North America, Europe, China, Japan, the other Asia Pacific regions, and internationally. It operates in four segments: Bio-Science Services and Products, Biologics Development Services, Industrial Synthetic Biology Products, and Cell Therapy. The Bio-Science Services and Products segment provides research services in various categories, including gene synthesis and molecular cloning, oligonucleotide synthesis, protein production, peptide synthesis, and antibody development for use in basic biology studies, disease and pharmaceutical research, drug discovery, agriculture, environmental studies, and food industry; life sciences research catalogue products, such as pre-packaged, ready-to-use, and off-the-shelf products; and contractual research services, including protein engineering. The Biologics Development Services segment provides various services, such as antibody drug discovery, antibody drug pre-clinical and clinical development, plasmid and virus pre-clinical development, and plasmid and virus clinical development for antibody therapeutic antibodies and gene/cell therapy products. The Industrial Synthetic Biology Products segment constructs non-pathogenic microbial strains; and develops and produces industrial enzymes. The Cell Therapy segment discovers and develops therapies for the treatment of liquid tumors. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Nanjing, China. Genscript Biotech Corporation is a subsidiary of GenScript Corporation.

Ever Harvest Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides sea freight transportation and freight forwarding services in the People's Republic of China. It offers feeder shipping, carrier owned container, and sea freight forwarding agency services, as well as feeder rental and freight forwarding consulting services. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong.

Guangzhou Rural Commercial Bank Co., Ltd. provides banking and related financial products and services. It operates through four segments: Corporate Banking, Retail Banking, Financial Market Business, and Others. The company offers personal deposits, including demand, call, time, and fixed deposits; personal cheques; personal consumption and mortgage loans; credit cards; and personal finance products. It also provides institutional call, agreement, time, and demand deposits; corporate financing and credit, such as house development, project, working capital, commercial property mortgage, and fixed asset project loans; international payment and remittance services; and intermediary, trade, and SME financing services. In addition, the company offers investment banking services; short, medium, and long term loans; and domestic and international settlements, and bill acceptance and discounting services. Further, it provides money market placements, investments and repurchasing, and foreign exchange transaction services; inter-bank placements; debit and credit cards; payment collection and insurance agency, safe locker, advisory, and attestation services; and agency services for issuing/redemption and underwriting of government bonds. Additionally, the company trades in government and financial bonds; engages in bill, fixed-income, wealth management, and institutional banking activities; and provides Internet, telephone, SMS, mobile, WeChat, self-service, and VTM banking services. As of December 31, 2018, it had a total of 631 outlets, including 619 outlets in Guangzhou; 5 branches in Foshan, Qingyuan, Heyuan, Zhaoquing, and Zhuhai, Guangdong province; and 2,170 automated teller machines, as well as 801 self-service inquiry terminals. The company was formerly known as Guangzhou Rural Credit Cooperative Unions and changed its name to Guangzhou Rural Commercial Bank Co., Ltd. The company was founded in 1951 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Guangzhou Rural Commercial Bank Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: MIE Holdings Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, primarily explores, develops, produces, and sells crude oil, gas, and other petroleum products under production sharing contracts in North America and the People's Republic of China. It holds interests in the Daan project that covers an area of 62,518 acres located in the Songliao Basin of DaanJilin Province; South China Sea PY10-4 project that covers an area of 16,700 acres located in the middle of the Pearl River Mouth Basin; and Emir-Oil project that covers an area of 11,100 acres located in the Mangshrak Basin in west Kazakhstan. As of December 31, 2018, the company operated a total of 2,392 wells. It also has net proved oil and gas reserves of approximately 213 million barrels of oil equivalents (BOE); net proved and probable oil and gas reserves of 339 million BOE; and net proved, probable, and possible oil and gas reserves of 366 million BOE. The company is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

Chinney Kin Wing Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in foundation construction and drilling, and site investigation works for public and private sectors in Hong Kong and internationally. It operates in two segments, Foundation Construction and Ancillary Services; and Drilling and Site Investigation. The company offers piling construction services, such as bored piling, percussive H-piling, socketed H-piling, mini-piling, and sheet piling; other ancillary services comprising ELS works, site formation, and pile cap construction; and drilling and site investigation, and related ground engineering construction services. It also offers equipment and machinery leasing and construction material testing services. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Chinney Kin Wing Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Chinney Alliance Group Limited.

YiChang HEC ChangJiang Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd. develops, manufactures, and sells pharmaceutical products in the therapeutic areas of anti-virus, endocrine and metabolic diseases, and cardiovascular diseases in the People's Republic of China. The company offers its products in the form of capsules and granules. Its principal products include Kewei, an anti-influenza virus product; Ertongshu, a medicine for treatment of excess level of uric acids and gouts; Oumeining for the treatment and prevention of hypertension; Xinhaining for the treatment and prevention of hypertension and chest pains, as well as the treatment of artery diseases; and Xining, a generic drug for the treatment of hay fever, allergies, colds, and swelling. The company sells its products to hospitals and medical institutions through a network of distributors. YiChang HEC ChangJiang Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd. has a strategic cooperative partnership with China National Accord Medicines Corporation Ltd.; and a strategic agreement with Lannett Company, Inc. The company was formerly known as Yichang Changjiang Pharmaceutical Company Limited and changed its name to YiChang HEC ChangJiang Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd. in May 2015. The company was founded in 2001 and is based in Yichang, China. YiChang HEC ChangJiang Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of Guangdong HEC Technology Holding Co., Ltd.
longName: YiChang HEC ChangJiang Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: Kwan On Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the construction and maintenance works on civil engineering contracts in Hong Kong. The company undertakes works related to buildings, waterworks, site formation, roads, drainage, and slopes upgrading services. It is also involved in the provision of contracting work on civil plumbing, fire protection, insulation, concrete repair, and related activities; property holding activities; and construction site workmen services, as well as the trade of diesel. The company was founded in 1975 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.

Star Properties Group (Cayman Islands) Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the property development and investment activities in Hong Kong. It also offers property management and financing services to the property buyers. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. Star Properties Group (Cayman Islands) Limited is a subsidiary of Star Properties Holdings (BVI) Limited.

International Alliance Financial Leasing Co., Ltd., an investment holding company, provides finance leasing and advisory services in the People's Republic of China. The company offers direct finance leasing and sale-leaseback services; and advisory services, including industry analysis, suggestions for optimizing financial management, and advice on financing options. It serves the healthcare, aviation, and public infrastructure industries. The company was formerly known as Nanshan International Alliance Financial Leasing Co., Ltd. International Alliance Financial Leasing Co., Ltd. was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.
longName: International Alliance Financial Leasing Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: Virscend Education Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides K-12 private education services in the People's Republic of China. It operates schools for grades K-12, which include Chengdu Foreign Languages School, Chengdu Experimental Foreign Languages School, Chengdu Experimental Foreign Languages School (Western Campus), the Primary School Attached to Chengdu Foreign Languages School, and Kindergarten of the Primary School attached to Chengdu Jinniu District Foreign Languages School. The company also operates Chengdu Institute Sichuan International Studies University; and offers elementary school education services. As of December 31, 2018, it had an enrollment of approximately 45,802 students, which included 29,415 students in K-12 schools and 16,387 students in the university. Virscend Education Company Limited was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Chengdu, the People's Republic of China.

China Animation Characters Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the sales of animation derivative products, establishment and operation of indoor theme parks, and multimedia animation entertainment businesses in the People's Republic of China, Japan, and Hong Kong. It trades in animation derivative products, including general plastic toys and food-grade toys; and provides value-added services, such as quality control and advice on product design. The company also offers animation games comprising HanBaGui, Violet, virtual reality (VR) games, and mobile games, as well as an online game; and owns movies and animated dramas, such as The King of Tibetan Antelope, Project Egg, Animal Conference on the Environment, and Amazing UU. In addition, it establishes and operates three indoor interactive entertainment parks and an indoor children playground; and designs animation derivative products. The company was formerly known as China Animation Group (Holding) Limited and changed its name to China Animation Characters Company Limited in February 2015. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. China Animation Characters Company Limited is a subsidiary of Bright Rise Enterprises Limited.

Sundart Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides fitting-out services in the People's Republic of China. The company undertakes fitting-out works for hotels, serviced apartments, residential properties, and other properties; and alteration, addition, and construction and civil engineering works. It also manufactures, sources, and distributes interior decorative materials; and leases intellectual properties. In addition, the company provides project management and consultancy services. Further, it manufactures interior decorative timber products, such as fire-rated timber doors and wooden furniture. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. Sundart Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Reach Glory International Limited.

Minsheng Education Group Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides educational services in the People's Republic of China. The company operates six higher education schools, two secondary vocational schools, and two high schools. It also provides education management and services; disease diagnosis and treatment services; university and college logistics services; rental and business management services; investment management and services; education consulting and management services; and asset management, and project investment and management services. In addition, the company invests in education projects, as well as develops real estate properties. Minsheng Education Group Company Limited was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China. Minsheng Education Group Company Limited is a subsidiary of Minsheng Group Company Limited.

Weiye Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, develops residential and commercial properties. It operates in two segments, Property Development and Equipment Manufacturing. The company also constructs resettlement houses and leases investment properties. In addition, it manufactures, trades in, and wholesales heating, ventilation, air-conditioning, air purification, and clean room equipment, including fan filter units, air showers, clean booths, pass boxes, clean hand dryers, clean benches, deflection grilles, and air diffusers. Further, the company trades in building construction materials; provides property management services; and offers logistics management, ancillary, technology consultation and transfer, and after-sales services, as well as agency services. Additionally, it imports and exports industrial products. The company operates in the People's Republic of China, Singapore, and internationally. Weiye Holdings Limited was incorporated in 1984 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, China.

Xin Point Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells automotive and electronic components in the People's Republic of China, North America, Europe, and internationally. The company offers automotive interior decorative components, such as interior door handles, door trims, shifter bezels, steering wheel components, console parts, and cluster rings; and exterior decorative components, including emblems, exterior door handles, fog lamp trims, front grill trims, tail lamp trims, and wheel hub trims. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Huizhou, the People's Republic of China.

China Art Financial Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as an art finance service provider in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through two segments, Art and Asset Pawn Business, and Art and Asset Auction Business. It provides pawn loan services secured by artworks and assets as collaterals. The company's artwork collateral portfolio primarily includes zisha artworks, as well as paintings and calligraphies, and jewel artworks. In addition, it provides online art auction services. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Yixing, the People's Republic of China. China Art Financial Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Intelligenesis Investment Co. Ltd.
address1: Northern side of Jiefang East Road

longBusinessSummary: Southern Energy Holdings Group Limited engages in the extraction and sale of anthracite coal in the People's Republic of China. The company offers big lump coal, medium lump coal, clean coal, and fine coal. It operates four coal mines located in Bijie City, Guizhou Province. The company's coal products are used as chemical coal and PCI coal, as well as for further value-added applications, such as premium quality active charcoal. The company was formerly known as China Unienergy Group Limited and changed its name to Southern Energy Holdings Group Limited in December 2018. Southern Energy Holdings Group Limited was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Guiyang, China.

Morris Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, manufactures, and sells upholstered sofa, sofa covers, and other furniture products in the People's Republic of China. It offers stationary sofas and motion sofas, as well as sofas with smart home features, such as audio, massage, beverage cooling, Bluetooth, and USB port connections. The company offers its products under Morrisofa brand name through its flagship stores. It also exports its products to the United States, Canada, the United Kingdom, and Australia. Morris Holdings Limited was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Haining, the People's Republic of China.

Qilu Expressway Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, operates as an expressway operator in the People's Republic of China. The company constructs, maintains, operates, and manages the Jihe Expressway that has a total length of approximately 153.6 kilometers, which runs from Jinan City to Heze City in Shandong Province. It also produces and distributes outdoor advertising. The company was formerly known as Shandong Jihe Expressway Company Limited. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Jinan, the People's Republic of China. Qilu Expressway Company Limited is a subsidiary of Qilu Transportation Development Group Company Limited.

Quanzhou Huixin Micro-credit Co., Ltd., a microfinance company, provides various short-term financing solutions in the People's Republic of China. The company offers revolving credit facilities, joint-guaranteed loans, targeted payment loans, bridge loans, and collateralized quick-access loans. It serves entrepreneurial individuals, small and medium-sized enterprises, and microenterprises. The company also provides investment advisory and financial leasing services. Quanzhou Huixin Micro-credit Co., Ltd. was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Quanzhou, the People's Republic of China.

Bank of Tianjin Co., Ltd. provides banking products and services primarily in Tianjin municipality, the People's Republic of China. It operates through Corporate Banking, Personal Banking, and Treasury Operations segments. The Corporate Banking segment offers deposit taking, corporate loan, trade financing, and other types of corporate intermediary services to corporations, government agencies, and financial institutions. The Personal Banking segment provides deposit products, personal loans, cards, personal wealth management services, and other types of personal intermediary services to individual customers. The Treasury Operations segment is involved in debt instruments investment activities; and offers money market, foreign exchange, precious metal, and derivatives transactions services. As at December 31, 2018, Bank of Tianjin Co., Ltd. had a total of 14 tier-one branches. The company was formerly known as Tianjin City Cooperative Bank Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Bank of Tianjin Co., Ltd. in February 2007. Bank of Tianjin Co., Ltd. was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Tianjin, China.

Yihai International Holding Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, researches, develops, manufactures, distributes, and sells hot pot soup flavoring, hot pot dipping sauce, and Chinese style compound condiment products under Haidilao brand. It offers sour tomato, spicy clear oil, clear oil, butter, mellow butter, clear oil slag-free, and handmade butter hot pot bottom materials; fresh fragrant and seafood clear hot pot soups; and fresh flavor, spicy, and original hot pot sauces, as well as oatmeal green pepper, and red onion and soy sauces. The company also provides spicy, flavored, garlic, boiled fish, soup pickled fish, three pepper spicy fish, spicy incense pot, fresh oil spicy hot, and halal spicy seasonings; and pickled sour soup with fish sauce. In addition, it offers various hot pot course, which includes spicy tender beef boiled, tomato burdock self-cooking, crispy beef belly boiled, spicy vegetarian self-cooking, scented curry self-cooking, tomato small crispy meat boiled, spicy assorted vegetables, vine pepper flavored assorted vegetables, chicken mixed with hot and sour powder boiled, and bean sprouts meet hot and sour powder boiled hot pot courses. Further, the company offers self-serving small hot pot products, and consulting services. It provides its products through distributors to hypermarkets, supermarkets, grocery stores, neighborhood stores, and butcher shops, as well as e-commerce channels covering approximately 31 provincial regions of China, as well as the Hong Kong, Macau, and Taiwan regions; and 42 international countries and markets. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China. Yihai International Holding Ltd. is a subsidiary of ZYSP YIHAI Ltd.

Da Sen Holdings Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells plywood products and biomass wood pellets in the People's Republic of China. It offers furniture board, ecological plywood, and hardwood multi-layered board, which are used as materials for interior decoration or furniture making; and produces biomass wood pellets fuel using wood residues to generate energy. The company offers its products to furniture manufacturers, equipment manufacturers, decoration or renovation companies, and packing material producers, as well as trading companies. The company was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Heze, the People's Republic of China.

Progressive Path Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the construction works, construction machinery rental, and construction machinery trading businesses. It undertakes various construction projects, such as the foundation and site formation, builder's, and general building works. The company is also involved in the trade and rental of construction machineries and vehicles, as well as provision of machine operator and transportation services. It serves the construction work companies operating in public and/or private construction projects. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Tuen Mun, Hong Kong. Progressive Path Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Profit Gold Global Limited.

CR Construction Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a building contractor in Hong Kong. The company provides building construction, as well as repair, maintenance, addition, and alteration work services. It serves public and private sectors. The company was founded in 1967 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. CR Construction Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of CR Construction Investments Limited.

Qinqin Foodstuffs Group (Cayman) Company Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures, distributes, and sells food and snacks in the People's Republic of China. It operates through four segments: Jelly Products, Crackers and Chips, Seasoning Products, and Confectionery and Other Products. The company offers jelly, puffed, baking, seasoning, seaweed, and other leisure food products, as well as candies and drinks primarily under the Qinqin, Shangerry, and Xiang Ge Li brands. It is also involved in trading and online trading activities. The company was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Jinjiang, China.

Yadea Group Holdings Ltd., an investment holding company, researches, develops, manufactures, distributes, and sells electric vehicles and related accessories in the People's Republic of China. The company offers electric two-wheeled vehicles, including electric scooters and electric bicycles; and electric tricycle. It also provides batteries and chargers, as well as other electric two-wheeled vehicles parts; and manufactures industrial products. The company exports its products in approximately 70 countries. Yadea Group Holdings Ltd. was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Wuxi, the People's Republic of China.

China Leon Inspection Holding Limited, an investment holding company, provides testing and inspection services of coal and coke in the People's Republic of China. The company offers testing and inspection services of minerals; and witnessing and ancillary services to prevent dishonest or abnormal activities in the testing and transportation of coal and ensure the contractual compliance of the weight of coal carried on rail, truck or conveying belt, or shipping conditions of the cargo. It also provides coal inspection technique advisory; inspection, testing, appraisal, and inspection technology development; vector biological control; chemical product wholesale and retail; software development; computer and equipment; product quality, control, inspection, evaluation supervision, testing, and relevant technique; professional technique; and scientific research, technique, and business services, as well as inspection and testing of commodities. China Leon Inspection Holding Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Shineroad International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, distributes food ingredients and additives in the People's Republic of China. It serves food ingredients and additives processing companies, manufacturers, and trading companies. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Shanghai, China.

Chanjet Information Technology Company Limited provides software and other related services to micro and small scale enterprises (MSEs) in Mainland China. The company offers cloud services, including Chanjet Good Accountant, an artificial intelligence technology based financial application; T+ Cloud enterprise management services; Chanjet Good Business that provides online and offline marketing and transaction management services for MSEs in trade and commerce; Biz Chat; and Chanjet Easy Accounting Agent. It is also involved in the technical development, consulting, transfer, service, and training of computer software, hardware, and external devices; sale of typing paper, computer consumables, computer software, and hardware and external devices; provision of database services and information services of the second category value-added telecom business; and design, manufacturing, agency, and publication of advertisements. The company was formerly known as Chanjet Software Company Limited. Chanjet Information Technology Company Limited was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Beijing, China. Chanjet Information Technology Company Limited is a subsidiary of Yonyou Network Technology Co., Ltd.

China Logistics Property Holdings Co., Ltd, an investment holding company, designs, develops, leases, and manages logistics facilities in the People's Republic of China. It develops and constructs storage facilities; and provides investment management, warehouse and house leasing, project investment, enterprise management consulting, cargo agency and transportation consulting, stowage loading and unloading and related business advisory, property development and management, landscape engineering, business information consulting, marketing planning, and enterprise image design services. The company also leases self-owned buildings; sells building materials; manufactures and sells automobile components and parts, steel structure, painted metal and other metals, and logistics and mechanical equipment; imports and exports goods and technology; and develops e-commerce technology. In addition, it is involved in flowers, seedling, and fruit trees planting activities. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Shanghai, China.
longName: China Logistics Property Holdings Co., Ltd

longBusinessSummary: Shun Wo Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a foundation works contractor in Hong Kong. It undertakes excavation and lateral support, socketed H-piling and mini-piling, and pile caps construction works. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Sai Wan Ho, Hong Kong. Shun Wo Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of May City Holdings Limited.
address1: Flat A, Sai Wan Ho Plaza

longBusinessSummary: Anchorstone Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the supply and installation of marble and granite in Hong Kong. The company undertakes marble and granite works for a range of building and property types, including commercial buildings, residential buildings, hotels, and public infrastructures. It also sells stones, such as marble and granite on project and wholesale basis. The company was founded in 1991 and is based in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong. Anchorstone Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of PMG Investments Limited.

Hebei Yichen Industrial Group Corporation Limited provides rail fastening systems to the railway industry in the People's Republic of China. The company offers high speed rail fastening system, metro series, traditional track series, and heavy haul railway series products, as well as flux cored wire products to the shipbuilding industry. It primarily sells its flux cored wire products through direct sales and e-commerce platforms. The company also manufactures and sells welding materials; trades in steel scrap and rubbers; and produces and sells engineering plastics. Hebei Yichen Industrial Group Corporation Limited was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Shijiazhuang, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Hebei Yichen Industrial Group Corporation Limited

longBusinessSummary: China 21st Century Education Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides education services in the People's Republic of China. It operates through three segments: Tertiary Education, Tutorial Center Education, and Preschool Education. The company offers kindergarten education and management services; after-school tutoring services; tertiary and continued education services; online education services; university education and related management services; and technical and management consultancy services. As of December 31, 2018, it operated a total of 15 schools, including 1 private college under the Shijiazhuang Institute of Technology name, 6 Saintach Tutorial Schools, and 8 Saintach Kindergartens. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Beijing Urban Construction Design & Development Group Co., Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides various services for infrastructure construction. It operates through two segments, Design, Survey, and Consultancy; and Construction Contracting. The company offers designing, surveying and mapping, monitoring, and consulting services in the engineering of urban rail transit, industrial and civil construction, and municipal engineering projects; and construction contracting services related to urban rail transit and the service concession arrangements under the build-operate-transfer arrangements. It also provides engineering consulting and testing, as well as development services; technical consulting and technical services; advisory services; and investment management services. In addition, the company is involved property management; and construction project investment, construction, and operation maintenance activities, as well as urban public transportation operation, maintenance, management, and services business. It has operations in Mainland China and internationally. The company was formerly known as Beijing Urban Construction Design & Research Institute Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Beijing Urban Construction Design & Development Group Co., Limited in October 2013. Beijing Urban Construction Design & Development Group Co., Limited was founded in 1958 and is based in Wanchai, Hong Kong.
longName: Beijing Urban Construction Design & Development Group Co., Limited

longBusinessSummary: China Tian Lun Gas Holdings Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the transportation, distribution, and sale of natural gas and compressed natural gas through its gas pipeline connections in the People' Republic of China. The company provides construction, designing, laying, installation, and maintenance services for gas pipeline connections. It also constructs and operates gas filling stations; produces and sells liquefied natural gas in bulk and in cylinders; sells gas equipment; provides engineering design and consulting, and new energy technology development services; trades in natural gas equipment; and invests in equity and assets. The company serves residential customers, commercial and industrial customers, and urban gas distributors. It owns 51 gas refilling stations. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Zhengzhou, the People's Republic of China. China Tian Lun Gas Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Tian Lun Group Limited.
longName: China Tian Lun Gas Holdings Limited

longBusinessSummary: China Development Bank Financial Leasing Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the leasing business in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Aircraft Leasing; Infrastructure Leasing; Ship, Vehicle and Construction Machinery Leasing; and Other Leasing Business segments. The Aircraft Leasing segment engages in the acquisition, leasing, management, and sale of commercial aircraft. The Infrastructure Leasing segment is involved in the leasing of transportation, urban, and energy infrastructure. The Ship, Vehicle and Construction Machinery Leasing segment engages in the leasing of vessels, commercial vehicles, and construction machinery. The Other Leasing Business segment is involved in the leasing of commercial properties, such as plants, offices, hotels, and shops; and manufacturing equipment in various sectors, such as chemicals, papermaking, textile, coal and steel, strategic emerging industries, environmental protection industry, wind power, nuclear power, photovoltaic, and other industries. The company was formerly known as CDB Leasing Co., Ltd. and changed its name to China Development Bank Financial Leasing Co., Ltd. in September 2015. The company was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China. China Development Bank Financial Leasing Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of China Development Bank Corporation.
longName: China Development Bank Financial Leasing Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: VPower Group International Holdings Limited designs, integrates, and sells gas-fired and diesel-fired engine-based gen-sets and power generation systems. The company operates through two segments, System Integration; and Investment, Building and Operation. It also operates and leases distributed power generation (DPG) stations for customers with semi-permanent electricity. In addition, the company engages in the sale and installation of power generation systems; trading of engines and components; and provision of distributed power solutions and management services. It serves customers in various sectors, including industry-grade and utility-grade DGP stations, governmental, residential and commercial buildings, data centers, hotels, construction works, mining operations, and railway and telecommunications projects primarily in the People's Republic of China, Singapore, Hong Kong, the United Arab Emirates, South Korea, Israel, and the Philippines. The company also serves off-takers in Indonesia, Bangladesh, Peru, Myanmar, and Ghana. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Hung Hom, Hong Kong. VPower Group International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Energy Garden Limited.

Chong Kin Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides concrete placing services and other ancillary services to various types of building and infrastructure related projects in Hong Kong. It provides logistics related services, including road freight transportation, logistics park development, and warehousing services; and car leasing services; as well as engages in the sale and leasing of new energy vehicles. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Wan chai, Hong Kong. Chong Kin Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Prestige Rich Holdings Limited.

COFCO Meat Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily engages in the hog production and livestock slaughtering businesses in the People's Republic of China. It is also involved in the production of feed; slaughtering, wholesale, and retail sale of fresh and frozen meats; manufacture, wholesale, and retail sale of processed meat products and fresh pork under the Maverick and Joycome brands; and sale of imported meat products, including pork, beef, poultry, and mutton, as well as by-products. COFCO Meat Holdings Limited was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Huobi Technology Holdings Limited manufactures and sells power-related and electronic products. The company's products include electronic power supplies, battery chargers, and coils/solenoids, as well as LED and optical products comprising LED lighting. It also offers manufacturing services to customers in the power conversion, tool, commercial, and consumer industries; and data center related services, including data storage and backup, data center operation and maintenance, and cloud-related services, such as cloud migration, environment construction, and introduction support services for Amazon Web Service and other cloud services. The company was formerly known as Pantronics Holdings Limited and changed its name to Huobi Technology Holdings Limited in November 2019. Huobi Technology Holdings Limited was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Vincent Medical Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, researches, develops, manufactures, markets, and sells medical devices. It operates in two segments, Original Equipment Manufacturing (OEM) and Original Brand Manufacturing. The company develops medical devices focusing on respiratory products; imaging contrast media power injector disposables; and orthopedic and rehabilitation products for OEM customers. Its respiratory products portfolio includes humidification systems, nCPAP interface systems, respiratory units, electronic air-oxygen blenders, and anesthesia systems. The company's orthopedic and rehabilitation products comprise various adjustable rehabilitation braces for support and protection, and rehabilitation of various skeletomuscular parts after injury or surgery. It also develops robotic hand training devices. Vincent Medical Holdings Limited sells its products under the Inspired Medical, Hand of Hope, and Hypnus brand names in the People's Republic of China, the United States, the Netherlands, Australia, Japan, and internationally. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Hung Hom, Hong Kong. Vincent Medical Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Vincent Raya International Limited.

Synertone Communication Corporation researches and develops, designs, manufactures, trades, and sells specialized communication systems, equipment, and systems technologies in the People's Republic of China and internationally. It operates through Communication Technology, Building Intelligence and Smart Home, and Industrial Control System segments. The Communication Technology segment manufactures and assembles core components of the digital trunking system and very small aperture terminal satellite system for system integrators, distributors, and end-users. The Industrial Control System segment offers automation control systems for use in various industries to monitor pressure, temperature, fluid levels, traffic condition, etc., including airport control and public utilities control to corporations, governmental entities, municipal utilities, and power generation plants. The Building Intelligence and Smart Home segment offers video intercoms system and security alarm solutions for residential complexes; and smart home devices and systems for households, as well as engages in the software development activities. Synertone Communication Corporation was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.

AB Builders Group Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a construction contractor in Macau. The company provides structural works, including structure and superstructure works, such as foundation works, basement works, piling and pile cap works, and the construction of high-rise buildings; and fitting-out works. It serves hotel and casino owners, property developers, governments, and construction works contractors. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Macau.

Starrise Media Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the manufacture, processing, and sale of textile products in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company operates through two segments, Textile and Media. It also produces, distributes, and licenses drama and television series, and films, as well as provides related services. In addition, the company invests in and guarantees drama series and films; provides agency services to performers, as well as event planning services; and leases equipment, costumes, and props relating to drama series and films production. Starrise Media Holdings Limited has a strategic partnership with Hubei Changjiang Huasheng Television Co., Ltd. The company was formerly known as Silverman Holdings Limited and changed its name to Starrise Media Holdings Limited in October 2017. Starrise Media Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Zibo, the People's Republic of China.

Nanfang Communication Holdings Limited, investment holding company, manufactures and sells optical fiber cables in the People's Republic of China. The company is also involved in the research and development of communication devices and accessories; and the provision of technology consultation and transfer of technology. Its customers primarily include national and regional telecommunications network operators and telecommunications supporting services providers. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Changzhou, the People's Republic of China. Nanfang Communication Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Pacific Mind Development Limited.

Metallurgical Corporation of China Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the engineering contracting, property development, equipment manufacture, and resource development businesses in China and internationally. The company's Engineering Contracting segment offers engineering, construction, and other related contracting services for metallurgical and non-metallurgical projects. Its Property Development segment develops and sells residential and commercial properties, and housing; and develops land. The company's Equipment Manufacture segment engages in the development and production of metallurgical equipment, steel structures, and other metal products. Its Resource Development segment is involved in the development, mining, and processing of mineral resources; and the production of nonferrous metals and polysilicon. The company also engages in the mining and smelting of nickel cobalt ore, as well as provision of investigation, design, infrastructure contractor, finance, repair work, trading, finance lease, integrated pipe network technology development, etc services. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Beijing, the People's Republic of China. Metallurgical Corporation of China Ltd. is a subsidiary of China Metallurgical Group Corporation.

Cteh Inc., an investment holding company, provides travel services in Canada and the United States. The company operates through three segments: Air Ticket Distribution, Travel Business Process Management, and Travel Products and Services. The Air Ticket Distribution segment distributes air tickets to travel agents and travelers; and issue air tickets directly on behalf of contracted airlines. The Travel Business Process Management segment provides mid-office and back-office support services comprising air ticket transaction processing, customer contact, BSP/ARC settlement and reconciliation, software development, travel licensing, compliance, and other administrative services to travel agents. The Travel Products and Services Segment designs, develops, and sells package tours, as well as travel products and services to travel agents and travelers in Asia, Europe, the Middle East, North America, and South America. The company was founded in 1976 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.

Vico International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, distributes third-party branded petrochemicals in Hong Kong, Macau, and Vietnam. It offers diesel; lubricant oils, including self-branded lubricant and third-party branded lubricant oils; and other petrochemicals, such as bitumen, as well as kerosene. The company also provides fleet card services. As of March 31, 2019, it operated a total number of 35,434 fleet card accounts. The company was formerly known as Rico International Holdings Limited and changed its name to Vico International Holdings Limited in May 2017. The company was founded in 1977 and is headquartered in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong. Vico International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Max Fortune Holdings Limited.

Redco Properties Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the property development and investment activities in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Greater Western Taiwan Straits Economic Zone; Central and Western Regions; Bohai Economic Rim; Pearl River Delta Region; and Others segments. It develops residential and commercial properties. The company is also involved in the provision of construction design and cost consulting, construction and sea reclamation, project management, and healthcare services. In addition, it trades in construction materials and provides property management services. Redco Properties Group Limited was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China.

Hilong Holding Limited, an investment holding company, provides oilfield equipment and services worldwide. The company operates through Oilfield Equipment Manufacturing and Services, Line Pipe Technology and Services, Oilfield Services, and Offshore Engineering Service segments. The Oilfield Equipment Manufacturing and Service segment produces and sells oilfield equipment; and offers oil country tubular goods (OCTG) coating services. The Line Pipe Technology and Services segment provides services related to oil and gas pipe line; and produces coating materials for anticorrosive and anti-friction purposes. The Oilfield Services segment offers well drilling services; and OCTG trading and related services to oil and gas producers. The Offshore Engineering Services segment provides offshore engineering and design services. The company is also involved in the manufacture, trading, and distribution of oil and gas equipment; the manufacture and distribution of hardbanding materials and special steel; the research and development on the technology of manufacturing oil and gas equipment, as well as coating services; the research, inspection, and repairment of oil and gas equipment; and the provision of offshore oilfield services. Hilong Holding Limited was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China. Hilong Holding Limited is a subsidiary of Hilong Group Limited.

Jia Yao Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, prints, and sells paper cigarette packages and social product paper packages in the People's Republic of China. The company offers various paper cigarette packages, including hard and soft cigarette packets; cigarette cartons; and gift sets to pack and carry various sets of cigarette packets. It also provides social product paper packages, such as colored boxes, labels, gift sets, and paper bags for packaging drugs and medicines, liquor and alcoholic beverages, and food and other social products. The company was formerly known as Tourism International Holdings Limited and changed its name to Jia Yao Holdings Limited in July 2019. Jia Yao Holdings Limited was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Yichang, the People's Republic of China.

Able Engineering Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates in the construction industry in Hong Kong. It is involved in the construction of private and public housing, institutional and private buildings, etc.; fitting out and interior works; and provision of design and building services. The company also engages in the repair, building maintenance, alteration, and addition works. It serves public and private sectors, including government departments and developers. The company was founded in 1976 and is headquartered in Kowloon Tong, Hong Kong. Able Engineering Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Profit Chain Investments Limited.

Yuzhou Properties Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the investment, development, and management of properties in the People's Republic of China. It operates through five segments: Property Development, Property Investment, Property Management, Hotel Operation, and Others. The company develops residential, retail, and commercial properties. As of December 31, 2018, it had approximately 17.38 million square meters of land reserve. The company also manages and operates hotels; trades in building and construction materials; and provides marketing services. Yuzhou Properties Company Limited was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.

Champion Alliance International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells cigarette packaging materials in the People's Republic of China. It offers transfer and laminated metallized papers for cigarette package manufacturers. The company was formerly known as Mengke Holdings Limited and changed its name to Champion Alliance International Holdings Limited in January 2019. Champion Alliance International Holdings Limited was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Yichang, the People's Republic of China.

Kin Shing Holdings Limited engages in erecting formworks for construction works in private residential and commercial buildings primarily in Hong Kong. The company primarily provides timber formworks by using timber and plywood; and metal formwork system by using aluminum and other metals. It also engages in building construction works. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong. Kin Shing Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Five Continental Enterprise Limited.

REF Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides financial printing services in Hong Kong. The company offers financial printing services comprising typesetting, proofreading, translation, design, printing, Web submitting, and newspaper placement to distribution of listing documents, financial reports, compliance documents, and other documents. It also provides conference room facilities; and media placement services. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. REF Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Jumbo Ace Enterprises Limited.

Minshang Creative Technology Holdings Limited operates a chain of restaurants. It operates 19 restaurants under the Viet's Choice brand name, 1 restaurant under the Five Spice brand name, and 1 restaurant under the Tascalopo brand name in Hong Kong. The company was formerly known as Food Wise Holdings Limited and changed its name to Minshang Creative Technology Holdings Limited in October 2018.
