Shanghai Haohai Biological Technology Co., Ltd. engages in the research and development, manufacture, and sale of biomedical materials in Mainland China, the United States, the United Kingdom, and internationally. The company offers orthopedics, medical aesthetics and wound care; ophthalmology, and anti-adhesion and hemostasis products. It also provides medical sodium hyaluronate, medical chitosan, medical collagen sponge, and rhEGF, as well as biological reagents and materials. In addition, the company engages in the manufacture and sale of contact lens and intraocular lens materials, machines, and accessories; and investment and trading businesses. Further, it is involved in research and development of biological engineering and pharmaceutical products, related technology transfer, and consultation and service activities. The company was formerly known as Haohai Limited and changed its name to Shanghai Haohai Biological Technology Co., Ltd. in 2010. Shanghai Haohai Biological Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Shanghai, China.
longName: Shanghai Haohai Biological Technology Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: Beijing Gas Blue Sky Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the sale and distribution of natural gas and other related products in the People's Republic of China. It operates through three segments: Natural Gas Refuelling Station; Trading and Distribution of Natural Gas; and City Gas, Pipeline Construction Fee, Value-Added Service, and Others segments. The company constructs and operates compressed natural gas (CNG) and liquefied natural gas (LNG) refueling stations for vehicles; and distributes and trades in CNG, LNG, and liquefied petroleum gas as a wholesaler and sales agent to industrial and commercial users through direct supply facilities. It also sells natural gas to residential, industrial, and commercial users through pipelines; and provides other related products, such as transportation, rental, consultancy, and value-added services, as well as sells electricity. The company was formerly known as Blue Sky Power Holdings Limited and changed its name to Beijing Gas Blue Sky Holdings Limited in January 2017. Beijing Gas Blue Sky Holdings Limited was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.
longName: Beijing Gas Blue Sky Holdings Limited

longBusinessSummary: Dragon Rise Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides foundation works services as a subcontractor in Hong Kong. Its activities include excavation and lateral support works, and pile cap construction works; disposal of excavated materials from piling; and ancillary services, including dismantling of shoring, site formation, steel fixing, and site clearance. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Shatin, Hong Kong. Dragon Rise Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Fame Circle Limited.

Huazhong In-Vehicle Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells automobile body parts in Mainland China and internationally. It offers internal and external decorative and structural automobile parts, molds and tooling products, and casings and liquid tanks of air-conditioning or heater units; and other non-automobile products, such as top cowl covers and office chairs. The company also manufactures and sells plastic parts and automotive parts; imports and exports various products and technologies; and processes and sells plastic and latex products, and spare and accessory parts. It serves automakers and automobile body parts manufacturers, as well as suppliers for automakers. The company was formerly known as Huazhong Holdings Company Limited and changed its name to Huazhong In-Vehicle Holdings Company Limited in January 2015. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Xiangshan, China. Huazhong In-Vehicle Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of Huayou Holdings Company Limited.

Sinco Pharmaceuticals Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides marketing, promotion, and channel management services for imported pharmaceutical products and medical devices in China. The company offers Octapharma, a human albumin solution for use in premature infants; Axetine, which is used for the treatment of bacterial infections, including respiratory infections, urinary tract infections, soft tissue infections, gynecological and obstetrical infections, gonorrhea, and other infections, as well as for the prevention of post-surgery infections; and Medocef that is used for the treatment of bacterial infections, such as the infections of the lower respiratory tract comprising pneumonia, urinary tract, bile duct, peritoneum, skin, soft tissue, pelvic area, and sepsis. It also provides Esafosfina, which is used for treating hypophosphatemia and chronic diseases, including alcohol intoxication, malnutrition, and hypophosphatemic respiratory failure; Taurolite, a third generation oral cholic acid drug that is used for the treatment of gallstone diseases; and Tamifil injection for the treatment of metastatic prostate cancer, true precocious puberty, and endometriosis. In addition, the company offers pharmaceutical products research and development services; warehouse facilities for pharmaceutical products; and medical and biological technology consultation services. The company was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Chengdu, the People's Republic of China. Sinco Pharmaceuticals Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Risun Investments Limited.

Tianyun International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, produces and sells processed fruit products; and trades fresh fruits in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and internationally. The company operates through Own Brand Sales, OEM Sales, and Fresh Fruits Sales and Others segments. The company offers various processed fruit products, such as strawberry, apricot, peach, pear, apple, pineapple, and mixed fruits under the Tiantong Food, Bingo -My Times, and Guo Xiao Lan brand names. It also engages in the manufacture and trading of food machineries. Tianyun International Holdings Limited was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Linyi, the People's Republic of China.

Winox Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, develops, manufactures, and sells stainless steel products. The company's products include watch bracelets; costume jewelry; accessories and parts for leather goods; and mobile phone cases and parts for mobile phone manufacturers. It is also involved in the provision of management and administration services; and properties holding activities. The company operates in Switzerland, Taiwan, Liechtenstein, and other European countries, as well as the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and internationally. The company was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Yau Tong, Hong Kong. Winox Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Ming Fung Investment Limited.

Yunnan Water Investment Co., Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, constructs, operates, and maintains municipal water supply and wastewater treatment facilities in the People's Republic of China and internationally. It operates through five segments: Wastewater Treatment, Water Supply, Construction and Sales of Equipment, Solid Waste Treatment, and Others. It constructs and operates wastewater treatment projects, water supply projects, and solid waste treatment projects; undertakes build and transfer (BT) projects, and engineering-procurement-construction (EPC) projects; and produces, installs, and sells equipment for wastewater treatment, water supply, solid waste treatment, and other infrastructure facilities. The company undertakes operation and maintenance (O&M) projects for wastewater treatment, water supply, and solid waste treatment facilities owned by third parties; and offers technical and consultancy services. As at 31 December 2018, it had 115 concession wastewater treatment projects, including 7 build-own-operate (BOO), 68 build-operate-transfer (BOT), 2 transfer-own-operate (TOO), 20 transfer-operate-transfer (TOT) projects, 1 rehabilitate-operate-transfer (ROT), and 17 municipal environment comprehensive treatment projects, with total daily treatment capacity of approximately 3,027,200 tonnes; 62 concession water supply projects comprising, 15 BOO projects, 31 BOT projects, 11 TOT projects, and 5 municipal environment comprehensive treatment projects with total daily capacity of approximately 2,221,000 tonnes; 19 solid waste treatment projects with annual treatment capacity of approximately 3,527,500 tonnes; 11 BT projects and 10 EPC projects; and 32 O&M projects. The company was formerly known as Yunnan Water Industry Investment and Development Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Yunnan Water Investment Company Limited in July 2014. The company was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Kunming, the People's Republic of China.

Ascentage Pharma Group International, a clinical-stage biotechnology company, engages in developing novel therapies in the United States and Mainland China. It is involved in developing eight drug candidates, such as APG-1252, APG-2575, AT-101, APG-1387, APG-115, and HQP1351, as well as HQP8361 and APG-2449 for cancers, hepatitis B virus, and age-related diseases. The company was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Suzhou, China.

Honma Golf Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and sells a range of golf club equipment in Asia, North America, Europe, and internationally. It offers driver, fairway wood, utility, iron, wedge, and putter clubs; golf balls, golf bags, golf club head covers, gloves, shoes, and other golf-related accessories; and apparel for men and women under the BERES, TOUR WORLD, Be ZEAL, and HONMA brands. The company distributes its products through HONMA-branded self-operated stores; direct third-party retailers, including sports megastores; and wholesale distributors that on-sell its products to other third parties. As of March 31, 2019, it had 68 HONMA-branded self-operated stores. Honma Golf Limited was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.

FingerTango Inc., an investment holding company, develops, operates, and publishes mobile games in the People's Republic of China. The company publishes and sells simulation mobile games. As of December 31, 2018, it had approximately 150 million cumulative registered users. FingerTango Inc. was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Tianhe, China.

Haidilao International Holding Ltd., an investment holding company, engages in the restaurants operation and relevant delivery businesses. Its Haidilao brand Chinese cuisine restaurant focuses on hot pot cuisine. The company is also involved in the sale of condiment products and food ingredients; logistics and wholesale trade activities; and food research and development, and trading businesses. As of December 31, 2018, it owned and operated 466 restaurants, including 430 restaurants in 109 cities in Mainland China, as well as 36 restaurants in Taiwan, Hong Kong, Singapore, South Korea, Japan, the United States, and Canada. Haidilao International Holding Ltd. was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

longName: China Huishan Dairy Holdings Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Flat Glass Group Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the design, development, production, and sale of glass products in the People's Republic of China, Europe, North America, and internationally. The company offers photovoltaic glass, architectural glass, float glass, household glass, and other types of related products. In addition, it is involved in the extraction of a quartzite mine; electricity generation of solar battery module; and trading of glass products of glass products. The company serves PV module manufacturers, glass processing manufacturers, glass wholesalers, furniture manufacturers and processing companies, furniture retailers, architectural contractors, architectural glass processing companies, and construction companies. Flat Glass Group Co., Ltd. was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Jiaxing, the People's Republic of China.

Zuoli Kechuang Micro-finance Company Limited operates as a microfinance company in the People's Republic of China. The company offers unsecured, guaranteed, collateralized, and pledged loans; enterprise loans, including agriculture loans and technology enterprises credit loans, as well as loans for other small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs), and microenterprises; individual loans, such as individual business, consumption, start-up, and other loans; and fast and zhang shang tong loans. It serves customers engaged in agricultural businesses and rural development activities; customers residing in rural areas; and SMEs and microenterprises, as well as online retailers for lifestyle products, agricultural products, cultural supplies and industrial products. The company was formerly known as Deqing Zuoli Kechuang Micro-finance Company Limited and changed its name to Zuoli Kechuang Micro-Finance Company Limited in April 2014. Zuoli Kechuang Micro-finance Company Limited was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Huzhou, the People's Republic of China.

Tenfu (Cayman) Holdings Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a tea-product company. It sells and markets various tea products; and develops product concepts, tastes, and packaging designs. The company offers approximately 1,300 varieties of traditional Chinese tea-leaf products; 300 varieties of tea snacks; and tea ware. It sells its products primarily under the Tenfu, Tenfu Ten Xin, and Uncle Lee brands. As of December 31, 2018, the company sold tea products in 1,120 retail outlets and retail points in 31 provinces, autonomous regions, and municipalities in the People's Republic of China, including stores with shop fronts at street level; and shopping malls and concession counters in the department stores and hypermarkets. It is also involved in the classification and packaging of tea leaves; manufacture of tea snacks; catering management, beverage production, pre-packaged food sale, and property management activities; and provision of hotel, restaurant, and related services, as well as sells tea leaves, tea snacks, and tea ware through Internet. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Xiamen, the People's Republic of China.

Yangtze Optical Fibre And Cable Joint Stock Limited Company manufactures and sells optical fiber and cable products in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company operates through Optical Fibres and Optical Fibre Preforms, and Optical Fibre Cables segments. It offers products, such as communication optical fibers, cable products, specialty fibers, integrated cabling, optical distribution frames, optical transceivers, coaxial cables, and cable manufacturing equipment. The company provides copper wire and related products; integrated wiring systems; germanium tetrachloride; technical development consulting services for computer hardware and software and ancillary equipment; vapor; and chemicals, as well as trades in raw materials. In addition, it offers solutions to telecom operators, cloud and data centers, government, smart campus, railway transportation, education, power grids, and consumer electronics. Further, the company sells submarine cables, optical cables, and other power cables and their accessories; and installs cables, accessories, and systems related to various submarine projects. Yangtze Optical Fibre And Cable Joint Stock Limited Company was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Wuhan, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Yangtze Optical Fibre And Cable Joint Stock Limited Company

longBusinessSummary: KVB Kunlun Financial Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides leveraged foreign exchange, trading, cash dealing, and other services. It offers margin dealing, commodity and index trading, and precious metals trading and settlement services. The company also provides securities brokerage and management services. It primarily operates in Hong Kong, New Zealand, Australia, and the People's Republic of China. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. KVB Kunlun Financial Group Limited operates as a subsidiary of Citic Securities Overseas Investment Company Limited

Differ Group Holding Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides financial services in the People's Republic of China. The company provides asset management services, including investments on land and properties, distressed assets, and equities; finance lease services; and financial services, including financial consultancy, guarantee, and supply chain agency services, as well as provides loan, and securities dealing and brokerage services. It also offers property development and management services; and hotel and tourism services. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Xiamen, China.

Tempus Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the health and wellness business under the OTO brand. The company operates through Sales of Health and Wellness Products Business; and Trading and Logistics Business segments. It researches, develops, and sells health and wellness products. The company sells relaxation products, fitness products, therapeutic products, diagnostic products, and cookware products to financial institutions, retail chain stores, and professional bodies. As of December 31, 2018, it operated 24 retail outlets in Hong Kong and Macau; 112 retail outlets in Mainland China; and 16 retail outlets in Singapore and Malaysia, as well as Internet sales and corporate sales channels. The company also exports its products to distributors or wholesalers in Eastern Europe and the Middle East. In addition, it is also involved in the trading and distribution of consumer products; and provision of transportation, warehousing, and other services. The company was formerly known as OTO Holdings Limited and changed its name to Tempus Holdings Limited in March 2015. Tempus Holdings Limited was founded in 1978 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong. Tempus Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Tempus Holdings (Hong Kong) Limited.

EGL Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides package tours, free independent travelers packages, individual travel elements, and ancillary travel related products and services in Hong Kong, Macau, Japan, and internationally. It also owns, develops, and manages a hotel. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. EGL Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of Evergloss Management Group Company Limited.

Henan Jinma Energy Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, operates in the coking chemical industry in the People's Republic of China. Its Coke segment produces and sells coke. The company's Refined Chemicals segment processes and sells benzene based and coal tar based refined chemicals. Its Energy Products segment processes and sells coal gas and liquefied natural gas. The company's Trading segment trades in coal, coal mining equipment, and nonferrous materials. Henan Jinma Energy Company Limited was founded in 2003 and is based in Jiyuan, China.
address1: The South of West 1st Belt Road

longBusinessSummary: Huatai Securities Co., Ltd., a security company, provides financial services in Mainland China and internationally. It operates through Wealth Management, Institutional Services, Investment Management, International Business, and Other segments. The company trades in stocks, funds, bonds, futures, and options on behalf of clients; promotes and sells securities products and services; and provides various financial products and asset allocation, margin financing, securities lending, securities-backed lending, and stock pledged lending services. It also offers investment banking services consisting of equity underwriting services, which include IPO and equity refinancing services; debt underwriting services, such as bond financing services; mergers-oriented financial advisory services; and over-the-counter financial products and transactions, including national equities exchange and quotations listing, and follow-on financing services. In addition, the company provides asset custody and fund services, including settlement, liquidation, reporting, and valuation for private and public funds; margin trading; research services; equity securities investments and transactions; fixed income investments and transactions; asset management; private equity and alternative investment; commodities trading and arbitrage; investment portfolio and fund management; customer relation management; and leveraged buyout, pre-listing financing, business expansion, and other related services. It offers its wealth management products through ZhangLe Fortune Path mobile application and PC platform. Huatai Securities Co., Ltd. was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Nanjing, China.

Freetech Road Recycling Technology (Holdings) Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells road maintenance equipment, and provides road maintenance services in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Maintenance Services and Sale of Equipment segments. It offers asphalt pavement maintenance (APM) equipment; and APM services to repair damaged asphalt pavement surfaces under the Road Doctor name. Freetech Road Recycling Technology (Holdings) Limited was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

DYNAM JAPAN HOLDINGS Co., Ltd., through its subsidiaries, operates and manages a chain of pachinko halls in Japan. The company also provides real estate and property management services; real estate development services; accounting and administration services; cleaning services for offices and pachinko halls; travel and insurance agency services; international freight forwarding services; and contracting services for construction works, property transactions, and management services. In addition, it is involved in developing and trading of pachinko machines; trading LCD monitors; operating restaurants; selling coffee beans; manufacturing and selling household supplies; and supporting franchise chain, as well as the aircraft leasing business. As of March 31, 2019, the company operated 450 pachinko halls. DYNAM JAPAN HOLDINGS Co., Ltd. was founded in 1967 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.

KangLi International Holdings Limited manufactures and sells galvanized steel products in the People's Republic of China, South Korea, and internationally. It operates in three segments: Hard Steel Coil, Unpainted Galvanised Steel Products, and Painted Galvanised Steel Products. The Hard Steel Coil segment provides cold-rolled hard steel coils. The Unpainted Galvanised Steel Products segment offers hot-dipped galvanized/zinc coated steel coils and sheets. The Painted Galvanised Steel Products segment provides hot-dipped color coated galvanized steel coils and sheets. The company sells its products to midstream steel product processors for further processing; and home appliance manufacturers for use in the production of home appliances, such as refrigerators, washing machines, and ovens. KangLi International Holdings Limited was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Changzhou, China.

Hin Sang Group (International) Holding Co. Ltd. primarily engages in the manufacture, marketing, and sale of healthcare products. It operates through four segments: Product Development, Brand Development and Management, Trading of Goods, and Healthcare. The Product Development segment develops and sells healthcare products, personal care products, household products, and health supplements under the Hin Sang, Beautymate, Shuang Long, and King's Antiseptic brand names, as well as Chinese medicines under the Tai Wo Tong brand. The Brand Development and Management segment purchases, distributes, and sells personal care products under the Pahmi, Vcnic, Zici, and Sunew brand names; and manages and develops related product brands. The Trading of Goods segment engages in the distribution and sale of skin care products, personal care products, and household products purchased from various authorized dealers, independent traders, and manufacturers or parallel importers. The Healthcare segment provides Chinese medical healthcare related services for mothers and children; develops mother and child related health products; and hospital, medical center, and related services. The company is also involved in the trading of slimming products; and property holding business. Further, it formulates and implements marketing and branding strategies; and prepares and controls annual budgets for marketing activities of branded products. The company sells its products in Hong Kong, as well as sells through a network of distributors in the People's Republic of China and Macau; and exports its products to Malaysia. It also sells its products online. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong. Hin Sang Group (International) Holding Co. Ltd. is a subsidiary of Genwealth Group Holding Company Limited.
longName: Hin Sang Group (International) Holding Co. Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: Golden Throat Holdings Group Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells lozenges, and other pharmaceutical and healthcare food products in China. It offers Golden Throat lozenges over-the-counter medicine to relive symptoms of sore, dry throat, and hoarse voice caused by acute pharyngitis. It also provides Golden Throat lozenge series products that include Dule lozenges and sugar-free Dule lozenges in various flavors, such as orange, fructus momordicae, chrysanthemum, American ginseng, and hawthorn; Yinxingye tablet that are designed to facilitate blood circulation, remove blood stasis, and dredge energy channels; and herbal vegetable beverages for soothing voice and relieving sore throats. The company exports its products to the United States, Canada, Russia, the European Union, Australia, Southeast Asia, the Middle East, Mexico, Peru, Africa, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, Maldives, and Brazil. Golden Throat Holdings Group Company Limited was founded in 1956 and is headquartered in Liuzhou, China.
longName: Golden Throat Holdings Group Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: China Aluminum Cans Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily manufactures and sells aluminum aerosol cans in Mainland China, Africa, the United States, Japan, rest of Asia, the Middle East, and internationally. It operates through Aluminum Aerosol Cans, and Aerosol and Non-Aerosol Products segments. The company offers aluminum aerosol cans for packaging personal care products, such as body deodorant, hair styling products, and shaving creams; and pharmaceutical products, including pain relieving sprays, spray dressings, and antiseptic sprays. It is also involved in the content filling of aerosol cans; and production and sale of aerosol and non-aerosol products comprising car refrigerants, air conditioner disinfectant cleaners, paint removers, spray paints, wax products, air fragrances, multi-purpose foam cleaners, carburetor cleaners, anti-rust lubricating sprays, furniture polishers, sticker removers, skin care products, sunscreens, facial products, fragrance, and hair treatments products. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Zhongshan, the People's Republic of China. China Aluminum Cans Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Wellmass International Limited.

Ourgame International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, develops and operates online card and board games in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company operates through Online Games Business - Lianzhong Group; Online Games Business  Peerless Group; and ESports Business segments. It operates an integrated online game platform that offers personal computer (PC) games and provides services through its PC client portals, such as Ourgame Hall; and distributes mobile games and provides services primarily for android and iOS operating systems through third-party distribution and payment channels, including mobile operators. The company also provides Web games through its ourgame.com and wpt.com Websites; and through third-party distributors, including Baidu, Sina Weibo, and Qihoo 360 Web-based portals, as well as Websites. In addition, it distributes games developed and operated by third-party developers; provides computer related technical support services; offers television production, brand licensing, and tour management services in Gibraltar; and organizes and broadcasts online to offline mind-sports events, tournaments, TV shows, and contents. Further, the company engages in the provision of cultural events organization and consulting services; and operation of an Internet café. Ourgame International Holdings Limited was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

HongGuang Lighting Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and sells light-emitting diode (LED) beads and LED lighting products in the People's Republic of China. The company offers candle, flood, bulb, spot, down, oyster, and panel lights, as well as tube and torch. It serves manufacturers of backlight LED modules/panels, LCD panels, and other electronic products, as well as a trading company. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Zhuhai, the People's Republic of China.

Orient Securities International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides brokerage services, and underwriting and placing services in Hong Kong. It also offers margin financing services, securities trading, and initial public offering financing services. Orient Securities International Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Great World Company Holdings Ltd, an investment holding company, engages in the property, forestry, and general trading, and advertising businesses in the People's Republic of China. It is involved in the property investment and development activities; and operation and management of residential and commercial properties. The company also researches, grows, and sells forestry products for clean energy sector. In addition, it engages in the provision of mobile advertising media services for property developers. Additionally, the company distributes information technology products. The company was formerly known as T S Telecom Technologies Limited and changed its name to Great World Company Holdings Ltd in November 2008. Great World Company Holdings Ltd was founded in 1991 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

Sino Splendid Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in publishing and events organizing business in Singapore and Hong Kong. It operates through four segments: Travel Media Business, Financial Magazine Business, Securities Investment, and Money Lending. The company provides advertising services through the Internet and travel magazines; organizes events; and publishes magazines. It also provides contents and advertising services in a financial magazine distributed in the People's Republic of China; and invests in securities. In addition, it provides funds to clients and receives loan interest income in return. The company was formerly known as China.com Inc. and changed its name to Sino Splendid Holdings Limited in October 2013. Sino Splendid Holdings Limited was founded in 1974 and is headquartered in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.

Global Strategic Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the copper trading business in the People's Republic of China. It operates through three segments: Trading of Copper, Natural Gas Operations, and Leasing Business. It also invests in natural gas projects; sells natural gas, natural gas cooking appliances, and accessories; and provides pipeline installation services. In addition, the company offers leasing services for steel support axial force servo system and technology support. Further, it operates e-commerce platform for design of garments; provides commodity trading services; and designs and constructs new energy power generation equipment, energy storage systems, and power equipment, as well as provides technology development, technical, and technology transfer services. The company was formerly known as DIGITALHONGKONG.COM and changed its name to Global Strategic Group Limited in January 2015. Global Strategic Group Limited is based in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

Chinese Energy Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the trading business in the People's Republic of China. The company is involved in the general trading activities, including market sourcing of technical and electronic products; and trading of liquefied natural gas products. It also invests in financial assets; and offers money lending and factoring services. Chinese Energy Holdings Limited is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Polyard Petroleum International Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the exploration, exploitation, and development of oil, natural gas, and coal the Philippines. The company holds interests the Central Luzon gas project that covers approximately 6,840 square kilometers located in Central Luzon; the San Miguel coal mine project, which covers an area of 50 square kilometers located in San Miguel; and the South Cebu oil and gas project covering an area of 1,970 square kilometers located in Cebu Island. It also provides technical services; and consultancy services for oil and gas exploration and development, as well as trades in minerals, energy, and petroleum-related products. The company was formerly known as Kanstar Environmental Paper Products Holdings Limited and changed its name to Polyard Petroleum International Group Limited in November 2007. Polyard Petroleum International Group Limited is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Polyard Petroleum International Group Limited is a subsidiary of Silver Star Enterprises Holdings Inc.

Changhong Jiahua Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, distributes information technology (IT) consumer products, IT corporate products, and other products in Mainland China and other regions. The company's IT Consumer Products segment distributes personal computers, digital products, and IT accessories. Its IT Corporate Products segment distributes storage products, minicomputers, networking products, personal computer servers, intelligent building management system products, and unified communication and contact center products. The company's Others segment distributes smartphones; develops own brand products, such as mobile location-based service products; sells warranty packages; and provides professional integrated IT solutions and services. The company was formerly known as China Data Broadcasting Holdings Limited and changed its name to Changhong Jiahua Holdings Limited in January 2013. Changhong Jiahua Holdings Limited is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Changhong Jiahua Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Sichuan Changhong Electronic Co., Limited.

TradeGo FinTech Limited operates as an integrated securities trading platform service provider in Hong Kong and the People's Republic of China. The company develops trading platform software, such as TradeGo Pro and Futures Platform. It offers front office trading system services to support trading of a range of financial instruments, including equities, ETFs, futures, options, warrants, and derivatives; value-added services; and other services, such as simulation trading platform, online account opening appointment, two-factor authentication, customized software development, cloud infrastructure, hosting, and online advertising services. In addition, the company holds market data vendor licenses from five stock and future exchanges, as well as provides a range of real-time market data feeds from these exchanges. The company was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.

Finsoft Financial Investment Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily develops and sells financial trading software solutions. The company operates through Financial Trading Software Solutions, Other IT and Internet Financial Platforms Services, Money Lending, Assets Investments, and Others segments. The Financial Trading Software Solutions segment offers trading and settlement systems of financial products for financial institutions. The Other IT and Internet Financial Platforms Services provides e-commerce platforms, other online consultancy services, IT services, and other financial information. The Money Lending segment offers loan financing. The Assets Investments segment trades in listed securities, and invests in properties for rental income. The Others segment provides referral services to source, identify, and refer deal opportunities to interested parties; and corporate finance advisory services. This segment also trades in gaming products, as well as offers related marketing services. Finsoft Financial Investment Holdings Limited primarily serves financial institutions that conduct brokerage business of financial products traded in Hong Kong. The company was formerly known as Finsoft Corporation and changed its name to Finsoft Financial Investment Holdings Limited in June 2015. Finsoft Financial Investment Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in North Point, Hong Kong.

Hao Wen Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in money lending business in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company also engages in the processing and trading of electronic parts; and manufacturing and trading of biomass fuel products. Hao Wen Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.

Unitas Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides corporate finance advisory services primarily to listed and non-listed companies in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Corporate Finance Advisory Service and Dry Bulk Shipping segments. The company advises on the listing rules, growth enterprise market (GEM) listing rules, and takeovers codes; mergers and acquisitions activities; other corporate activities, such as fund raising exercises; and corporate resumptions, as well as acts as an independent financial adviser to transactions of listed issuers that are under the listing rules, GEM listing rules, and takeovers codes. It also provides dry bulk shipping and general business consulting services. The company was formerly known as Chanceton Financial Group Limited and changed its name to Unitas Holdings Limited in October 2016. Unitas Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.

WLS Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides scaffolding and fitting out, management contracting, and other services for the construction and building works in Hong Kong. It operates through eight segments: Scaffolding Services for Construction and Buildings Work; Fitting Out Services for Construction and Buildings Work; Management Contracting Services for Construction and Buildings Work; Gondolas, Parapet Railings and Access Equipment Installation and Maintenance Services; Money Lending Business; Securities Brokerage and Margin Financing; Securities Investment Business; and Assets Management Business. The company offers various scaffolding services, including metal-bamboo matrix system scaffold, bamboo scaffold, and steel/ Pik Lik scaffold. It also provides permanent gondola services, such as building maintenance unit and permanent access platform; temporary gondola services; and gondolas rental services. In addition, the company offers false ceiling and fitting out services; glass fiber reinforced concrete, glass reinforced plastic, signages, artworks, and stamping concrete solutions; and transportation, management, and consultancy services. Further, it engages in the property investment and holding, and money lending businesses; design, sale, trade, rental, repair, and maintenance of gondolas and parapet railings; and installation and maintenance of access equipment. Additionally, the company provides securities brokerage, margin financing, securities investment, and assets management services. WLS Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Aberdeen, Hong Kong.

Evershine Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in trading, property development and investment, money lending, mobile application, and cemetery businesses primarily in the People's Republic of China. The company is involved in the trading of goods, including steaming coal and chrome ores; and building construction, property development, and leasing of properties; trading of construction materials; and retail trade of window frames, doors, and wardrobes, as well as the provision of consultancy and money lending services. It also constructs and operates cemeteries; develops mobile games; and publishes games and applications, as well as provides related solutions. The company was formerly known as TLT Lottotainment Group Limited and changed its name to Evershine Group Holdings Limited in November 2014. Evershine Group Holdings Limited was founded in 1997 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

Kwong Man Kee Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides engineering services to the car park flooring industry in Hong Kong. The company offers flooring services, including application of proprietary floor coating products for providing a colorful, slip-resistance, and hard wearing surface that is resistant against water and petrochemicals; and ancillary services comprising specialized texture painting and waterproofing works. It also offers screeding and anti-skid surfacing services. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. Kwong Man Kee Group Limited is a subsidiary of Sage City Investments Limited.

Asian Capital Resources (Holdings) Limited, an investment holding company, provides private investment fund management and consultancy services in the People's Republic of China and Hong Kong. It also provides traditional and Internet media, content production management, and media content design services; and Internet development and maintenance services. In addition, the company offers business management and consulting services. Asian Capital Resources (Holdings) Limited is headquartered in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.

China Brilliant Global Limited, an investment holding company, engages in researching, designing, developing, wholesaling, and retailing jewelry in the Peoples' Republic of China. The company operates in three segments: Trading and Retailing of Jewelry, Lending Business, and Pharmaceutical and Healthcare Products. It is also involved in the distribution and retail of Chinese herbal medicines and drugs; Internet artificial Intelligence research, management, and consultancy activities; and network and data and money lending businesses. In addition, the company manufactures, distributes, and trades in medical, pharmaceutical, and healthcare food products. The company was formerly known as Prosten Health Holdings Limited and changed its name to China Brilliant Global Limited in May 2018. China Brilliant Global Limited was incorporated in 1989 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong. China Brilliant Global Limited is a subsidiary of Brilliant Chapter Limited.

Timeless Software Limited, an investment holding company, engages in mining business in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in two segments, Mining Business and Other Business. It explores, exploits, processes, and sells nickel and copper ores. The company has interest in the Baishiquan nickel-copper mine located in Xinjiang. It is also involved in the provision of consultancy, software maintenance and development, and e-commerce services, as well as invests in IT and innovation projects, including e-Sport tournament organizing, bio and nano new materials, IT startup fund, and intelligent agricultural applications. In addition, the company engages in the technology and business investment activities; and research and development of Styrofoam. Timeless Software Limited was founded in 1996 and is based in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.

Sun International Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in equine services, securities services, and money lending businesses in Hong Kong, Australia, Europe, and Singapore. It operates through Financial Services and Equine Services segments. The company offers securities trading, margin financing, and futures and options brokerage services; financial intermediary services for facilitating capital investment entrant scheme applications; investment management services for individual and corporate clients, including managed accounts, hedge funds, private funds, dedicated funds, investment advisory services, etc.; personal and SME loans, home mortgages, equity financing, equity mortgage, and corporate finance services; and custodian services. It also provides stallion services; and trades in and breeds bloodstocks. In addition, the company invests in yachts and properties. The company was formerly known as Sun International Resources Limited and changed its name to Sun International Group Limited in December 2017. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Sun International Group Limited is a subsidiary of First Cheer Holdings Limited.

Flying Financial Service Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides financial services to real estate developers primarily in the People's Republic of China. It offers short-term and long-term financial consultation services; and entrusted, pawn, and other loans to borrowers and financial institutions. The company also provides long-term finance lease and short-term factoring services; and operates a financial services platform. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, China. Flying Financial Service Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Ming Cheng Investments Limited.

ETS Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides multi-media contact service, contact center systems, and staff insourcing and financial services in Hong Kong. It operates through Outsourcing Inbound Contact Services, Outsourcing Outbound Contact Services, Staff Insourcing Services, Contact Service Centre and Service Centre Facilities Management Services, Financial Services and Others segments. The Outsourcing Inbound Contact Services segment offers general enquiry, promotion, customer service, order, registration, emergency, and helpdesk hotlines. The Outsourcing Outbound Contact Services segment provides telemarketing and customer retention services, and cross-selling and customer satisfaction surveys. The Staff Insourcing Services segment offers staff support to various client activities, such as customer service, telemarketing, data entry, helpdesk assistance, and other backend projects. The Contact Service Centre and Service Centre Facilities Management Services segment consisting of leasing of its contact center facilities in the form of workstations; IVRS hosting services; contact center system holding solution; and service center facility management. The Financial Services segment offers securities broking, margin lending, and consultancy services; and provision of asset management and fund management services. The Others segment provides licensing; sells software and system; and system maintenance services. In addition, the company is involved in provision of rental, home maintenance, and corporate financial management services. The company was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Mongkok, Hong Kong. ETS Group Limited is a subsidiary of Million Top Enterprises Limited.

Viva China Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as an integrated sports conglomerate in the People's Republic of China. It operates through two segments, Sports-Related Business and Community Development. The Sports-Related Business segment produces and distributes sports content; manages and markets sports talents; and provides sports consultancy services. The Community Development segment develops property for sales and investment; researches and develops, manufactures, markets, and sells construction materials; operates sports parks and centers; develops communities; and provides consultancy and subcontracting services. The company was formerly known as Coolpoint Energy Limited and changed its name to Viva China Holdings Limited in November 2010. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Vodatel Networks Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily engages in the design, sale, and implementation of network and systems infrastructure in Mainland China, Hong Kong, and Macau. It offers customer data automation, customization and integration, and technical support services; and IT and surveillance solutions for the public sectors, as well as the telecommunications, gaming, and hospitality sectors. The company engages in the research and development of software, and provision of related software consultancy services; and provision of wireless data communications and Internet related products and services. It offers computer software, hardware, and system integration services. The company sells data networking systems and provides related engineering services; and provides warehouse services. Vodatel Networks Holdings Limited is headquartered in Taipa, Macau.

eBroker Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides financial software solution services to financial institutions in Hong Kong. The company's trading solution includes eBrokerSys, sponsored DMA, institutional sales desk solutions, and global futures and options trading platform; Algo solutions comprises Algo trader, volatility trading system, and market making system; investment solutions, such as Alpha Investment system, fund administration system, and wealth management system; and enterprise solutions consists of global back office system, portfolio risk reporting system, and data centers hosting and exchange colocation services. It also sells computer products. The company was founded in 2000 and is based in Central, Hong Kong.

China Biotech Services Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, offers medical laboratory testing and health check services in the People's Republic of China. The company also researches and develops, manufactures, and sells Chinese medicine products; and manufactures and sells health supplements, slimming pills, and beauty products; and trades in pharmaceutical intermediates and traditional Chinese medicines. It also engages in property investment and holding, and money lending businesses; trades in securities; and provides management services. The company was formerly known as Rui Kang Pharmaceutical Group Investments Limited and changed its name to China Biotech Services Holdings Limited in November 2017. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. China Biotech Services Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of China Wah Yan Healthcare Limited.

Luxey International (Holdings) Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and trades in swimwear and garment products. The company operates through three segments: Swimwear and Garment, Trading and On-line Shopping Related, and Money Lending. It also engages in trading activities, as well as the provision of online shopping and media related services. In addition, the company engages in microfinance business. It sells its products in the People's Republic of China, the Kingdom of Cambodia, the United Kingdom, Spain, Sweden, the United States, the Netherlands, Israel, France, Italy, and internationally. The company was formerly known as China Post E-Commerce (Holdings) Limited and changed its name to Luxey International (Holdings) Limited in May 2012. Luxey International (Holdings) Limited is headquartered in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong.

KOS International Holdings Limited provides human resources (HR) services to clients from various industries in Hong Kong. It offers recruitment services, and secondment and payroll services. Its recruitment services include for various positions at all levels, including administrative, executive, managerial, and professional. The company also assists in payroll and other administration services at its clients' requests. KOS International Holdings Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.

Atlinks- Group Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, and sells home and office telecommunication products to retailers, telecommunication operators, and distributors worldwide. The company develops and distributes telephones, monitoring solutions, baby monitors, and conferencing phones under the Alcatel brand; and landline phones, smart home accessories, mobile phones, and various services to support and reassure senior users under the Swissvoice brand. It also provides sound telephones, headphones, accessories, and mobile phones under the Amplicomms brand. In addition, the company develops and trades in electrical equipment, including radio communication equipment; and manages trademarks. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong. Atlinks Group Limited is a subsidiary of Eiffel Global Limited.

Jiangsu NandaSoft Technology Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, sells computer hardware and software products primarily in the People's Republic of China. It operates through three segments: Computer Hardware and Software Products; System Integration Service; and Property Investment. The company also engages in the trading of information technology related products and equipment; provision of information technology training services; and developing, manufacturing, and marketing of network security software, Internet application software, education software, and business application software. In addition, it offers system integration services, services related to building installation, and information system integration; invests in properties; and researches and develops medicine and pharmaceutical equipment. Further, it provides biological medicine, properties management services, communication intelligence control systems, and online education services. The company was formerly known as Jiangsu NandaSoft Company Limited and changed its name to Jiangsu NandaSoft Technology Company Limited in September 2008. Jiangsu NandaSoft Technology Company Limited was founded in 1998 and is based in Nanjing, China.

China Ocean Fishing Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the supply chain management, money lending, and ocean fishing businesses in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company provides services involving the planning and implementation of an integrated solution for the flow of business, logistic, information, and funds to small and medium sized enterprises in various industries. It also offers money lending services to individuals. In addition, the company is involved in the fishing and catching business in an open sea. Further, it provides administration and ships building services; and trades in seafood products. The company was formerly known as Sky Forever Supply Chain Management Group Limited and changed its name to China Ocean Fishing Holdings Limited in November 2016. China Ocean Fishing Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

Yu Tak International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the development, sale, implementation, and maintenance of enterprise software products in the People's Republic of China and Southeast Asia. The company operates through Jewellery Products, and IT Products and Services segments. It designs, retails, and sells gold and jewellery products, including platinum, diamond, karat gold, and jade; sells enterprise software products; provides information technology, systems integration, and professional services; develops computer software; and offers sales and marketing services. The company was formerly known as Hong Kong Jewellery Holding Limited and changed its name to Yu Tak International Holdings Limited in October 2016. Yu Tak International Holdings Limited was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Jilin Province Huinan Changlong Bio-pharmacy Company Limited manufactures and distributes Chinese medicines and pharmaceutical products in the People's Republic of China. The company offers tablets, capsules, bulk drugs, pills, Chinese medicine pretreatment and extraction products, powders for injections, small volume parenteral solutions, APIs, and granules. It markets its products under the Changlong and Qing Tong brand names. The company was formerly known as Jilin Province Huinan Biochemical Pharmaceutical Company Limited. Jilin Province Huinan Changlong Bio-pharmacy Company Limited was founded in 1989 and is based in Mong Kok, Hong Kong.
longName: Jilin Province Huinan Changlong Bio-pharmacy Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Quantum Thinking Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the provision of system development and other value-added technical consultation services, and hardware-related businesses in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Hardware and Services segments. The Hardware segment sells telecommunication and enterprise hardware products. The Services segment provides system development, consultancy, and maintenance services. The company engages in developing and establishing integrated online platforms for the distribution of mobile products, as well as online network systems. In addition, it provides IT network consultation services; and trades in residential gateway products, as well as engages in the technical development and software development of identity authentication services related products. The company was formerly known as Yunbo Digital Synergy Group Limited and changed its name to Quantum Thinking Limited in December 2017. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong. Quantum Thinking Limited is a subsidiary of Happy On Holdings Limited.

CircuTech International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the research and development, manufacture, marketing, and sale of video surveillance systems in North America, Europe, Asia, Africa, and internationally. It is also involved in the distribution of third party IT products; and provision of repair, maintenance, and other support services for electronic products. The company was formerly known as TeleEye Holdings Limited and changed its name to CircuTech International Holdings Limited in August 2016. CircuTech International Holdings Limited was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong. CircuTech International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Hon Hai Precision Industry Co. Ltd.

Luk Hing Entertainment Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the food and beverage, and entertainment industry in Macau and Hong Kong. The company operates clubs and restaurants; and organizes music-related events, as well as grants loans to entities in the food and beverage, and entertainment industry. It is also involved in catering business. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.
longName: Luk Hing Entertainment Group Holdings Limited

longBusinessSummary: Pizu Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, trades in non-ferrous metals and bulk minerals in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in Bulk Mineral Trade, and Explosives Trading and Blasting Services segments. It also manufactures and sells civil explosives; and offers blasting operation and related services. The company was formerly known as China Electric Power Technology Holdings Limited and changed its name to Pizu Group Holdings Limited in May 2012. Pizu Group Holdings Limited is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

China E-Information Technology Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides occupational education, industry certification courses, skills training, and education consultation services in the People's Republic of China. The company principally provides an Internet platform for the facilitation of education program in Chinese medicine, and other advisory and training programs. It also offers distance learning program in Chinese medicine. The company was formerly known as China E-Learning Group Limited and changed its name to China E-Information Technology Group Limited in June 2017. China E-Information Technology Group Limited was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

Life Concepts Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates restaurants and bars in Italian style, Western style, and Asia style in Hong Kong. As of March 31, 2019, the company operated 27 restaurants, including 24 full-service and 3 bakery restaurants. It also provides catering management and design services; organizes promotional events for restaurants; and operates cricket club. The company was formerly known as Dining Concepts Holdings Limited and changed its name to Life Concepts Holdings Limited in July 2019. Life Concepts Holdings Limited was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Life Concepts Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Strong Day Holdings Limited.

Madison Holdings Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the retail and wholesale of various wine products and other alcoholic beverages in the People's of Republic of China, Europe, and Japan. It operates through Sales of Alcoholic Beverages, Financial Services, Blockchain Services, Loan Financing Services, and Auction segments. Its agency brands include Vega Sicilia, Roy Estate, Lail Vineyards, Amuse Bouche, and Bass Phillip. The company also offers wine storage services; financial consultancy services; securities and futures dealing services; loan financing, micro financing, and loan referral services; and alcoholic beverages auction services. In addition, it provides transaction verification and computing services. The company was formerly known as Madison Wine Holdings Limited and changed its name to Madison Holdings Group Limited in July 2017. Madison Holdings Group Limited is based in Wanchai, Hong Kong.
address1: Bank of East Asia Harbour View Centre

longBusinessSummary: Glory Flame Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the provision of construction works and building materials supply businesses in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, and the United States. The company operates through four segments: Construction, Agricultural Equipment, Trading Business, and Financial Services. It offers concrete demolition, construction engineering, and construction works; and concrete coring, wall sawing and diamond wire cutting, and bridge and road saw cutting, as well as environmental-friendly demolition through hydraulic crusher and burster, grouting and bar fixing, and various demolition robots. The company also develops and sells agricultural equipment; and trades in clean coal and light-emitting diode products for decoration. In addition, it offers insurance brokerage, consultancy, and commercial factoring services. Further, the company engages in the research and sale of LED cultivation cabinets and hydroponics products; and manufacture and sale of prestressed concrete piles and prefabricated precast construction components. Glory Flame Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.

Global Link Communications Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the development, production, sale, integration, supply, and service of rail transit passenger information management systems in the People's Republic of China and Hong Kong. It offers train-borne closed-circuit television systems, railway transit passenger information display systems, onboard public address and passenger information display systems in LED, and others. The company is also involved in the development of community mobile Internet applications and related services; and telecommunication application software, URT video surveillance system solutions, URT radio system solutions, intelligence video surveillance systems, value-added telecommunication service systems, and large-scale call center and board-band telecommunication systems, as well as technology products and integrated solutions. In addition, it provides spare parts and accessories; and technical support, system solutions, maintenance, and after-sale services, as well as holds software rights. The company serves government service departments and local public facilities, such as libraries, hospitals, gardens, schools, community smart service stations, public transport, shopping malls, residential housing, and interim rental housing. Global Link Communications Holdings Limited is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.

EFT Solutions Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides electronic fund transfer at point-of-sale (EFT-POS) solutions in Hong Kong, Australia, and internationally. It operates through Sale of Hardware Devices, and System Support and Software Solution Services segments. The company engages in sourcing EFT-POS terminals and peripheral devices, as well as providing EFT-POS system support services to various EFT-POS terminal manufacturers, acquirers, and merchants. It also provides value-added EFT-POS system support services, including installation, specification testing and electronic payment standards acceptance certification solutions, maintenance, collection, repair, and other related services of EFTPOS terminals. In addition, the company provides embedded system solution services. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong. EFT Solutions Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of LCK Group Limited.

Global Mastermind Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the travel business. The company operates through five segments: Travel Business, Treasury Management Business, Money Lending Business, Brokerage Business, and Asset Management Business. It offers travel related products and services, including airtickets, hotel rooms, free independent traveler packages, and ground transportation handling services for business travelers and travel services providers, as well as for corporate customers, convention organizers, and special projects organizers. The company also engages in the treasury management business; money lending business; securities brokerage, margin financing, securities advising businesses, and asset management business; and property holding business. In addition, it provides management services. Global Mastermind Holdings Limited has operations in Singapore, Hong Kong, and Malaysia. The company was formerly known as Well Way Group Limited and changed its name to Global Mastermind Holdings Limited in December 2015. Global Mastermind Holdings Limited is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

KML Technology Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides electrical and mechanical (E&M) engineering solutions and services in Hong Kong, Singapore, Taiwan, Canada, and internationally. It operates through E&M Engineering Solutions and Services; E&M Engineering Design and Fabrication Services; E&M Engineering Maintenance Services; and Sales of Parts and Components segments. The company provides electrical and mechanical engineering solutions and services for transportation mission critical system solutions, such as automatic fare collection system, electronic payment and ticketing system, road and tunnel toll collection system, traffic control and surveillance system, and railway signaling communication and control system. It also offers security and access control system services; railway station electrical and mechanical engineering services, and architectural works, including services in relation to air-conditioning and mechanical ventilation system, fire service system, plumbing and drainage system, and electrical system; and trackside and depot electrical and mechanical engineering works. In addition, the company provides engineering design and fabrication services for the fabrication of made-to-order products, such as control room consoles, public access kiosks and terminals, relay racks, test rigs, control room technical furniture, and industrial enclosures and instrument cabinets. Further, it offers rolling stock refurbishment and modification services; and railway and road transport infrastructure project services, as well as sells railway signaling parts and components. The company serves transportation companies, engineering companies, and governmental departments. KML Technology Group Limited was founded in 1977 and is headquartered in Shatin, Hong Kong.

Phoenitron Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the contract manufacturing and sales of smart cards. The company also sells petrochemical products; and develops and provides smart card application systems. It operates through five segments: Sales of Smart Cards; Sales of Smart Card Application Systems; Financial and Management Consultancy Services; Trading of Scrap Metal; and Sales of Petro-Chemical Products. The company also provides LNG services; financial and management consultancy services; and research and development, marketing, and sales services. In addition, it engages in the trading and dismantling of scrap vehicles. The company was formerly known as Cardlink Technology Group Limited and changed its name to Phoenitron Holdings Limited May 2010. Phoenitron Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong.

Oriental University City Holdings (H.K.) Limited, an investment holding company, leases education facilities in the People's Republic of China and Malaysia. The company leases primarily teaching buildings and dormitories to education institutions; and commercial spaces to tenants operating a range of supporting facilities, including grocery stores, laundry shops, Internet cafes, and canteens. Its campus site covers an area of approximately 487,270 square meters located in Oriental University City. The company owns teaching building with a total gross floor area of approximately 119,453 square meters and dormitories with a total gross floor area of approximately 144,490 square meters. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Langfang, the People's Republic of China. Oriental University City Holdings (H.K.) Limited is a subsidiary of Raffles Education Corporation Limited.

WWPKG Holdings Company Limited operates as a travel agent in Hong Kong and Macau. It designs, develops, and sells package tours; and sells air tickets and hotel accommodations, as well as ancillary travel related products and services under the WWPKG brand. The company was founded in 1979 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. WWPKG Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of WWPKG Investment Holdings Limited.

Keen Ocean International Holding Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, produces, and sells transformers, switching mode power supplies, enameled copper wires, electronic parts and components, and inverters. The company offers toroidal, EI, and distribution transformers; chokes, coils, and inductors; and original equipment manufacturer (OEM) products, such as OEM chargers, emergency ballasts, exit signs, handheld controllers, OEM PCB assemblies, and SMPS open flames. It also undertakes civil engineering works. The company sells its power supply products under the Keen Ocean brand. It primarily serves manufacturers and trading entities. The company operates in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, the United States, Europe, and internationally. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong. Keen Ocean International Holding Limited is a subsidiary of Cyber Goodie Limited.

China Netcom Technology Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides financial technology services in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Financial Technology Services Business, Apartment leasing Business, Smart Wearable Device Business, Lottery Business, and Sports Training Business segments. The company offers financial technology services, including credit referral and services, such as credit facilitation, post-origination, and financial guarantee services; and researches, develops, produces, wholesales, and sells smart wearable devices, smart glasses, and smart watches. It also develops computer software, hardware, and application system, as well as provides self-developed technology and related technical consultancy services to the operating system sector of lottery market. In addition, the company manages and leases apartments for property owners and lessees; and provides sports training services. Further, it company offers asset management services; and consultation and result transfer on network technology and computer network engineering services. The company was formerly known as China Metal Resources Holdings Limited and changed its name to China Netcom Technology Holdings Limited in January 2011. China Netcom Technology Holdings Limited is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.

Roma Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides valuation and technical advisory services in Hong Kong. The company offers valuation services for business and intangible assets, such as business contracts, mining and exploration rights, customer relationships, franchises, distribution and publicity rights, technology and software applications, trademarks, patents, copyrights, domain names, Websites, and publication rights; and natural resources valuation and technical advisory services, including exploration planning, project feasibility study, resource estimation, evaluation, environmental and social, and risk management services. It also provides valuation services for financial instruments comprising accumulators/decumulators, call and put options, convertible bonds, convertible preference shares, equity-linked investments, financial guarantees, forward/futures contracts, share options, structured products, swap contracts, and warrants; property valuation services for various types of properties; credit and risk evaluation services; biological assets valuation services; and purchase price allocation services, as well as various services for clients' antiques, work of art, and collectables. In addition, the company offers machineries and equipment valuation services for manufacturing processes and industrial facility installations; various technical advisory services; and corporate advisory services, such as business planning, feasibility studies, fairness opinions, risk control and management, alliance with other professional parties, advisory before issuance of financial instruments, and advisory on regulatory and accounting standards, as well as valuation-related consultancy services related to mergers and acquisitions, initial public offerings, private placements, and others. It provides marketing and event organization, financing, property investment, and ESG and credit reporting services. The company is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

China Singyes New Materials Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the research and development, manufacture, sale, and installation of indium tin oxide films and related downstream products in the People's Republic of China. The company offers smart light-adjusting films, smart light-adjusting glasses, smart light-adjusting projection systems, and home theaters. It also manufactures and sells photovoltaic products. China Singyes New Materials Holdings Limited serves touch-screen device manufacturers, construction companies, contractors of developers, and commercial users. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Zhuhai, the People's Republic of China. China Singyes New Materials Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Top Access Management Limited.
longName: China Singyes New Materials Holdings Limited

longBusinessSummary: Shenzhen Investment Holdings Bay Area Development Company Limited, an investment holding company, develops, operates, and manages expressways in the People's Republic of China. The company operates toll-expressway projects comprising Guangzhou-Shenzhen Superhighway, Phase I of the Western Delta Route, Phase II of the Western Delta Route, and Phase III of the Western Delta Route. It is also involved in loan financing activities. The company is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Shenzhen Investment Holdings Bay Area Development Company Limited is a subsidiary of Shenzhen Investment Holdings Co., Ltd.
longName: Shenzhen Investment Holdings Bay Area Development Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Media Asia Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as an entertainment company in Hong Kong, Mainland China, Macau, and internationally. The company operates through Media and Entertainment, and Film and TV Program segments. Its principal activities include film production and distribution; organization, management, and production of concerts and live performances; artiste management; production and distribution of television programs; music production and publishing; licensing of media contents; and provision of consultancy services in planning and management of cultural, entertainment, and live performance projects. The company was formerly known as Rojam Entertainment Holdings Limited and changed its name to Media Asia Group Holdings Limited in August 2011. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong. Media Asia Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of eSun Holdings Limited.

Sing Lee Software (Group) Limited, an investment holding company, develops and sells information and network technologies and services to the financial industry in the People's Republic of China. It is involved in the development and sale of software products; sale of related hardware products; and provision of technical support services. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Sing Lee Software (Group) Limited is a subsidiary of Goldcorp Industrial Limited.

China Creative Digital Entertainment Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the cultural and entertainment business. It is involved in the provision of artiste management services; production of music; and production and distribution of films and television programs. The company also engages in the money lending, securities and bonds investment, and property investment businesses; and provision of consultancy services. It operates in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, Taiwan, Japan, other Asian countries, North America, Europe, and internationally. The company was formerly known as HMV Digital China Group Limited and changed its name to China Creative Digital Entertainment Limited in May 2019. China Creative Digital Entertainment Limited is based in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong.
