It operates through Traditional Loans and Loans Financing, Third Party Payment Service, Online Investment and TechnologyEnabled Lending Service, Blockchain Services, and Others segments. The company offers traditional financial services and related financing consultancy services, including entrusted, real estate-backed, pawn, and other loan services, as well as microfinance services; and Internet financing services, such as third party payment and prepaid card issuance, online investment and technology-enabled lending, and related activities on loan portfolio management. In addition, it provides transaction verification, social gaming, IT solution, and exhibition services, as well as engages in money lending activities. The company operates in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, Vietnam, Canada, Singapore, and Georgia. The company was formerly known as Credit China FinTech Holdings Limited and changed its name to Chong Sing Holdings FinTech Group Limited in August 2017. Chong Sing Holdings FinTech Group Limited was founded in 2003 and is based in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong.
longName: Chong Sing Holdings FinTech Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: WMCH Global Investment Limited, an investment holding company, provides civil and structural engineering consultancy services to infrastructural, residential, industrial, commercial, and institutional projects in Singapore. It also offers master planning, structural due diligence, and visual inspection services to existing buildings. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Singapore. WMCH Global Investment Limited is a subsidiary of WMCH Global Holdings Limited.

DLC Asia Limited, an investment holding company, operates as an interdealer broker in Hong Kong. The company provides derivatives brokerage services to professional investors for SGX listed derivatives and HKEx listed single stock options. DLC Asia Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

Zhejiang Yongan Rongtong Holdings Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells woven fabrics in the People's Republic of China. It offers cotton, polyester, spandex, T/R, and fashion fabrics. The company also provides subcontracting, asset management, and investment advisory services. It also exports its products to the United States, Europe, Japan, South Africa, and Arabic countries. The company was formerly known as Zhejiang Yonglong Enterprises Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Zhejiang Yongan Rongtong Holdings Co., Ltd. in May 2017. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong. Zhejiang Yongan Rongtong Holdings Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of Guizhou Yongan Finance Holdings Company Ltd.
longName: Zhejiang Yongan Rongtong Holdings Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: Celebrate International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the money lending activities in Hong Kong. The company operates through six segments: Trading of Food and Beverage; Money Lending; Health Care Services; Securities Investment and Trading; Logistic Services; and Property Investment. It is involved in the trading of food and beverage; provision of hot stone spa and health related services; purchasing and selling securities and investments; and property investment business. The company also provides logistic services comprising general services in palletization, receiving and delivery, and custom clearance for air and ocean cargoes, as well as warehousing. The company was formerly known as Hong Kong Life Group Holdings Limited and changed its name to Celebrate International Holdings Limited in August 2012. Celebrate International Holdings Limited is headquartered in North Point, Hong Kong.

StarGlory Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides food and beverage services. The company operates restaurants, café, and cake shops under the Italian Tomato brand name; the Japanese Tonkatsu restaurants under the Ginza Bairin brand; the Japanese curry specialty stores under the Shirokuma Curry brand; and the Japanese Izakaya restaurants under the Enmaru brand. As of March 31, 2019, it operated 29 shops in Hong Kong and 7 shops in the People's Republic of China. The company was formerly known as New Wisdom Holding Company Limited and changed its name to StarGlory Holdings Company Limited in April 2019. StarGlory Holdings Company Limited was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. As of April 25, 2019, StarGlory Holdings Company Limited operates as a subsidiary of Oceanic Fortress Holdings Limited.

Luen Wong Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a subcontractor in civil engineering works in Hong Kong. It undertakes civil engineering works, including roads and drainage works; structural works; and site formation works. The company also provides decoration and renovation works. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.

Echo International Holdings Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides integrated manufacturing services in Hong Kong, other Asian countries, Europe, North and South America, and internationally. It offers design verification, procurement, manufacturing, assembling, testing and inspection, packaging, and after-sales services for its branded customers. The company's products include PCB assemblies used in beauty, fishing, security, and other electronic related products. It also offers manufacturing and assembly services for electronic products, such as security alarms, buzzers, fire alarms, massage toners, fishing indicators, and communicators; and trades in electronic products and accessories. In addition, the company provides food catering services. The company was formerly known as Gold Treasure Hung Holdings Limited and changed its name to Echo International Holdings Group Limited in January 2012. Echo International Holdings Group Limited was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong.

Hanvey Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the design and development, manufacture, and distribution of watch products on an original design manufacturing basis. The company offers female and male watches, such as metal and non-metal banded, mechanical, and quartz movement watches under the Grandber brand name; and semi-knocked-down kits and watch parts. It serves watch manufacturers, brand owners, and watch importers primarily in Indonesia, Hong Kong, Brazil, India, the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, Australia, the United Arab Emirates, Turkey, Sweden, Spain, Singapore, and Germany. The company was founded in 1986 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong. Hanvey Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Million Easy Enterprises Ltd.

Bingo Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the cinema investment and management business in the People's Republic of China and internationally. The company operates through two segments, Cinema Investment and Management; and Filmed Entertainment, New Media Exploitations and Licensing Businesses. It engages in movie production; licensing and derivatives; crossover marketing; the provision of interactive contents; artist development; last miles engagement; and cartoon production activities. The company is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong. Bingo Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Beglobal Investments Limited.

PF Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides services primarily related to equity and debt securities traded on the Stock Exchange in Hong Kong. The company offers securities dealing and brokerage services; placing and underwriting services; financing services, including securities and initial public offering margin financing; and asset management services. It also provides ancillary services that include application for new issues and nominee services, such as collection of cash and scrip dividends. In addition, it offers referral services in relation to fund raising related and other projects. The company was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. PF Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Thoughtful Mind Limited.

Ziyuanyuan Holdings Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides finance leasing services in the People's Republic of China. The company offers equipment-based finance leasing services, such as sale-leaseback and direct finance leasing services to small and medium-sized enterprises in the printing, logistics, transportation, and medical device industries. It also provides technological services and money lending services. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China. Ziyuanyuan Holdings Group Limited is a subsidiary of Hero Global Limited.

China Health Group Inc., an investment holding company, provides clinical research services to pharmaceutical and biotechnology companies in the People's Republic of China. The company offers contracted clinical research services; contracted pharmaceutical development services; post launch market research, medical, and medical market services; medical science liaisons; and other medical services. It also provides hospital management, specialized hospital, and medical tourism services, as well as Venturepharma cloud; and sells drugs technologies. The company was formerly known as Venturepharm Laboratories Limited and changed its name to China Health Group Inc. in January 2015. China Health Group Inc. was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

KOALA Financial Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the securities investment, underwriting and placing, and brokerage activities in Hong Kong. It is involved in the trading of commodities; leasing of investment properties; and asset management, as well as money lending activities. The company was formerly known as Sunrise (China) Technology Group Limited and changed its name to KOALA Financial Group Limited in June 2017. KOALA Financial Group Limited is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

Xi'an Haitian Antenna Technologies Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, researches and develops, manufactures, installs, and sells base station antennas and related products in the People's Republic of China and other Asian countries. The company offers underwater and underground surveillance, imaging, mechanical equipment, and other related products; complicated environment warning and surveillance equipment; and agricultural and forestry used unmanned aerial vehicles, as well as consultancy services. It also trades in construction related products; and poultry and agricultural products. The company was formerly known as Xi'an Haitiantian Holdings Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Xi'an Haitian Antenna Technologies Co., Ltd. in August 2019. Xi'an Haitian Antenna Technologies Co., Ltd. is headquartered in Xi'an, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Xi'an Haitian Antenna Technologies Co., Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: National Arts Entertainment and Culture Group Limited, an investment holding company, produces and distributes films primarily in the People's Republic of China. It operates in three segments: Films Production and Distribution, Sales of Travel Related Products, Artiste Management and Event Coordination; Film Studio Operation; and Hotel Operation. The company also sells travel related products; and provides artiste management and event coordination services. In addition, it operates film studios, hotels, theme parks, and restaurants; offers promotional performance; engages in property development and operations; and retails souvenirs. The company was formerly known as National Arts Holdings Limited and changed its name to National Arts Entertainment and Culture Group Limited in June 2013. National Arts Entertainment and Culture Group Limited is headquartered in Shatin, Hong Kong.
longName: National Arts Entertainment and Culture Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: Future Data Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides system integration and maintenance services in South Korea and Hong Kong. The company offers integrated systems with network connectivity, cloud computing, and security elements. It serves small and medium enterprises, multinational corporations, and government-owned entities. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Seoul, South Korea. Future Data Group Limited is a subsidiary of LiquidTech Limited.

China Yu Tian Holdings Limited engages in the research, development, manufacture, and sale of industrial coated products in the People's Republic of China. It offers coated architectural glass products, coated glass production equipment, and capacitive touch panel (CTP) module components, as well as handset accessories. The company was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Huaian, the People's Republic of China.

Classified Group (Holdings) Limited, an investment holding company, owns and operates restaurants in Hong Kong. Its restaurants provide western cuisine in casual dining and full service environments. As of December 31, 2018, the company operated 11 restaurants, including 10 brand restaurants and 1 The Pawn restaurant. Classified Group (Holdings) Limited also franchises its brands, as well as provides management services. The company was formerly known as Press Room Group (Holdings) Limited and changed its name to Classified Group (Holdings) Limited in February 2016. Classified Group (Holdings) Limited was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Wong Chuk Hang, Hong Kong.

CCID Consulting Company Limited provides consulting services in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Management and Strategic Consultancy Services, Market Consultancy Services, Information Engineering Supervision Services, and Other segments. The Management and Strategic Consultancy Services segment offers services comprising the application and implementation of enterprise management information digitalization, which incorporates the functions of business process re-engineering, enterprise resource planning, customer relationship management, supply chain management, call center and other electronic business pattern designs, marketing, brand name promotion, public relationship, and advertising. The Market Consultancy Services segment provides standard research on specific sectors and tailor-made research services. The Information Engineering Supervision Services segment offers information engineering supervision services to the undertaken projects. The Other segment provides data information management and training services. It also offers investment and economic consultancy services. CCID Consulting Company Limited is based in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Powerleader Science & Technology Group Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides cloud computing solutions in the People's Republic of China and Hong Kong. It operates through Supply of Servers, Storage and Solutions; Distribution of Electronic Equipment and Accessories; Guangzhou Internet Data Centre (IDC) Business; and Industrial Park Development, Operation and Property Management segments. The Supply of Servers, Storage and Solutions segment provides cloud servers solutions; and cloud storage and other related equipment and services. The Distribution of Electronic Equipment and Accessories segment offers distribution services for new energy, consumer electronics, electronic components, LCD, and IoT products, as well as for other products and accessories. The Guangzhou IDC Business segment provides IDC cabinet and broadband services. The Industrial Park Development, Operation and Property Management segment engages in the development and operation of industrial parks; and property leasing and management businesses. Powerleader Science & Technology Group Limited also offers software and information technology; and technical consultation services. The company was formerly known as Shenzhen Powerleader Science & Technology Limited. Powerleader Science & Technology Group Limited was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, China.

Link Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the hotel business in Singapore, Indonesia, and Japan. It owns and operates Link Hotel, a 4-storey boutique-style hotel with 288 guest rooms and suites located in Tiong Bahru estate, Singapore. The company is also involved in property investment, cottage, and real estate businesses. In addition, it offers distressed debt asset management services in the People's Republic of China. Link Holdings Limited was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong. Link Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Vertic Holdings Limited.
address1: West Tower of Shun Tak Centre

longBusinessSummary: Winto Group (Holdings) Limited engages in the publishing, sale, and free distribution of Chinese language lifestyle magazines in Hong Kong and Mainland China. It owns and publishes Motoz Trader, a fortnightly magazine that focuses on new car models, second-hand car market, and properties, as well as provides lifestyle information, including dinning, fashion, and beauty; Motoz Trader (Free), a free fortnightly magazine; Shopping Monthly, a fortnightly magazine and focuses on updated information on consumer products; and Shopping Monthly (Free), a free fortnightly magazine that is extracted from Shopping Monthly. The company's magazines cover various areas of interests in lifestyle, including automotive, beauty and fashion, property, dining, and electronic products. It also provides outdoor advertising services; develops mobile phone apps; and provides apps solutions, as well as online marketing planning and production services. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

Ying Kee Tea House Group Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a Chinese tea leaves retailer for individual and corporate customers in Hong Kong. It offers various tea products, including pu-erh, old luk on, white, black, oolong, green, fragrant, and miscellaneous tea products; and tea wares and tea gift sets under the Ying Kee Tea House brand name. As of March 13, 2018, the company operated seven retail shops and three concession counters. The company also offers products through its Website; and through platforms provided by business partners, exhibitions, and/or other booth sales, as well as direct sale to commercial customers. Ying Kee Tea House Group Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Siu Sai Wan, Hong Kong. Ying Kee Tea House Group Limited operates as a subsidiary of Profit Ocean Enterprises Limited.
longName: Ying Kee Tea House Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: As of October 25, 2018, New Western Group Limited (SEHK:8242) operates as a subsidiary of Champsword Limited.

Dahe Media Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in outdoor media dissemination, terminal dissemination, outdoor advertising media production, and artwork trading businesses in the People's Republic of China. It disseminates outdoor advertising through owning and leasing outdoor advertising space; and designs and produces outdoor advertising products. The company is also involved in the cultural and art exchange activities; franchising of advertising boards; and provision of training, as well as integrated marketing communication consultation, media publication strategy consultancy, and monitoring and evaluation services. It primarily serves fast moving consumer goods, media, real estate, finance, tourism, and other industries. The company was founded in 1994 and is based in Nanjing, the People's Republic of China. Dahe Media Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of Dahe Investment Holdings Group, Co., Ltd.

On Real International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, manufactures, trades in, and sells two-way radios, baby monitors, and other communication devices on original design manufacturing basis. The company provides product design and development, sourcing and procurement, production and assembly, sales, marketing and logistics, and after-sales services. Its two-way radio product range includes consumer grade radios, such as FRS/GMRS radios and PMR radios; and commercial grade radios comprising emergency and weather alert radios, marine handheld floating radios, and dPMR radios. The company's baby monitor product range includes analog audio baby monitors, digital audio baby monitors, and digital video baby monitors. In addition, the company is involved in the technology development activities; and trades in plastic covers. It operates in the United States, Germany, the Netherlands, the United Kingdom, other European countries, Asia, and internationally. On Real International Holdings Limited was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.

Zhonghua Gas Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the new energy, catering, and property investments businesses in the People's Republic of China. The New Energy Business segment provides integrated new energy services, including technological development, construction, and consultancy services for heat supply and coal-to-natural gas conversion. This segment also sells and transmits liquefied natural gas (LNG); and operates LNG stations, as well as trades new energy related industrial products. The Catering Business segment owns and operates restaurants; provides management services to restaurants owned by the independent third parties; and sells non-staple food. As of December 31, 2018, the company owned and operated four restaurants under the Noble House brand in Shanghai. The Property Investments Segment rents and leases investment properties. Zhonghua Gas Holdings Limited is also involved in the food processing and money lending activities. The company was formerly known as Northern New Energy Holdings Limited and changed its name to Zhonghua Gas Holdings Limited in September 2018. Zhonghua Gas Holdings Limited is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

Biosino Bio-Technology and Science Incorporation, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures, sells, and distributes in-vitro diagnostic reagent products primarily in Mainland China. It offers clinical chemistry reagents, including single and double reagents, calibrators, QC products, and washing solution detergents; flow cytometers and clinical chemistry analyzers; Elisa kits; and rapid tests. The company also provides medical and medical inspection services; produces medical instruments; distributes immunodiagnostic products; and offers investment management services, as well as consulting services related to non-securities business and equity investment management. Further, it leases commercial and office buildings. The company also exports its products. Biosino Bio-Technology and Science Incorporation was founded in 1988 and is based in Beijing, China.

Zhejiang RuiYuan Intelligent Control Technology Company Limited designs, manufactures, and sells intelligent controller systems for consumer electrical and electronic appliances in the People's Republic of China. It is also involved in the assembly of mobile phones; original equipment manufacturing and electronic subassembly activities; and trading of electronic components, industrial electronic intelligent control equipment, and electronic automation digital control systems. The company was formerly known as Ningbo WanHao Holdings Company Limited and changed its name to Zhejiang RuiYuan Intelligent Control Technology Company Limited in January 2017. The company is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. As of April 7, 2017, Zhejiang RuiYuan Intelligent Control Technology Company Limited operates as a subsidiary of Zhejiang Ruiyuan Intelligent Robot Company Limited.
longName: Zhejiang RuiYuan Intelligent Control Technology Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Silk Road Energy Services Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides coal mining services in the Peoples Republic of China. It operates through Coal Mining Services, Money Lending, and Heating supply Services segments. The company offers mine construction engineering, mechanical equipment installation, and coal production and technical services; and trades in mineral products. It also provides money lending and heating supply services. The company was formerly known as China Natural Investment Company Limited and changed its name to Silk Road Energy Services Group Limited in August 2015. Silk Road Energy Services Group Limited is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.
longName: Silk Road Energy Services Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: China Binary New Fintech Group, an investment holding company, provides online transaction services in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Online Transaction Services, Micro Financing Facilitating Services, and Software Technology Services and Sale of Smart Hardware Products segments. It facilitates transactions between online game operators and online game users; and offers mobile top-up services to mobile subscribers, as well as micro financing facilitating services, including financing guarantee services to individual borrowers and lenders; and software technology services and sales of smart hardware products. The company is also involved in the distribution of online game products; and provision of information technology and advertising services. In addition, it designs and develops tailor made cryptocurrencies trading platform systems. The company was formerly known as China Binary Sale Technology Limited and changed its name to China Binary New Fintech Group in July 2018. China Binary New Fintech Group was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Genes Tech Group Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a turnkey solution provider and trades in used semiconductor manufacturing equipment (SME) and parts in Taiwan. The company's services include tool relocation, tool refurbishment, equipment module modification, repairmen, and parts supply of SME. It provides SME and parts, such as furnaces and clean tracks used in semiconductor manufacturing process and wafer fabrication, which includes deposition, photoresist coating, and development. It operates in Taiwan, the People's Republic of China, South Korea, Japan, Singapore, the United States, and internationally. Genes Tech Group Holdings Company Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Zhubei City, Taiwan. Genes Tech Group Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of Queenbest Development Limited.
longName: Genes Tech Group Holdings Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Shaanxi Northwest New Technology Industry Company Limited engages in the research and development, production, and sale of environmental protection energy material and products, fuel oil additives, petroleum processing aids, and oil field chemicals in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Unleaded Gasoline Additives and Mercaptoacetic Acid Isooctyl segments. Its principal products include FA-90 unleaded gasoline additive and 2-ethylhexyl thioglycolate (thiol products). The company was incorporated in 1999 and is based in Xi'an, the People's Republic of China. Shaanxi Northwest New Technology Industry Company Limited is a subsidiary of Xi'an Northwest Industry (Group) Company Limited.
longName: Shaanxi Northwest New Technology Industry Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Hon Corporation Limited, an investment holding company, provides construction services in Singapore. The company undertakes building and infrastructure projects, including institutional, industrial, commercial, and residential buildings in public and private sectors. It also undertakes interior works of an institution, apartment, office, or other structural space; and provides a range of works and services, including repair and renovation, addition and alteration works, and installation of mechanical and electrical systems. The company serves government agencies and private companies. Hon Corporation Limited was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Singapore.

Yin He Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides human resources services in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through five segments: Human Resources Services, Credit Consultancy Services, Loan Facilitation Services, Asset Management Services, and Loan Financing Services. It offers staff outsourcing services, executive/staff search, and other human resources support services; credit assessment and consultancy services; financial advisory services for corporate, asset management firms, private equity funds, and minority investments in private companies; and loan financing services. Yin He Holdings Limited also operates peer-to-peer financing platform and other loan facilitation business, as well as provision of other relevant consultation services. In addition, it engages in insurance training business. The company was formerly known as Zebra Strategic Holdings Limited and changed its name to Yin He Holdings Limited in January 2016. Yin He Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Super Strong Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides property construction and building management services in Hong Kong. It undertakes general and specialized building, demolition, site formation, foundation, electrical engineering, and superstructure and decoration patent works. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Tokwawan, Hong Kong.

China Trustful Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the research, development, manufacturing, and sale of rechargeable lithium batteries, electric vehicles, and related products and services in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Silverware Business and Electric Vehicle Business segments. The company also retails and wholesales silverwares, silver utensils, and luxury goods. In addition, it trades in electric vehicles and related products, as well as offers related consultancy services. The company was formerly known as Powerwell Pacific Holdings Limited and changed its name to China Trustful Group Limited in June 2017. China Trustful Group Limited was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Zhuoxin International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the trading of electronic parts and components in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through three segments: Trading of Electronic Parts and Components, Property Development, and Property Investment. It trades in display and touch panel modules, as well as provides professional solutions with engineering services. The company is also involved in the development and sale of properties; and property investment. In addition, it offers human resources management services. The company was formerly known as Gold Tat Group International Limited and changed its name to Zhuoxin International Holdings Limited in February 2018. Zhuoxin International Holdings Limited is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong.

Linekong Interactive Group Co., Ltd., an investment holding company, researches, develops, and publishes online games in the People's Republic of China and internationally. It operates through two segments, Game Business and Film Business. The company distributes its self-developed games and licensed games through its own game distribution channels, third-party game distribution channels, payment collection channels, and prepaid game card distributors. It also offers technology consulting and services; and produces and distributes film and television drama series. The company was formerly known as Linekong Interactive Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Linekong Interactive Group Co., Ltd. in June 2015. Linekong Interactive Group Co., Ltd. was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Deson Construction International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a contractor in the building industry in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and Macau. It operates in three segments: Construction Business, Securities Investment, and Property Investment. The Construction Business segment undertakes building construction works; electrical and mechanical engineering works; and alteration, addition, renovation, refurbishment, and fitting-out works, as well as provides decoration engineering services. The Securities Investment segment invests in long term and short term marketable securities. The Property Investment segment invests in, acquires, and rents properties. The company was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong.

Wealth Glory Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the trade of natural resources and commodities in the People's Republic of China, Indonesia, the United States, and internationally. It operates through Natural Resources and Commodities; Branding, Trendy Fashion Merchandise and Other Consumers Products; Money Lending; and Securities Investments segments. The company engages in the trade of iron ore concentrate, coal, crude palm oil, etc. It is also involved in the trade of fashion items, camera bags, and sports cars. In addition, the company distributes vehicles; develops and promotes brands; and designs, manufactures, and sells fashion merchandises and other consumer products. Wealth Glory Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.

China CBM Group Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the exploitation, liquefaction production, and sale of natural gas in the People's Republic of China. The company sells piped natural gas; provides gas supply connection and liquefied coalbed gas logistics services; explores for, develops, produces, and sells coalbed methane; distributes gas; and manufactures and sells PE gas pipelines. It serves industrial, commercial, and residential customers. The company was formerly known as China Leason CBM & Shale Gas Group Company Limited and changed its name to China CBM Group Company Limited in May 2014. China CBM Group Company Limited was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.

Global Digital Creations Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the computer graphic (CG) creation and production, and property leasing and building management services. The CG Creation and Production segment is involved in the CG creation and production; production and exhibition of television series and movies; and production of animated films. This segment also holds copyrights of original animated films and animated television series. The Property leasing and building management services segment engages in the property rental and building management activities. The company also provides administration and management services; invests in animation business; invests in culture, entertainment, and related commercial properties; and develops multimedia software and hardware, as well as offers related technical consultancy services. It operates in the People's Republic of China, Denmark, Korea, Hungary, Hong Kong, the United States, and France. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in North Point, Hong Kong.

Chinese Food and Beverage Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in catering business in Hong Kong. The company operates through Catering Business and Securities Trading segments. It is involved in the operation of Chinese restaurants in Hong Kong; and securities investment and trading activities. The company was formerly known as Best Miracle International Limited and changed its name to Chinese Food and Beverage Group Limited in August 2011. Chinese Food and Beverage Group Limited was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.
longName: Chinese Food and Beverage Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: Beaver Group (Holding) Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides foundation work and ancillary services in Hong Kong and Macau. The company undertakes bored piling and other foundation works. It also offers management services for construction works; and machinery rental and leasing services. Beaver Group (Holding) Company Limited was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong.

Steed Oriental (Holdings) Company Limited, an investment holding company, sources, manufactures, and sells plywood and other wooden products in Japan, Mainland China, Thailand, Hong Kong, and internationally. The company provides general plywood used for manufacture of furniture for home and office; packing plywood used for packaging; structural panels for house construction; floor base products for flooring applications; and other plywood products, such as concrete panels for exterior construction. It sells its plywood products to construction materials trading companies and wholesalers; retailers, including supermarkets; flooring and furniture manufacturers; and individual or corporate end-users. Steed Oriental (Holdings) Company Limited was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

AGTech Holdings Limited, an integrated technology and services company, engages in the lottery, and mobile games and entertainment content businesses in the People's Republic of China and internationally. Its hardware and terminal products cover lottery hardware, including traditional draw-based lottery sales terminals, self-service terminals for instant win lottery and draw-based lottery, video lottery terminal of new draw-based lottery sales terminals, built-in instant win lottery module, instant ticket verification terminals, cloud printing devices, etc.; and keno products and instant scratch cards. The company is also involved in the development and supply of lottery games, related software, and underlying supporting systems; distribution of online non-lottery games and entertainment content; sale and distribution of lottery games and products; and provision of maintenance, after-sales, training, and consultancy services for software games and systems. In addition, it provides sports lottery management and marketing consultancy services; and phone and mobile betting solutions for lottery organizations, as well as offers handheld lottery sales equipment and related after-sales maintenance services. The company is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong. AGTech Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Ali Fortune Investment Holding Limited.

China Digital Video Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the research and development, manufacture, and sale of video related and broadcasting equipment and software to television broadcasters, media operators, and other digital video content providers in the People's Republic of China. The company offers graphics creation, video capture and editing, and visual effects and video compositing products; and convergent media, news workflow, studio, program production, entertainment, sports and events, media management, digital broadcast automation, multi-functional platform, media operation, and professional application solutions. It also provides cloud platform, post production, visual art integration, show field production, games broadcast television and games information system, media assets cataloguing, and sports events data sharing system services. China Digital Video Holdings Limited was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

China Golden Classic Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and trades in oral care, leather care, and household hygiene products in China and internationally. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Jiangyin, China.

Gameone Holdings Limited, an integrated game developer, develops, operates, publishes, and distributes mobile, online PC, and Web games in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, and Taiwan. It serves game players. The company was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in North Point, Hong Kong.

Zheng Li Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides a range of passenger car services. The company offers maintenance and repair, modification, tuning, and grooming services; and trades in passenger car spare parts and accessories in Singapore, as well as exports to Malaysia, Indonesia, the United Kingdom, the People's Republic of China, and Thailand. It also provides timeshare and long-term car rental services; and car rental and sales integrated service platform. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Singapore.

Sling Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, promotes, and sells women's handbags, small leather goods, luggage products, and travel goods in the People's Republic of China. It provides handle bags, clutch bags, wallets, coin cases, card holders, and suitcases under the ELLE, and Jessie & Jane brands. The company offers its products to end customers through 3 self-operated stores and 90 offline retail points; and third party online retail platforms. It also exports its products. The company was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. Sling Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Yen Sheng Investment Limited.

Shanxi Changcheng Microlight Equipment Co. Ltd. engages in the research, design, development, manufacture, and sale of image transmission fiber optic products in the People's Republic of China, Europe, Hong Kong, Russia, and Taiwan. The company's primary products include fiber optic inverters, fiber optic straight plates, fiber optic face plates, fiber optic tapers, and microchannel plates. It is also involved in the wholesale of household water purifiers; and manufacture and sale of optoelectronic and chemical glass products. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Taiyuan, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Shanxi Changcheng Microlight Equipment Co. Ltd.

longBusinessSummary: Zioncom Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells networking and non-networking products for home use and small scale commercial applications. It offers routers for wired and wireless transmission of data; and wired and wireless networking products, such as Ethernet switches, LAN cards, Wi-Fi modules, and access points, as well as non-networking products, including power banks and USB hubs. The company provides its products under the TOTOLINK brand name. It has operations in Korea, the People's Republic of China, Vietnam, other Asian countries, Europe, South America, Africa, North America, and Central America. The company was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China. Zioncom Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Lincats (BVI) Limited.

Ahsay Backup Software Development Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides online backup software products and services to IT consultants, Web hosting companies, telecommunications companies, and MSPs in the United States, the United Kingdom, and internationally. The company sells and leases software license; and sells hardware devices, as well as provides software upgrade and maintenance, and other services under the Ahsay brand name. It also offers information sharing services through KINTIPS, a trading platform for information providers, such as horse racing and football tipsters; and subscribers to share information through its Website or mobile application. The company was formerly known as Ahsay Cloud Backup Software Development Company Ltd. Ahsay Backup Software Development Company Limited was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Lai Chi Kok, Hong Kong.
longName: Ahsay Backup Software Development Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Wan Cheng Metal Packaging Company Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells tinplate packaging products in the People's Republic of China. The company offers tin cans in cylindrical and rectangular shapes; aerosol cans; and steel pails for storing paint and coatings. It serves paint and coatings suppliers; and other manufacturers of packaging products. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Foshan, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Wan Cheng Metal Packaging Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: SingAsia Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides workforce solutions in Singapore. The company offers manpower outsourcing services, manpower recruitment services, and manpower training services. The company also provides cleaning services. It offers workforce solutions for the hotel and resort, retail, and food and beverage sectors; educational institutions; event organizers; and other industries. SingAsia Holdings Limited was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Singapore.

ZZ Capital International Limited, an investment holding company, provides corporate advisory and loan financing services in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, the United Kingdom, and the United States. It also offers investment advisory and asset management, and money lending services. The company was formerly known as Asian Capital Holding Limited and changed its name to ZZ Capital International Limited in August 2016. ZZ Capital International Limited was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. ZZ Capital International Limited is a subsidiary of Jinhui Capital Company Ltd.

Sino-Life Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides funeral services. It operates through Funeral Services  Taiwan, Funeral Services  Hong Kong, Funeral Services  the PRC, Funeral Services  Vietnam, and Elderly Care and Related Consultancy Services  Taiwan segments. The company offers funeral arrangement services to funeral and non-funeral services deed holders; and cremation services in funeral parlours and funeral service centers. It also sells burial plots and tombstones; and provides cemetery maintenance services, as well as elderly care and related consultancy services. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong.

My Heart Bodibra Group Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and sells lingerie products. It offers bras, body shaping underwear, and chest support vests, as well as complementary and ancillary products, primarily breast creams, panties, nude bras, swimwear, bra straps and pads, and waist bands. The company is also involved in trading of garments; and the provision of beauty services. It operates retail stores in Hong Kong, Macau, and the People's Republic of China. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. My Heart Bodibra Group Limited is a subsidiary of Global Succeed Group Limited.

Grand T G Gold Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the exploration, mining, processing, and sale of gold properties in the People's Republic of China. It holds interest in the Taizhou gold mines in the Tongguan county, Shaanxi province. The company is headquartered in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.
longName: Grand T G Gold Holdings Limited

longBusinessSummary: Royal Catering Group Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides casual dining food catering services in Hong Kong. The company operates two restaurants under the Chinese Kitchen and Macao Harbour brands at the Hong Kong International Airport; and seven restaurants under the Du Hsiao Yueh Restaurant, Hanlin Tea Room/Hut, Flamingo Bloom, and Da Shia Taiwan brands in the urban area of Hong Kong. It is also involved in the sale of beverages and light refreshments; property investment business; provision of human resources management services; and holding of trademarks and franchises. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Royal Catering Group Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of Fortune Round Limited.
longName: Royal Catering Group Holdings Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Shenzhen Mingwah Aohan High Technology Corporation Limited, together with its subsidiaries, designs, develops, manufactures, and sales IC cards, magnetic cards and related equipment, and application systems in the People's Republic of China. It operates through Card Products, Non-Card Products, and Liquor Products segments. The company's products include radio frequency identification device (RFID) solutions used in telecommunications, digital communications, computer, general electronics, network equipment, automotive, and medical equipment fields; RFID cards; and hand-held terminals, contact and contactless cards, dual interfaces, and module readers. It also offers CPU cards and smart chip operating systems; IC cards; WLAN products; eKey, which is used for ID verification, encryption/decryption, digital signature, and safe data storage; RFID rewritable cards and hybrid thermal printing systems; and administrative support services. In addition, the company trades in liquor products. Shenzhen Mingwah Aohan High Technology Corporation Limited was founded in 1993 and is based in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Shenzhen Mingwah Aohan High Technology Corporation Limited

longBusinessSummary: Tong Kee (Holding) Limited operates as a multi-disciplinary contractor in the construction industry. It is involved in the repair, alteration and addition, maintenance, modification, rehabilitation, steel, civil, and demolition works in various venues, such as residential buildings, commercial buildings, carparks, roads, footbridges, and theme parks. The company also undertakes new construction works projects, including noise mitigation works, architectural metal works, bus shelters, and dangerous goods store building, as well as innovative and creative structure comprising air balloons. In addition, it engages in the installation of cathodic protection systems consisting of sacrificial anodes protection and impressed current systems. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Sha Tin, Hong Kong.

Medicskin Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides medical skin care services in Hong Kong. The company operates Medicskin centres, which provides various medical skin care services for the treatment of skin diseases and problems, such as acne, pigmentation, rosacea, dermatitis, eczema, and warts; improvement of appearance through skin rejuvenation, facial sculpturing, and body contouring treatments; and treatment of acne scars and enlarged pores, removal of undesirable naevi, and hair removal. It is also involved in the sale of skincare products; provision of skin care and health management services; and property holding activities. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Medicskin Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Topline Worldwide Limited.

Gudou Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates and manages hot spring resort and hotel facilities in Guangdong Province, the People's Republic of China. It operates through two segments, Property Development, and Hotel and Resort Operation. The company also develops and sells tourism properties, such as villas, high-rise apartments, low-rise apartments, low-rise studio flats, and commercial units in Gudou Hot Spring Resort, as well as operates an entertainment business in the resort. In addition, it provides property management services. The company was formerly known as Gudou International Holdings Limited and changed its name to Gudou Holdings Limited in October 2015. Gudou Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Jiangmen, the People's Republic of China.

Man Shing Global Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides environmental cleaning services in Hong Kong. The company offers street cleaning solutions, which include street and public area, and refuse collection point cleaning, as well as pest control; building cleaning services, including general building cleaning, refuse collection and waste disposal, toilet cleaning, and janitorial services; and bus and ferry cleaning services, such as general depot and pier cleaning, vehicle and vessel cleaning, refuse collection and waste disposal, and toilet cleaning. It also provides other cleaning services comprising sewage management and fumigation services, as well as external wall and window, and confined space cleaning services. The company serves government, private, and public transport sector customers. Man Shing Global Holdings Limited was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong.

Dafeng Port Heshun Technology Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in trading business in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, and internationally. The company operates through Integrated Logistics Freight Services; Provision of Fuel Cards; Tractor Repair and Maintenance Services, and Insurance Agency Services; Trading Business; and Petrochemical Products Storage Business segments. It trades in wood logs, scrap metals, textile products, electronic products, sugar, coal, petrochemical products, etc. The company also engages in the petrochemical products storage business. In addition, the company provides integrate logistics handling services, including ocean freight and land transportation, and container drayage services; ocean freight and air forwarding services; supply chain management; feeder container storage facilities; and hiring services of barges and vehicles, as well as manufactures and trades in tin wires. Further, it offers freight, feeder, and truck rental services; land freight services; and non-vessel operating common carrier and international forwarding agency services, as well as provides tractor repair and maintenance. The company was formerly known as Gamma Logistics Corporation and changed its name to Dafeng Port Heshun Technology Company Limited in May 2015. Dafeng Port Heshun Technology Company Limited was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong. Dafeng Port Heshun Technology Company Limited is a subsidiary of Dafeng Port Overseas Investment Holdings Limited.
longName: Dafeng Port Heshun Technology Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Perfect Optronics Limited, an investment holding company, engages in trading display components for electronics in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in two segments, Display Products and Optics Products. Its product portfolio includes thin film transistor liquid crystal display panels and modules, driver integrated circuits, and polarizers. The company also designs, develops, manufactures, and sells optics products and related electronic components, such as virtual reality entertainment headsets and automotive head-up display devices. In addition, it offers technical support and related services. Perfect Optronics Limited was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. Perfect Optronics Limited is a subsidiary of Winful Enterprises Limited.

ZACD Group is a real estate investment firm. The firm seeks to invest in industrial properties, data centres, and high-end residential segment with a focus on discounted luxury homes in Singapore and student accommodation in Australia. It typically invests in the Asia Pacific. ZACD Group was founded in 2005 and is based in Singapore with an additional office in Hong Kong.

Greatwalle Inc., an investment holding company, provides manned security guarding services in Hong Kong and the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Security Guarding, Mobile Game, and e-Education segments. The Security Guarding segment offers security guarding services, including patrolling, access control at the lobby entrances, making entrance records of visitors and stopping trespassers, and handling and reporting complaints. This segment also provides guarding and personal escorting services, as well as crowd management services in various events, occasions, exhibitions, ceremonies, and press conferences. The Security Guarding segment offers its services to property management companies, schools, warehouse operators, property redevelopers, and construction companies under the KING FORCE name. The Mobile Game segment engages in the mobile gaming business for overseas markets. The e-Education segment provides e-education and security services to students. It also provides software development, and advisory and management services. The company was formerly as King Force Group Holdings Limited and changed its name to Greatwalle Inc. in October 2018. Greatwalle Inc. was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Greatwalle Inc. is a subsidiary of Greatwalle Holding Limited.

Pak Wing Group (Holdings) Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a foundation subcontractor for private and public sectors in Hong Kong. The company undertakes LS works; pipe piling and soldier piling for the construction of retaining walls; grouting and grout curtains that are used to form barriers to seal joints, reinforce steel and/or protect foundation works from water seepage; and groundwater control services. It also provides pumping test administration for estimating the hydraulic properties of an aquifer system; pre-boring, a process of drilling a bore hole into the ground to prepare a site for foundation works; mini piling, which involves sinking a permanent casing into a pre-bored hole; bored piling construction; and H-piles for use in construction projects, including buildings, bridges, highways, and others. In addition, the company offers other works, such as earth stabilization and pile extraction. Further, it is involved in the rental of machinery. The company's customers primarily include main contractors and subcontractors. Pak Wing Group (Holdings) Limited was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Finet Group Limited, an investment holding company, develops, produces, and provides financial information services, advertising and investor relationship services, and technology solutions to corporate and retail investors in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in four segments: Financial Information, Advertising and Investor Relationship Service Business; Securities and Futures Business; Money Lending Business; and Property Investment Business. It also offers advertising, investor relationship and branding promotion, and communication services; and online securities and futures trading services. In addition, the company produces and distributes programs through the FinTV brand; and invests in properties. Further, it acts as a dealer in securities and commodities; and provides money lending, video making, data hosting, financial public relationship and information management, online and offline advertising, and financial services. The company was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong. Finet Group Limited is a subsidiary of Maxx Capital International Limited.

Expert Systems Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides information technology (IT) infrastructure solutions in Hong Kong and Macau. The company's IT infrastructure solutions include server and storage consolidation, virtualization, backup and recovery, disaster recovery, software-defined data center, hyper-convergence, confidential mail, email and file archive, enterprise content management and collaboration, and high performance computing services; and directory and email services setup, upgrade, and migration services. Its IT infrastructure solutions also comprise networking and wireless infrastructure and management, campus and enterprise networking, unified communication, network optimization, and software-defined networking and Wan services, as well as PC migration, edge management, virtual desktop infrastructure, enterprise mobility management, point of sales, managed printing, and passbook printing services. In addition, the company offers private and public cloud, hybrid and multiple cloud, cross cloud architecture, and hybrid cloud extension services; and IoT, data, cloud, Web and email, endpoint and mobile, system, and network security services, as well as finance leasing services. It serves medium-sized, multinational, and local business enterprises in various industries, such as banking, finance, insurance, telecommunications, information technology, and media; fashion, jewelry, and accessories; property and construction; and entertainment, hotel, and travel, as well as government, education institutions, and NGOs. Expert Systems Holdings Limited was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong.

Allied Sustainability and Environmental Consultants Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides environmental consulting services in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through four segments: Green Building Certification Consultancy; Sustainability and Environmental Consultancy; Acoustic, Noise and Vibration Control and Audio-Visual Design Consultancy; and Environmental, Social and Governance (ESG) Reporting and Consultancy. It offers green building certification consultancy services for commercial buildings, residential and industrial buildings, hotels, data centers, and public usage buildings; and sustainability and environmental consultancy services, which engage in the process of environmental impact assessment to identify, predict, evaluate, and mitigate the biophysical, social, and other relevant effects of property development proposal prior to major decisions being taken and commitments made. The company also provides acoustic analysis, design, and control in various kinds of spaces and buildings; ESG reporting and consultancy services, including ESG readiness assessment, generating reports for compliance and enhancement solutions, training to management and employees in various formats, and translation services from English to Chinese; and other consultancy services. Allied Sustainability and Environmental Consultants Group Limited was founded in 1994 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong. Allied Sustainability and Environmental Consultants Group Limited is a subsidiary of Gold Investments Limited.
longName: Allied Sustainability and Environmental Consultants Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: China Smartpay Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily engages in the prepaid cards and Internet payment businesses in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and Thailand. The company also offers trade financing, and securities investment services, as well as issues prestige benefits cards to consumers and financial institutions. In addition, it engages in Internet micro-credit business; software development activities; provision of travel package; hotel booking agency; and merchant acquiring businesses. The company was formerly known as Oriental City Group Holdings Limited and changed its name to China Smartpay Group Holdings Limited in March 2014. China Smartpay Group Holdings Limited was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Sai Wan, Hong Kong.

Tonking New Energy Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the renewable energy business in the People's Republic of China. It is involved in the research and development of solar power technology; consultation of solar power plant technology; engineering, procurement, and construction business; sale of photovoltaic mounting and tracking system materials; and sells electricity. The company was formerly known as JC Group Holdings Limited and changed its name to Tonking New Energy Group Holdings Limited in May 2016. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.
longName: Tonking New Energy Group Holdings Limited

longBusinessSummary: Xinyi Automobile Glass Hong Kong Enterprises Limited, an investment holding company, develops, processes, and sells battery pack and energy storage system facilities with lithium batteries. The company's battery pack and energy storage system facilities include large-scale power banks for manufacturing facilities to facilitate load shifting and power stabilization; and uninterruptible power supply and power banks for households. It also provides contract processing services; produces and sells lithium battery products; and sells automobile glass products, comprising laminated, automobile tempered, heated laminated, special tempered, solar-x solar reflective auto, and water repelling glasses. In addition, the company offers automobile glass installation, repair, replacement, and cutting services; invests in and develops wind farm projects; and provides management services for wind farm operations. Further, it is involved in the trading of forklift business. The company operates 4 service centers and a motorcade service team with 21 vehicles. It has operations in the People's Republic of China and Hong Kong. The company was founded in 2015 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.
longName: Xinyi Automobile Glass Hong Kong Enterprises Limited

longBusinessSummary: Shenzhen Neptunus Interlong Bio-technique Company Limited researches, develops, produces, and sells medicines in the People's Republic of China. The company is also involved in the purchase and sale of medicines and healthcare food products; and research and development of biological technology products and in vitro diagnostic reagents. In addition, it manufactures herbal medicines, generic drugs, transfusion, anti-tumor, and other drugs. The company markets its products under the Neptunus and Yinkeluo brand names. It sells its products in approximately 20 provinces in China; and serves approximately 500 medical organizations. The company is based in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China. Shenzhen Neptunus Interlong Bio-technique Company Limited is a subsidiary of Shenzhen Neptunus Bio-engineering Company Limited.
longName: Shenzhen Neptunus Interlong Bio-technique Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: HangKan Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the bentonite mining, and production and sale of drilling mud and pelletizing clay in the People's Republic of China. Its primary products are metallurgical pellet soil, mud bentonite, and bentonite for dry mortar. The company holds 100% interest in the Huanghu Bentonite mine an open-pit mine with a permitted mining area of approximately 2.1311 square kilometers located in Anhui province. The company was formerly known as Feishang Non-Metal Materials Technology Limited and changed its name to HangKan Group Limited in August 2018. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Wuhu, the People's Republic of China.

Astrum Financial Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides securities brokerage services in Hong Kong. It offers securities dealing and brokerage services; placing and underwriting services; corporate finance advisory services; financing services, including securities and initial public offering financing; and asset management services, as well as futures contracts dealing services. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong. Astrum Financial Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Autumn Ocean Limited.

Directel Holdings Limited, a mobile virtual network operator (MVNO), through its subsidiaries, provides mobile telecommunication and value-added services in the People's Republic of China and Singapore. The company operates through two segments, Telecommunications Services and Distribution Business. It is involved in the trading of airtime sourced from mobile network operators (MNOs); and sale of airtime and mobile data to dealers and users. The company also offers roaming services, which allow the users to access the Internet service through mobile phone with a single SIM card under the China-HK Telecom, Directel, and Direct-TX brand names; and pre-paid telecommunications products. In addition, it provides local mobile telecom services; IDD services; and telesales dealership and other services, as well as sells SIM cards. Further, the company distributes mobile phones and electronic equipment, and mobile data top-up e-vouchers. Directel Holdings Limited distributes its roaming pre-paid products primarily through its network, including travel agents, hotels, telecommunications services/equipment agents/distributors, retail stores/chains, automobile 4S shops, and others. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.

Vinco Financial Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides various financial services in Hong Kong. The company offers its clients with initial public offerings (IPO) on the Main Board and GEM Board of The Stock Exchange of Hong Kong Limited; underwriting and distribution of IPO's shares; corporate finance advisory; mergers and acquisitions; corporate restructuring; arranging loan syndication; and convertible bonds issuance. It also facilitates corporate fund raising in equity capital market and debt market; provides professional advice on the structure of the fund raising; and assists private companies in pre-IPO private placement activities. In addition, the company assists clients on various transactions comprising fundraising activities of share placements, rights issues, and warrants issuance; share split/consolidation, privatization, and scheme of arrangement; capital restructuring; convertible bonds issuance; and formation of strategic partnership. Further, it acts as a financial advisor and independent financial advisor for transactions related to takeovers codes, connected transactions, and notifiable transactions; and as a financial advisor for corporate mergers and acquisitions, and asset and business acquisition/disposal transactions for listed and non-listed companies. The company was incorporated in 2008 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Vinco Financial Group Limited is a subsidiary of Vinco Asia Limited.

Aeso Holding Limited, through its subsidiaries, engages in the provision of fitting-out and renovation contracting services for premises in Hong Kong. It undertakes fitting-out works for the construction of newly built commercial premises and residential developments; and renovation works, including alteration and addition works for existing commercial premises. The company serves property developers, contractors, landlords, government authority, and international retail brands and local retailers. It also supplies materials for fitting-out and renovation projects; and offers interior design services. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.

F8 Enterprises (Holdings) Group Limited primarily engages in the sale and transportation of diesel oil and related products in Hong Kong. It also supplies marine diesel oil used for construction vessels and lubricant oil used for construction machinery and vehicles. As of June 30, 2019, the company operated a fleet of 10 diesel tank wagons; and a marine oil barge. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong. F8 Enterprises (Holdings) Group Limited is a subsidiary of Grand Tycoon Limited.

Tianjin Binhai Teda Logistics (Group) Corporation Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides logistics services primarily in the People's Republic of China. The company operates in two segments, Logistics and Supply Chain Service for Finished Automobiles and Components; and Materials Procurement and Related Logistics Services. It offers logistics services and supply chain management, including planning, storage, and transportation management for finished automobiles and components. The company also sells raw materials to trading companies; and provides transportation management, storage, cold warehouse, and warehouse supervising and management services. In addition, it engages in the provision of electronics components and transportation agency services. The company is headquartered in Tianjin, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Tianjin Binhai TEDA Logistics (Group) Corporation Limited

longBusinessSummary: MEIGU Technology Holding Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the research and development, production, and sale of fiberglass reinforced plastic products (FRP) in the People's Republic of China. It offers FRP grating products are used in operating and equipment platform, stair treads, trench covers, filter plates, etc.; and various industries, including petrochemical, electrical, marine engineering, plating, vessel, metallurgy, steel, papermaking, brewing, and municipal, as well as to distributors. The company also provides phenolic grating products to shipbuilders and offshore oilfields construction companies; FRP subway evacuation platform products for railway construction contractors; epoxy wedge strip products to wind turbine blades manufacturers; and FRP crosstie products for railway and national railway bridge construction corporations. It also operates in the United States, the United Kingdom, Belgium, Canada, South Korea, Kazakhstan, Lithuania, Australia, Uruguay, France, and other countries. MEIGU Technology Holding Group Limited was founded in 2003 and is based in Nantong, the People's Republic of China.

Excalibur Global Financial Holdings Limited, through its subsidiaries, provides brokerage services for futures and options traded on the exchanges in Hong Kong, the United States, Japan, Singapore, and the United Kingdom. It also engages in the money lending business; and provision of investment consulting services. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Larry Jewelry International Company Limited, an investment holding company, designs, sells, and retails jewelry products under the Larry Jewelry brand name in the People's Republic of China, Singapore, Hong Kong, and Macau. The company offers fashion jewelry for cosmopolitan ladies under the Vera brand name. It is also involved in sourcing, processing, re-packaging, and retailing Chinese pharmaceutical products, dried seafood, health products, and foodstuffs under the Tung Fong Hung brand. In addition, the company engages in the provision of administrative and management services; property holding activities; distribution of Chinese medicine and health food; and retailing and distribution of dried seafood, luxury food products, and herbal medicine. As of December 31, 2018, it had 15 retail shops in Hong Kong, 2 retail shops in Macau, and 35 retail outlets in Mainland China. The company was formerly known as Eternite International Company Limited and changed its name to Larry Jewelry International Company Limited in October 2011. Larry Jewelry International Company Limited was founded in 1967 and is based in Central, Hong Kong.

Anacle Systems Limited engages in the software development, and provision of enterprise application software and energy management solutions in Singapore, Malaysia, the People's Republic of China, and internationally. It operates through three segments: Simplicity and myBill; Starlight; and SpaceMonster. The Simplicity and myBill segment include a package of enterprise application software solutions, which provides specific solutions for enterprise asset management, shared resources management, tenancy management, financial management, supply chain management, customer relationship management, and billing management. Its Starlight segment provides cloud-based energy management solutions to the energy profiles of buildings, including energy consumption, power quality, energy analytics, and carbon footprint profiles information. The SpaceMonster operates as an online venue booking platform. The company also offers support and maintenance services; and researches, designs, develops, and supervises the manufacturing and assembly process of hardware products. It serves aerospace, defense, education, environment, healthcare, real estate, and utility industries. Anacle Systems Limited was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Singapore.

i-Control Holdings Limited provides video conferencing and multimedia audiovisual solutions in the People's Republic of China and Singapore. It offers audio-video conferencing solutions, professional display and sound solutions, LED wall solution, digital signage solutions, room scheduling solutions, lighting and central control solutions, wireless presentation solutions, unified communication, smart home automation solutions, and network infrastructure solutions. It serves multinational and listed companies, financial services providers, educational institutions, hotel and shopping mall operators, etc. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong.

CNC Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily provides waterworks engineering services. It operates through Provision of Civil Engineering Services and Television Broadcasting Business segments. The company provides road works and drainage services, and site formation works for the public sector in Hong Kong, as well as laying of water pipes. It also broadcasts television programs on television channels operated by television broadcasting companies in the Asia-Pacific region. In addition, it holds and leases motor vehicles; and provides management services. Further, the company engages in advertising business. The company was formerly known as Tsun Yip Holdings Limited and changed its name to CNC Holdings Limited in February 2012. CNC Holdings Limited was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Wanchai, Hong Kong.

Republic Healthcare Limited, a primary healthcare services company, provides consultation, medical investigation, and treatment services. The company offers various treatment solutions for common medical conditions and focuses on sexual health and infectious diseases. It also provides treatment solutions for common skin conditions and basic medical aesthetics services. The company offers its services through a network of general practice clinics under the Dr. Tan & Partners and S Aesthetics brands. Republic Healthcare Limited was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Singapore.

AL Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides interior design and fit out solutions in Hong Kong. The company offers design and fit out solutions, as well as space planning services. It also provides project management, contracting, pre-lease, money lending, maintenance, and aftersales services. Its customers primarily include business owners and residential property owners/tenants. AL Group Limited was founded in 1999 and is based in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong.

Winning Tower Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the processing and trading of raw, frozen, and cooked food products in Hong Kong. It is also involved in the Internet sale and trading of food products, as well as provision of transportation services with a fleet of eight vehicles. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong. Winning Tower Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Keyview Ventures Limited.

SDM Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates dance institutions for children. It offers a range of dance courses, including elementary, RAD ballet, CSTD jazz, and other dance courses. The company also sells dance uniforms, shoes, and accessories. It provides its services for children between the age of 1 and 16 under the SDM Jazz & Ballet Academie brand name. In addition, the company offers educational services.
