As of December 31, 2018, it had 20 self-operated dance centers, 3 joint venture dance centers, and 1 kindergarten in Hong Kong; and 4 international pre-schools in Singapore. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. SDM Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Wealthy Together Limited.

Zhejiang United Investment Holdings Group Limited, an investment holding company, undertakes slope works, foundation works, and other general building works in Hong Kong. The company provides consultancy services related to the management of projects. It serves government departments, such as civil engineering and development department, lands department, and architectural services department; other statutory bodies, including housing authorities; and private corporations and other entities in the private sector. The company was formerly known as Fraser Holdings Limited and changed its name to Zhejiang United Investment Holdings Group Limited in September 2017. Zhejiang United Investment Holdings Group Limited was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Admiralty, Hong Kong.
longName: Zhejiang United Investment Holdings Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: Simplicity Holding Limited, an investment holding company, operates casual dining full service restaurants in Hong Kong. It also engages in the property investment activities. As of March 31, 2019, the company operated 5 Marsino restaurants, 3 Grand Avenue restaurants, 3 Baba Nyonya restaurants, 1 Beefst restaurant, and 1 Haha Prawn Mee restaurant. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong. Simplicity Holding Limited is a subsidiary of Marvel Jumbo Limited.

Creative China Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily provides program production and event organization services in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Program Production; Concert and Event Organisation; Mobile Live Broadcasting and E-commerce; Entertainment on Demand System; and Artist Management segments. The Program Production segment provides television program production, serial program publishing, and related services. The Concert and Event Organisation segment offers organization services, such as music concerts, prize presentation ceremony, automobile shows, university alumni, and other performance events. The Mobile Live Broadcasting and E-commerce segment provides an electronic platform for entertainment contents consumption and e-commerce services, such as an online store. This segment also offers online program production and related services. The Entertainment On Demand System segment provides Fengtingxun, an entertainment demand system that is installed at various karaoke boxes, mini-cinemas, hotels, and Internet cafes, as well as offers related services. The Artist Management segment offers agency services for the artists for arranging different performance activities. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Beijing, the People's Republic of China.

Zhi Sheng Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily manufactures and sells office furniture products in the People's Republic of China. The company trades in carpets, curtains and drapes, wallpapers, floorboards, and panels. It serves governmental departments, financial institutions, and state-owned entities. The company was formerly known as Smart Raise International Holdings Limited and changed its name to Zhi Sheng Group Holdings Limited in April 2016. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Chengdu, the People's Republic of China. Zhi Sheng Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Convoy Capital Hong Kong Limited.

Taste Gourmet Group Limited, an investment holding company, operates restaurants in Hong Kong. As of March 31, 2019, it operated 22 restaurants under the La'taste, Nabe Urawa, Dab-Pa, Say Cheese, Sweetology, Urawa, and Rakuraku Ramen brand names, as well as under Parkview, the PHO, and Madam Saigon brands. It offers Vietnamese, Japanese, Chinese, and Western cuisines. The company also provides management services. It serves customers in mid-to-high-end market segment. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong. Taste Gourmet Group Limited is a subsidiary of IKEAB Limited.

Grand Brilliance Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, supplies medical devices in Hong Kong. The company offers medical consumables, including enteral feeding products, airway management anesthetic products, urology products, ligation clips, biopsy needles, drapes used in operation, suction liners, suction tubings, wound drain products, and respiratory and feeding products; and medical equipment, such as electric beds and mattresses, stretchers, furniture used in wards, vacuum-assisted breast biopsy systems, respiratory care products, and blood warmers It also provides medical instruments comprising anterior cervical retractor systems for neurosurgery and laparoscopic instruments for minimally invasive surgery; and other healthcare products that include hand sanitizers. In addition, the company offers medical device solutions, which comprise market trend analysis, sourcing of medical devices, after-sale services, technical support and training services, medical devices leasing services, and quality assurance services; develops healthcare products; and holds trademarks. It sells its products to various private hospitals, public hospitals, private clinics, non-profit organizations, universities, and individual end-users. The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong. Grand Brilliance Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of B&A Success Limited.

Indigo Star Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a subcontractor for structural reinforced and concrete works in Singapore. It undertakes reinforced concrete works, including steel reinforced, formwork erection, and concrete works of general building and civil engineering projects. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Singapore. Indigo Star Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Amber Capital Holdings Limited.

Fineland Real Estate Services Group Limited, through its subsidiaries, provides property intermediary services in the People's Republic of China. Its property research and consultancy services include macroeconomic analysis of the market, analysis on investment return, market environment analysis, studies on project conditions, development and positioning, formulating planning and development strategies of the project, recommendations on construction and mix of properties, and recommendations on sales and marketing strategies. The company's real estate agency services comprise marketing research and analysis, target customers analysis, the assessment of market entrance, the strategy of advertising, media, promotion and pricing settling, and the management of selling and after-sales services for the primary market. It also provides secondary market real estate agency services to owners looking to sell or lease their properties, and to potential buyers or tenants looking to buy or rent properties. In addition, the company offers a range of value-added services to customers, including property developers, individual customers, and companies, which include Zhaoshangyi that assists property developers with primary market development projects that have commercial units identify and approach prospective lessees; and operates One-stop Service Centre that provides value-added services, such as rent collection, property repair and maintenance, and design and furnishing services, as well as assists purchasers to obtain ownership certificates and apply for mortgages from banks. Fineland Real Estate Services Group Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, the People's Republic of China.
longName: Fineland Real Estate Services Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: Shen You Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and trades in sewing threads and garment accessories in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, and internationally. The company offers spun polyester sewing threads for garments; and sewing threads, such as textured polyester series, elastic filament sewing threads, weft yarns, and nylon threads. It serves garment manufacturers and wholesalers. The company was founded in 1978 and is based in Tsim Sha Tsui East, Hong Kong. Shen You Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Three Gates Investment Limited.

Prime Intelligence Solutions Group Limited, an investment holding company, distributes biometrics identification devices and security products in Hong Kong, Macau, and the People's Republic of China. Its biometrics identification device functions include face identification, fingerprint identification, finger vein identification, hand geometry identification, and iris identification. The company also provides other devices and accessories; and auxiliary and other services, including maintenance, installation, and solution services. In addition, it offers application software, and repair and maintenance services; and engages in software licensing activities. Prime Intelligence Solutions Group Limited was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong.

Linocraft Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides integrated offset printing and packaging solutions to direct customers and contract manufacturers in Malaysia, Singapore, and the Philippines. Its products include packaging boxes, rigid boxes, paper-board inserts, instruction manuals and books, and printed labels, as well as blister packs and box fillers, folding cartons, and case covers. The company was founded in 1972 and is headquartered in Johor Bahru, Malaysia. Linocraft Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Linocraft Investment Pte Limited.

Prosperous Printing Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, produces and trades in books and paper products to print brokers and publishers in Hong Kong, the United States, the United Kingdom, Australia, and other European countries. The company's products include leisure and lifestyle books, such as photography books, cookbooks, and art books; educational textbooks and learning materials, which consist of primary, secondary, and tertiary level school books; children's books comprising movie and video game series; and other paper-related products, including national maps, leaflets, greeting cards, journals, and calendars. It is also involved in the property investment activities. The company offers its products through sales representatives. The company was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Chai Wan, Hong Kong. Prosperous Printing Company Limited is a subsidiary of First Tech Inc.

Elegance Commercial and Financial Printing Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides printing, typesetting, and translation services in Hong Kong. It offers commercial printing, financial printing, secured data printing, lettershopping and direct mailing, digital printing, and book printing services, as well as document solutions. The company prints direct mailing materials, promotional and marketing materials, textbooks and related publication materials, financial reporting documents, compliance documents, initial public offerings prospectuses, and application forms. It also provides ad hoc design and/or translation, marketing and media, courier, and machineries subletting services; and sells paper and accessories. Elegance Commercial and Financial Printing Group Limited offers its services to banks, insurance companies, corporate customers, and their advertising agents and fund houses; listed companies and listing applicants; and book publishers. The company was founded in 1980 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. As of November 19, 2019, Elegance Commercial and Financial Printing Group Limited operates as a subsidiary of Global Fortune Global Limited.
longName: Elegance Commercial and Financial Printing Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: Satu Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, markets, and trades in homeware products. The company offers home decorations, bathroom accessories, and kitchenware and tableware under the Satu Brown brand name. It serves brand owners and licensee, chain supermarkets, and department stores through a third party e-commerce platform in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, the United Kingdom, Denmark, France, Australia, Poland, Italy, Germany, the Netherlands, and other countries. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong.

Asia Pioneer Entertainment Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the procurement, distribution, installation, and repair of electronic gaming equipment (EGM) and its spare parts for gaming operators in Macau SAR, Cambodia, Malaysia, the Philippines, and internationally. The company also provides regulatory, product design and content, localization, and on-site consultancy services to manufacturers of electronic gaming equipment, as well as technical services. It also sells refurbished EGMs, as well as leases electronic gaming equipment. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Macau. Asia Pioneer Entertainment Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of APE HAT Holdings Limited.

Stream Ideas Group Limited operates as a digital media company, provides online advertising services to brand owners and advertising agencies. Its online advertising services include social viral, engager, and mass blogging services. The company provides its services in Hong Kong, Taiwan, Malaysia, and Singapore. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. Stream Ideas Group Limited is a subsidiary of Jag United Company Limited.

Dowway Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as an integrated exhibition and event management company in the People's Republic of China. The company is involved in the design, planning, coordination, and management of exhibitions and events. It provides integrated exhibition and event management services to domestic and overseas automobile brands, primarily for facilitating showcases, promotion, and/or sales of their brands; and undertakes projects related to automobile exhibitions and events from non-automobile companies. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Beijing, China.

Hang Chi Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates elderly residential care homes under the Shui On, Shui Hing, and Shui Jun brand names in Hong Kong. The company offers residential care home services to elderly residents, including the provision of accommodation with dietician-managed meal plans, 24-hour nursing, and caretaking assistance, as well as professional services comprising regular medical consultation, physiotherapy, occupational therapy, psychological, and social care services. It also provides elderly related goods, such as adult nappies, nutritional milk, other medical consumable products, and daily supplies. In addition, the company engages in the provision of management and customizable add-on healthcare services to the elderly residents. It operates 816 residential care places. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. Hang Chi Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Shui Wah Limited.

Edvance International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, distributes information technology (IT) security products and services in the People's Republic of China and Singapore. The company's IT Security Products segment distributes network, system, and application and data security products, such as hardware, software, and auxiliary products. Its IT Security Services segment offers technical implementation, maintenance and support, and consulting services. The company primarily serves IT companies. Edvance International Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. Edvance International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Success Vision International Group Limited.

K W Nelson Interior Design and Contracting Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides interior design and project management services, and fitting-out works for office and retail spaces in the People's Republic of China. It offers pre-lease advisory, space planning, construction, maintenance for tailor made sections, and after sales services. The company offers services for design and decoration projects; and other interior design and fitting-out services. It serves multi-national companies from various industries, such as banking, retail, healthcare, legal services, catering, education, energy, insurance, telecommunications, property management, and logistics management. The company was formerly known as K W Nelson Interior Architect Group Limited and changed its name to K W Nelson Interior Design and Contracting Group Limited in August 2017. K W Nelson Interior Design and Contracting Group Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Quarry Bay, Hong Kong.
longName: K W Nelson Interior Design and Contracting Group Limited

longBusinessSummary: BCI Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the food and beverage, and entertainment businesses in Hong Kong. The company owns and operates two night entertainment clubs, such as Volar and Mudita; sports themed bar under the Paper Street brand; an entertainment studio under the Maximus Studio brand; and two restaurants that provide Japanese-style curry dishes under the Tiger brand. It also engages in the provision of public relations services; and securities investment activities. The company was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Asia Grocery Distribution Limited, an investment holding company, trades in and distributes food and beverage groceries in Hong Kong. The company offers commodities and cereal products, such as rice, wheat flour, noodle products, edible oil, sugar, and salt; and packaged food products, including meat and vegetables in preserved, canned, frozen, and other forms, as well as snacks and pre-packaged food items. It also provides sauces and condiments; dairy products and eggs; beverages and wines; and kitchen products comprising cling films, baking sheets, foils, detergents, bleach products, liquid soaps, tissue papers, toothpicks, and towels. In addition, the company offers product sourcing, repackaging, quality assurance, warehousing and storage, transportation, and other value-added services. Its customers include restaurants, non-commercial dining establishments, hotels and private clubs, food processing operators, and wholesalers. The company was founded in 1975 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. Asia Grocery Distribution Limited is a subsidiary of Sky Alpha Investments Limited.

HM International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides integrated printing services for corporate clients in the financial and capital markets in Hong Kong. It also provides concept creation and artwork design, IT, and languages services. The company also offers non-printing services, such as Website design, video production, e-book and APP production and maintenance, and electronic marketing presentation material production. It serves corporations and multinational financial institutions, such as fund houses and insurance companies, education organizations, and private companies in hospitality, marketing and advertising, and legal sectors. HM International Holdings Limited was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. HM International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of HM Ultimate Holdings Limited.

Dadi Education Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides overseas studies consultancy services in the People's Republic of China. The company also provides education information technology services. It serves students seeking secondary and higher education studies in the United Kingdom, Australia, Canada, New Zealand, the United States, and internationally. The company was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Mong Kok, Hong Kong. Dadi Education Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Grand Courage Investments Limited.

Optima Automobile Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides aftermarket automotive services in Singapore. It operates through three segments: After-market Automotive Services, Car Rental Services, and Automotive Supply Business. The After-market Automotive Services segment provides inspection, maintenance, and repair services. The Car Rental Services segment offers car rental services. The Automotive Supply Business segment supplies passenger car spare parts, accessories, and automotive equipment. The company was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Singapore.

AV Promotions Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides visual, lighting, and audio solution services in the People's Republic of China. The company offers services to its customers in various events, including exhibitions, ceremonies, conferences, concerts, TV shows, product launches, and other types of events. AV Promotions Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Aberdeen, Hong Kong. AV Promotions Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Jumbo Fame Company Limited.

Nexion Technologies Limited, an investment holding company, provides information and communications technology solutions. The company offers cyber infrastructure solutions, including maintenance and support services for telecommunications service providers and large enterprises; and cyber security solutions in the area of Internet content management for government agencies. It is also involved in the provision of consulting services and property holding business. The company operates in Indonesia, Laos, Malaysia, Myanmar, the People's Republic of China, the Philippines, Singapore, South Korea, Taiwan, Thailand, and Vietnam. Nexion Technologies Limited has a business cooperation agreement with Shanghai Qiange Information Technology Co. Ltd. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Singapore.

Winson Holdings Hong Kong Limited, an investment holding company, provides environmental hygiene and related, and airline catering support services in Hong Kong. It offers environmental hygiene services, including public area and office cleaning, and waste disposal, as well as specialized services, such as external curtain wall and window cleaning, marble floor maintenance and restoration, intensive cleaning, and pest control services etc. to residential, commercial and shopping complexes, public utilities, transportation systems, and government bodies. The company also provides pest control services comprising indoor pest management and rodent prevention, and control services that involve spraying of pesticides and fogging treatment, etc. to a range of customers, including government departments, educational institutes, public utilities, transportation systems, and residential, commercial and shopping complexes. In addition, it offers airline catering support services consisting of plating of meals, tray-setting, dry store packing and internal logistic for equipment flow, etc. at flight kitchens of airline catering operators. Further, the company provides property holding services. The company was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong. Winson Holdings Hong Kong Limited is a subsidiary of Sze's Holdings Limited.

WT Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the business of specialized and general building works in Hong Kong. It undertakes specialized works, including foundation and site formation, demolition, and ground investigation field works; and general building works, such as superstructure building, slope maintenance, hoarding, alternation and addition, and other miscellaneous construction works. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Tai Kok Tsui, Hong Kong. WT Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Talent Gain Ventures Limited.

Chi Ho Development Holdings Limited, through its subsidiaries, engages in renovation and maintenance, alteration and addition, and fitting-out works in Hong Kong. Its renovation and maintenance works include general upkeep, restoration, and enhancement of existing facilities and components of buildings, as well as their surroundings. The company's alteration and addition works, and fitting-out works comprise alteration and addition of building layouts, structural works, and decoration works to the interior spaces and to the existing premises. Chi Ho Development Holdings Limited was founded in 2016 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong.

Hing Ming Holdings Limited provides rental services for temporary suspended working platforms and other equipment. It rents tower cranes and generators; and trades in equipment and spare parts, including permanent suspended working platforms, motors, and wire ropes. The company also offers project planning; design and customization; delivery of equipment to construction site; installation and inspection; on-site customer support; and disassembly and delivery of equipment. It provides services to construction companies, owners of commercial properties, and trading companies in Hong Kong, Thailand, Macau, and internationally. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Kowloon City, Hong Kong. Hing Ming Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Hing Gut Limited.
address1: Room A4, Tsim Sha Tsui Mansion

longBusinessSummary: Modern Living Investments Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides property management services for public housing in Hong Kong. It offers estate management services, such as entailing general, tenancy, financial, and project management services, as well as minor repair and maintenance; and security and cleaning services. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Sha Tin, Hong Kong. Modern Living Investments Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of R5A Group Limited.

SK Target Group Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and trades in precast concrete junction boxes under the Target brand name in Malaysia. The company operates through Manufacturing and Trading; Other Building Materials and Services; Japanese Catering Services; and Sourcing Services segments. Its concrete junction boxes are used in telecommunication and electrical infrastructures upgrade, and expansion works, as well as in construction projects. The company also trades in junction box accessories and pipes; and provides mobile crane rental and ancillary services, such as uplifting services for precast concrete junction boxes. In addition, it offers catering services; and materials sourcing services. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Seri Kembangan, Malaysia. SK Target Group Limited operates as a subsidiary of Merchant World Investments Limited.

CBK Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the provision of food catering services through a chain of hotpot specialty restaurants in Hong Kong. Its restaurants sell food and beverages. The company also provides management consultancy services. As of March 31, 2019, it operated seven restaurants under the Calf Bone King, Calf Bone King Steam Pot, CBK Prince Club, 3H Island Fusion Pot, and Hotpot Hongding brands. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong. CBK Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Sure Wonder Investments Limited.

Hao Bai International (Cayman) Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the design, procurement, and installation of water circulation systems in Hong Kong and Macau. It operates through Management Contracting Services, Consultancy Services, and Maintenance Services segments. The company's water circulation systems include swimming pools, water fountains, water curtains, etc. It also offers consulting, maintenance, and repair services for water circulation systems. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. Hao Bai International (Cayman) Limited is a subsidiary of Harmony Asia international Limited.

Bar Pacific Group Holdings Limited operates a chained bar that primarily offers beverages and light refreshments under the Bar Pacific and Pacific brands in Hong Kong. As of March 31, 2019, it operated a network of 37 shops. The company's bars offer beer, other alcoholic drinks, and non-alcoholic beverages. It is also involved in operating electronic dart machines. Bar Pacific Group Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Hunghom, Hong Kong. Bar Pacific Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Moment to Moment Company Limited.

Takbo Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, develops, manufactures, and sells beauty products in the United States, the People's Republic of China, the United Arab Emirates, the United Kingdom, and internationally. It offers colour cosmetics, shower gels, body lotions, misty sprays, and perfumes; and designs, develops, and sells beauty bags, including tote bags, packaging bags, cosmetics bag sets, cosmetics clutches, and pouches. The company serves retailers, beauty product brand owners, and trading companies. It offers beauty products and beauty bags under the Pink Viva, Secret Lace, and Gorgeous Girl Forever brand names. The company was founded in 1994 and is based in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. Takbo Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Classic Charm Investments Limited.

RMH Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides dermatology treatment solutions in Singapore. It offers specialty care services for various dermatological conditions affecting skin, hair, and nails through medical, surgical, laser, and aesthetic treatments. The company also provides consultancy, prescription and dispensing, and treatment services. It offers treatment of skin cancer; and skin diseases, such as eczema, psoriasis, acne, pigmentation, adverse drug reactions, and warts. The company operates three clinics at Orchard Road, Raffles Place, and East Coast. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Singapore. RMH Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Brisk Success Holdings Limited.

Somerley Capital Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides corporate finance advisory services in Hong Kong. The company acts as a financial adviser to Hong Kong public listed companies, various shareholders, and investors, as well as parties seeking to control or invest in listed companies in Hong Kong; and financial adviser to independent board committees and/or independent shareholders of listed companies in Hong Kong. It also acts as a compliance adviser primarily for newly listed companies in Hong Kong; and a sponsor to initial public offerings and listings of shares of companies on the Stock Exchange in Hong Kong, as well as provides advisory services on secondary equity issues and asset management services. The company offers advisory services related to takeovers of listed companies, whitewash waivers, acquisitions and disposals, connected transactions, spin-offs and reorganizations, privatizations, initial public offerings, and secondary issues. It serves the conglomerate, consumer, energy, natural resources and infrastructure, renewables, financial institutions and insurance, industrial, property and construction, gaming and hospitality, and TMT industries. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Somerley Capital Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Somerley Group Limited.

IWS Group Holdings Limited, a facility services company, provides security and facility management services to public and private sectors in Hong Kong. The company's security services include general manned guarding; manpower support to events; and crisis security at railway stations and facilities, public amenities, private commercial properties, and residential and other properties, as well as sea, land, and railway immigration control points. Its facility management services comprise property management, car parking rental and management, cleaning, and hotel management services. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong.
address1: Hang Seng Castle Peak Road Building

longBusinessSummary: SG Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the provision of apparel designing and sourcing services for branded fashion retailers and wholesalers. It operates through Online Fashion Retailers, Fashion Retailers, and Consultation Services segments. The Online Fashion Retailers segment supplies apparel products with designing and sourcing services to online fashion retailers. The Fashion Retailers segment supplies apparel products with designing and sourcing services to fashion retailers. The Consultation Services segment offers consultation services, primarily to apparel and footwear manufacturers, including the assistance services to comply with the corporate social responsibility standards requirements; fashion trend forecast analysis; design specifications; and introducing potential customers. The company also provides quality assurance services; and operates a showroom. It operates in the United Kingdom, the People's Republic of China, Germany, the United States, Hong Kong, Ireland, Singapore, Spain, and Internationally. The company was formerly known as S&G Holdings Co. Ltd. SG Group Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong. SG Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of JC Fashion International Group Limited.

Noble Engineering Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, principally provides wet trade work services in Hong Kong. The company undertakes tile and brick laying, plastering, floor screeding, and marble works. It offers wet trade services for various building construction projects, including residential, community facility, public housing, and commercial development projects in the private and public sectors. The company was formerly known as Noble Engineering Holdings Limited and changed its name to Noble Engineering Group Holdings Limited in August 2017. The company was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong. Noble Engineering Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Land Noble Holdings Limited.

In Technical Productions Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides visual display solutions for pop concerts, corporate events, exhibitions, sports and recreational events, and other live performances in the People's Republic of China, Taiwan, and internationally. It rents LED panels, projectors, video control units, and other equipment; and offers stage design and equipment installation services. The company is also involved in the import, export, and wholesale of video equipment and parts, as well as provides related support services. In Technical Productions Holdings Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong.

MS Concept Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the provision of catering services in Hong Kong. As of March 31, 2019, the company owned and operated 11 restaurants, including 5 western cuisine restaurants under the Mr. Steak brand name; 1 buffet international cuisine restaurant under the Mr. Steak  Buffet à la minute brand name; 2 western cuisine restaurants under the Sky Bar brand name that offer seafood dishes, and a range of wines and cocktails; 2 western specialty restaurants under the Bistro Bloom and Bistro Bloom/Marbling brand names that serve western food along with specialty meat cuts; and 1 Japanese specialty restaurant under the Hana brand name that serves Nabemono. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong. MS Concept limited is a subsidiary of Future More Company Limited.

Universe Printshop Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides general printing services and trades in printing products in Hong Kong. Its printing services include offset printing, ink-jet printing, and toner-based digital printing. The company also offers business printing-related products, including stationery, advertisements, periodicals, directories, and catalogues; and other printing-related products, such as pre-ink stamps, plastic name-cards, printed eco-bags, and printed plastic folders. In addition, it provides various post-press treatment services to printed products, such as varnishing, binding, and laminating. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong.

EDICO Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides integrated financial printing services in Hong Kong. Its integrated services include typesetting and proofreading, translation, design, printing and binding, distribution, and media placement. The company handles a range of documents, including listing-related documents, periodical reporting documents, compliance documents, and miscellaneous and marketing collaterals. It serves listing applicants and listed companies. EDICO Holdings Limited was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Sunlight (1977) Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the supply of tissue products and hygiene related products for corporate customers in Singapore. It provides toilet tissues, including jumbo roll tissues and conventional roll tissues; hand towels; napkins; facial tissues; hygiene-related products comprising hygiene wipes, hygiene gloves, and industrial wipes; and tissue dispensers. The company was founded in 1977 and is headquartered in Singapore.

FY Financial (Shenzhen) Co., Ltd., a financial services company, provides finance leasing, factoring, advisory services, customer referral services, and medical equipment in the People's Republic of China. It operates through two segments, Financial and Advisory Business, and Trading Operation Business. The Financial and Advisory Business segment includes direct finance leasing; sale-leaseback; factoring services, such as financing and accounts receivable management services; advisory services, including provision of market information, product advice, analysis on competition in the industry, and solutions for optimizing operational workflow, as well as financial management and asset management advice; and customer referral. The Trading Operation Business segment engages in import and domestic trade of medical equipment, as well as the provision of maintenance services in the medical equipment industry. The company was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, the People's Republic of China.

Mansion International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells baby clothing and clothing accessories for infants and toddlers. The company offers underwear products; basic garments, such as rompers, robes, coats, pyjamas, windbreakers, vests, reversible jackets, pants, and leggings; and outdoor garments. It also provides sleeping accessories, including baby urine pads, blankets, receiving blankets, sleeping bags, and swaddles; and fabric accessories comprising bibs, hats, mittens, booties, and towels. The company offers its products through its original equipment manufacturing business directly to the brand companies or designated sourcing companies primarily located in Hong Kong, the United Kingdom, and the United States; and original brand manufacturing business under its mides brand name and complementary third party brand products through its 12 self-operated retail stores and 11 department store counters in Hong Kong, as well as wholesale in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, and Macao. Mansion International Holdings Limited was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.

Goal Rise Logistics (China) Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides a range of logistics services for customers supply chains in the People's Republic of China. The company operates through Transportation Services, Warehousing Services, In-Plant Logistics Services, and Customisation Services segments. The Transportation Services segment offers delivery of production materials, components, and finished goods. The Warehousing Services segment offers provision of inventory storage and management services. The In-Plant Logistics Services segment offers a range of in-house services at customers' manufacturing plants, including management of the movements of production materials and components, and work-in progress to the production lines, as well as finished goods to the factory gates of the relevant customers. The Customisation Services segment offers labelling and bundling services. It serves customers from various industries, including pharmaceutical, fast-moving consumer goods, packaging, health and beauty, and other industries. Goal Rise Logistics (China) Holdings Limited was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, China.

Omnibridge Holdings Limited provides human resources outsourcing and recruitment services in Singapore and Hong Kong. The company sources and employs suitable candidates that match the job descriptions specified by its clients; and identifies, screens, assesses, and procures qualified candidates for positions at various levels, including administrative, executive, managerial, and professional. It also offers other human resources support services, such as referral and parking services. The company serves public and private sector clients, including Singapore government agencies and non-profit organizations. Omnibridge Holdings Limited was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Singapore. Omnibridge Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Omnipartners Holdings Limited.

TOMO Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the design, manufacture, supply, and installation of leather upholstery for passenger vehicles in Singapore. It operates in two segments, Passenger Vehicle Leather Upholstery, and Passenger Vehicle Electronic Accessories. The company offers rear and front seats leather upholstery products. It also provides leather wrappings for other passenger vehicle interior products, such as door panels, and head and arm rests. In addition, the company offers passenger vehicle electronic accessories, including navigation and multimedia accessories comprising navigation systems, head units, and in-car entertainment systems; and safety and security accessories that enhance driver and passenger safety and security consisting of digital video recorders, reverse cameras and parking sensors, and security alarm systems. It sells its products to passenger vehicle distributors and dealers. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Singapore. TOMO Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of TOMO Ventures Limited.

Lumina Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides fire safety services in Hong Kong. Its services include design, supply, and installation of fire safety systems, such as evacuation and electrical fire alarm systems, water and gas suppression systems, and portable fire equipment for newly built and existing buildings; and repair and maintenance services on fire safety systems. The company serves construction contractors, property owners and tenants, property managers, government-related organizations, and non-governmental organizations. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Tai Kok Tsui, Hong Kong. Lumina Group Limited is a subsidiary of Foxfire Limited.

Reach New Holdings Limited, through its subsidiaries, manufactures and supplies labeling products and garment accessories in the People's Republic of China. The company offers printed products, including hangtags, price tags, and stickers; woven labels comprising brand labels, size labels, and badges; and printed labels, such as brand, size, and care content labels. It also sources and sells other garment accessories, such as tapes, hanging tablets, string locks, leather badges, buttons, and metal products. The company serves garment brand companies, sourcing companies, and garment manufacturers. Reach New Holdings Limited was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Huizhou, the People's Republic of China. Reach New Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Neo Concept Holdings Limited.

Lapco Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides environmental hygiene services in Hong Kong. The company offers cleaning, pest management, waste management and recycling, and landscaping services to a range of venues, including streets, cultural, leisure, and recreational and residential premises, commercial buildings, markets, restaurants, academic institutions, etc. It serves government departments, property management companies, and other corporations in the private sector. The company was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong.

Mi Ming Mart Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the retail of multi-brand beauty and health products in Hong Kong. The company's products include skincare products, cosmetic products, and food and health supplements. It operates 10 retail stores under the brand of mi ming mart in Hong Kong. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong. Mi Ming Mart Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Prime Era Holdings Limited.

K Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the restaurant and catering business. The company operates multi-branded restaurants that are mainly operated under a franchise model. It offers Korean and Japanese cuisines with casual dining concepts that target the middle-income mass market in Singapore, Malaysia, and Indonesia. The company operates 15 self-operated restaurants under the Chir Chir, Masizzim, Nipong Naepong, NY Night Market, Kogane Yama, Sora Boru, and Kota Zheng Zhong brands, as well as 1 central kitchen under the Gangnam Kitchen brand. K Group Holdings Limited was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Singapore. K Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Canola Investment Holdings Limited.

Ocean One Holding Ltd., an investment holding company, engages in importing and wholesaling frozen seafood products in Hong Kong, Macau, Mainland China, and Taiwan. The company offers frozen seafood products in various categories, such as prawns; scallops, oysters, and surf clams; fishes; crabs and roe; octopuses and cuttlefishes; processed seafood products; and miscellaneous products. It serves frozen seafood resellers and frozen seafood catering service providers. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong. Ocean One Holding Ltd. is a subsidiary of Karlson Holding Limited.

JTF International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in blending and selling fuel oil; and selling refined oil and other petrochemical products in the People's Republic of China. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, China. JTF International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Thrive Shine Limited.

Furniweb Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells elastic textile and webbing products in Malaysia, Vietnam, rest of the Asia Pacific, Europe, North America, and internationally. It operates in three segments: Elastic textile, Webbing, and Other products. The company offers upholstery, safety, rigid, and furniture webbing products, as well as covered elastic yarns; narrow elastic fabrics; and rubber strips and sheets. It also trades machinery and accessories; and sells clothing, footwear, and ancillary products. In addition, the company is involved in the property business. Its products are used in the apparel, intimate apparel, food packaging, furniture, automotive, household appliance, and health care industries. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Seri Kembangan, Malaysia. Furniweb Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of PRG Holdings Berhad.

Shenglong Splendecor International Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells decorative printing materials products. The company offers PVC furniture films, PU coated papers, uncoated papers, and furniture decorative papers; flooring decorative paper and PVC flooring films; and melamine impregnated paper and finish foil paper, as well as biaxial oriented polypropylen decorative films. It also manufactures and sales craft pictures. The company's products are primarily used in furniture, cabinets, profiles, doors, high pressure laminates, Eco plates, particleboards, fiberboards, flooring, etc. Shenglong Splendecor International Limited sells its products under the Splendecor brand in the People's Republic of China, Pakistan, India, Kenya, Thailand, and internationally. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Hangzhou, the People's Republic of China.

Wan Leader International Limited, an investment holding company, provides logistics services in Hong Kong and internationally. It offers freight forwarding and related logistics services, which include air freight and sea freight services; and warehousing and related value-added services, such as labelling and packaging services. Wan Leader International Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong.

Max Sight Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily engages in the provision of photography services by supplying automatic identity photo booths in Hong Kong and the People's Republic of China. The company operates automatic ID photo booths under the Max Sight Photo name serving general public. It owns approximately 214 automatic photo booths, including 83 photo booths in Hong Kong and 131 photo booths in Guangdong Province. The company was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Causeway Bay, Hong Kong. Max Sight Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Causeway Treasure Holding Limited.

Smart Globe Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, produces, distributes, and prints books, novelty, and packaging products in the United States, the United Kingdom, the Netherlands, the People's Republic of China, Belgium, Hong Kong, and internationally. It provides a range of services, such as pre-press, printing, and finishing services, as well as custom-made and value added printing products. The company also offers box products, children books and pop-ups, journals and book products, stationery and photo albums, leather products, and oversized books. The company was founded in 2012 and is based in North Point, Hong Kong. Smart Globe Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Master Sage Limited.

ISP Global Limited, an investment holding company, sells sound and communication systems for various building systems in Singapore. The company sells sound and communication systems and related services; integrated services of sound and communication systems with a focus on customization, and installation of sound and communication systems in buildings; and alert alarm system services. It serves government agencies, private organizations, and end users. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Singapore.

Niche-Tech Group Limited, an investment holding company develops, manufactures, and sells semiconductor packaging materials primarily in the People's Republic of China. It offers bonding wires, such as copper bonding wires, aluminum silicon bonding wires, heavy aluminum bonding wires, silver alloy bonding wires, palladium-coated copper wires, and gold alloy bonding wires; and encapsulant for LED filament and COB LED. The company also provides epoxy encapsulant products, such as glob top epoxy, LED epoxy encapsulant, and die attach adhesives; and soldering materials. It serves LED and IC packaging industries. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Tai Po, Hong Kong. Niche-Tech Group Limited is a subsidiary of Niche-Tech Investments Holdings Limited.

Cool Link (Holdings) Limited, an investment holding company, imports, exports, and supplies various food products to ship supply industry in Singapore, Cambodia, the Philippines, and Indonesia. It supplies various food products, including canned food and packaged beverages; and various dairy products, ice cream and frozen cakes, and pies. It serves ship supply customers, and retail and food service customers. The company was founded in 2001 and is based in Singapore.

1957 & Co. (Hospitality) Limited, an investment holding company, operates full service restaurants in Hong Kong and the People's Republic of China. It also provides restaurant management, catering management, and consultancy services. As of December 31, 2018, the company operated 12 restaurants under self-owned brands, including Ta-ke, An Nam, Modern Shanghai, 10 Shanghai, and Hokkaidon; and 3 franchised or sublicensed brands, such as Mango Tree, Gonpachi, and Paper Moon. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Hong Kong.

Sanbase Corporation Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the provision of interior fit-out management and solutions in Hong Kong and the People's Republic of China. It undertakes bare shell fit-out, restacking, reinstatement, design, churn works, and maintenance and other services. The company was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Sanbase Corporation Limited is a subsidiary of Madison Square International Investment Limited.

Ocean Line Port Development Limited, an inland terminal operator, provides port logistic services in the People's Republic of China. It operates two terminals, including Jiangkou Terminal and Niutoushan Terminal located in Chizhou, Anhui. The company offers cargo uploading and unloading, bulk cargoes handling, and container handling services, as well as related ancillary port services, such as storage, short distance road transportation, and other miscellaneous services. Ocean Line Port Development Limited was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Chizhou, the People's Republic of China. Ocean Line Port Development Limited is a subsidiary of Vital Force Developments Limited.

i.century Holding Limited provides apparel products and apparel supply chain management services in the United States, France, other European countries, Australia, Canada, Japan, and Internationally. It offers jackets, woven shirts, pullovers, pants, shorts, and T-shirts; and other products, including dresses and vests, as well as accessories, such as socks and bags. The company also provides sales consulting and support services; and merchandising quality control and sourcing services. i.century Holding Limited was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Lai Chi Kok, Hong Kong.

Wine's Link International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the wholesale and retail of a range of wine products and other alcoholic beverages in Hong Kong. The company offers wine products, such as premium collectible red, fine red, and white wine products; other alcoholic beverages comprising champagne, whisky, and sake; and wine accessory products, including wine decanters, wine glasses, and wine openers. It is also involved in trading of wine cellars. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in San Po Kong, Hong Kong.

Top Standard Corporation, an investment holding company, operates full-service restaurants in Hong Kong. It operates through San Xi Lou, Pure Veggie House, Pure Veggie House Taipei, Man Jiang Hong, Ronin Central, and Ronin Wanchai segments. The company operates two Sichuanese and Cantonese restaurants under the San Xi Lou brand located in Central and Causeway Bay; a fusion vegetarian restaurant under the Pure Veggie House brand in Central and Taipei; a Sichuanese restaurant under the Man Jiang Hong brand located in Tsimshatsui; and Japanese restaurants under the Ronin brand located in Wan Chai. Top Standard Corporation was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong.

Zhicheng Technology Group Ltd., an investment holding company, provides precision 3D testing and machining solutions in the People's Republic of China. The company offers non-contact optical measurement and full-field positioning systems to detect and analyze the shape and appearance data of objects; and non-contact three-dimensional dynamic measurement and analysis systems to calculate surface displacement and strain distribution. It serves equipment manufacturers in the aviation, aerospace, shipbuilding, ground transportation vehicles, and electronics industries. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, the People's Republic of China.

Hyfusin Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, manufactures, and sells candle products in the United States, the United Kingdom, and internationally. The company offers daily-use candles, scented candles, and decorative candles, as well as other products, such as diffusers. It primarily serves department store operators and buying agents. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Aberdeen, Hong Kong. Hyfusin Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of AVW International Limited.

Grand Talents Group Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the provision of civil engineering construction works of road and highway related infrastructures in Hong Kong. It constructs sewerage, waterworks, and barrier-free access facilities, as well as repairs and maintains structures for roads and highways. Grand Talents Group Holdings Limited was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.

Jia Group Holdings limited, an investment holding company, operates restaurants in Hong Kong and Singapore. Its restaurants offer dine-in services with a range of cuisines, including Chinese, Spanish, Thai, British, Italy, and Southern Californian dishes. The company also provides event-hosting services at its restaurants or other third party venues. As of January 22, 2018, it owned and operated 10 independent full-service restaurants under the names of 208 Duecento Otto, 22 Ships, Duddell's, Chachawan, Ham & Sherry, Aberdeen Street Social, Meen & Rice, Mak Mak, RHODA, and Commissary. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. Jia Group Holdings limited is a subsidiary of Giant Mind International Limited.

ST International Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides functional knitted fabrics in the People's Republic of China. It also sells functional fibers and yarns, as well as designs and sells apparels. The company offers its products primarily to lingerie and apparel brand owners, sourcing agents, and garment manufacturers. ST International Holdings Company Limited was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

Gain Plus Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a construction contractor for public and private sector projects in Hong Kong. It offers repair, maintenance, addition, and alteration services, including general upkeep, restoration, and improvement of existing facilities and components of buildings and their surroundings; and building construction services comprising building works and civil works for new buildings, such as lift towers, soccer fields, and walkways. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Sheung Shui, Hong Kong.

Sheung Moon Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the business of civil engineering construction works in Hong Kong. It undertakes site formation works, road and drainage works, and structural works for public and private sectors. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong. Sheung Moon Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Chrysler Investments Limited.

Byleasing Holdings Limited, a finance leasing company, provides equipment-based financing solutions primarily to small and medium-sized enterprises and entrepreneurial individuals in the People's Republic of China. The company primarily offers two types of finance leasing services, including direct finance leasing and sale-leaseback. It also provides factoring and value-added advisory services. Byleasing Holdings Limited was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Xiamen, the People's Republic of China.

Wing Fung Group Asia Limited, an investment holding company, provides supply, installation, and fitting-out services of mechanical ventilation and air-conditioning systems for buildings in Hong Kong and Macau. It serves contractors and subcontractors of various types of building projects, including infrastructural, commercial, and residential building projects. The company was formerly known as Wing Fung Capital Holdings Limited and changed its name to Wing Fung Group Asia Limited in December 2016. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Fotan, Hong Kong. Wing Fung Group Asia Limited is a subsidiary of Wing Fung Capital Limited.

JLogo Holdings Limited owns and operates restaurants in Singapore. The company operates through two segments, The Dining Operations, and The Artisanal Bakery. It operates eight restaurants, which include 6 restaurants under the Central Hong Kong Café brand, 1 restaurant under the Black Society brand, and 1 restaurant under the franchised Greyhound Café brand. The company also operates 20 bakery retail outlets in Malaysia, including 16 are self-operated bakery retail outlets and 4 are franchised bakery retail outlets under the Bread Story brand. Its bakery retail outlets sells bread and flour confectionary products, such as breads, pastries, and cakes. The company serves retail customers. JLogo Holdings Limited was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Singapore.

Polyfair Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the construction business in Hong Kong. It provides façade and curtain wall works solutions for residential and commercial buildings. The company offers various design and build services in projects, such as developing designs, conducting structural calculations, preparing shop drawings, sourcing and procuring building materials, arranging for building material logistics and installation works, project management, and post-project completion services. It serves property developers and main contractors from the private sector. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in North Point, Hong Kong. Polyfair Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of C.N.Y. Holdings Limited.

Vistar Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides electrical and mechanical engineering services in Hong Kong. The company operates through three segments: Installation Work, Alteration and Addition Services, and Maintenance Services. It undertakes installation, alteration, addition, and maintenance works of fire service systems. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Chai Wan, Hong Kong.

TL Natural Gas Holdings Limited supplies compressed natural gas (CNG) in Jingzhou, China. The company distributes CNG to retail customers, such as vehicular end-users; and wholesale customers, including urban gas companies, gas refuelling station operators, and industrial users. It operates four gas refuelling stations in Jingzhou, Hubei Province. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Jingzhou City, China.

Dominate Group Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in manufacturing, procurement, marketing and promotion, distribution, retail, and wholesale of jewelry products in Hong Kong. It offers gem-set jewelry and pure gold products. The company sells its products through a network of seven retail stores under the Chong Fai Jewellery brand name. It also engages in the trading of recycled gold products from the general public to customers. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. Dominate Group Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of Mythe Group Holdings Company Limited.

Victory Securities (Holdings) Company Limited, an investment holding company, provides integrated financial services in Hong Kong. The company offers securities broking, placing and underwriting, financing, and asset management services. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Hong Kong. Victory Securities (Holdings) Company Limited is a subsidiary of Dr. TT Kou's Family Company Limited.

Amuse Group Holding Limited, an investment holding company, designs, markets, distributes, and sells toys and related products in Hong Kong, Japan, the United States, China, and internationally. It operates through Sale of ODM Toys, Distribution of Imported Toys, and Sale of Own Licensed Toys segments. The company offers various premium and general class figures based on third party owned ACG characters; and other related products, such as pens and hair ties. It also produces and sells ODM toys according to customers' specifications and requirements; distributes imported toys; and develops and sells own licensed toys based on license rights. The company offers its own licensed toys under the SENTINEL, TOPI, and FLAME TOYS brands. Amuse Group Holding Limited was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong.

Pacific Legend Group Limited, an investment holding company, sells and rents home furniture and accessories in the People's Republic of China and the United Arab Emirates. It operates through three segments: Sale of Home Furniture and Accessories, Rental of Home Furniture and Accessories, and Project and Hospitality Services. The company sells home furniture and accessories through retail, corporate sale, online shop, wholesale, and franchise channels. It also offers project and hospitality services, which include designing, styling, decorating, and furnishing commercial or residential properties, such as hotels, serviced apartments, and show flats. In addition, the company offers design consultancy services for fitting out interiors with furnishings. Pacific Legend Group Limited was founded in 1979 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.

Fameglow Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides non-surgical medical aesthetic services in Hong Kong. The company offers energy-based procedures, including procedures that use various energy-based devices that emit various types of energy on skin surface; and minimally invasive procedures, such as injection treatments, which are non-surgical treatment procedures with minimal penetration to body tissue and no surgical incisions. It also provides traditional beauty services comprising non-medical and non-invasive beauty treatment services. In addition, the company sells skincare products through two retail shops and sales counters; and invests in properties. It operates two medical aesthetic centers under the per Face brand located in Causeway Bay and Tsim Sha Tsui. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong. Fameglow Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Equal Joy Holdings Limited.

Kinetix Systems Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides information technology (IT) services in Hong Kong and Macau. The company operates through three segments: IT Infrastructure Solutions Services, IT Development Solutions Services, and IT Maintenance and Support Services. It provides IT infrastructure solutions services to its clients by advising them the hardware and/or software that their IT systems would require and procuring the hardware and/or software from a range of authorized distributors or third party suppliers and integrating them with clients' IT systems. The company also offers IT development solutions services, including system analysis and design, software development, and technology consultancy services; and IT maintenance and support services. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong. Kinetix Systems Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Vigorous King Limited.

Narnia (Hong Kong) Group Company Limited, an investment holding company, principally engages in the manufacture and sale of fabrics in Mainland China, Hong Kong, and internationally. The company's fabric products primarily include brushed fabric, decorative fabric, imitation silk, sateen, pongee, polyester shirt fabric, taffeta, bed fabric, washed cashmere, and oxford fabric products. It is also involved in the provision of printing and dyeing services; and textile manufacturing activities. Narnia (Hong Kong) Group Company Limited was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Huzhou City, the People's Republic of China. Narnia (Hong Kong) Group Company Limited is a subsidiary of Spring Sea Star Investment Limited.

Eggriculture Foods Ltd., an investment holding company, engages in the production and sale of eggs and egg processed products primarily in Singapore. It offers fresh chicken eggs; and processed egg products, including pasteurized shell eggs, pasteurized liquid eggs, pasteurized soft yolk eggs, pasteurized hard boiled and peeled eggs, and century eggs and salted eggs. The company sells fresh chicken eggs under the name of N&N; and processed eggs products to supermarkets through various independent third party online sales platforms under the brand of Egg Story  Pasteurised to kill Salmonella and Bird Flu Virus. The company is headquartered in Singapore. Eggriculture Foods Ltd. is a subsidiary of Radiant Grand International Limited.

Mindtell Technology Limited, an investment holding company, provides information technology (IT) services in Indonesia, Malaysia, Singapore, and the United Kingdom. It operates through System Integration and Development Services, IT Outsourcing Services, and Maintenance and Consultancy Services segments. The company is involved in the design, procurement, installation, and maintenance of customized system applications for corporate customers. Its services primarily include system integration and development, IT outsourcing, and maintenance and consultancy services. The company primarily serves banks and financial institutions, government and statutory bodies, educational institutions, IT service firms, software principals, and other small and medium enterprises. Mindtell Technology Limited was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Subang Jaya, Malaysia.

World Super Holdings Limited primarily engages in the rental of crawler cranes, oscillators, reverse circulation drilling (RCD) rigs, and hydromill trench cutters for construction projects in Hong Kong and Macau. It is also involved in the trading of new or used crawler cranes, RCDs, trench cutters, and oscillators, as well as related spare parts. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in North Point, Hong Kong.

Oriental Payment Group Holdings Limited, a merchant acquirer, provides payment processing services to various merchants visited by Chinese tourists in Thailand. The company enables its merchants to accept various cross-border electronic payment methods, including credit cards, debit cards, quick response codes, near field communication, and other alternative payment technologies. Oriental Payment Group Holdings Limited was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand. Oriental Payment Group Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Charm Act Group Limited.

longBusinessSummary: WAC Holdings Limited, a construction engineering consultant company, provides structural and geotechnical engineering consultancy services in Hong Kong. The company offers structural engineering services, such as loading calculation and stress design; geotechnical engineering services, including calculation of earth surface conditions and assessment of risks posed by site conditions; and material engineering services that include analyzing the use of and selecting building materials in a construction project. It also undertakes infrastructure works comprising drainage works; and provides registered structural engineers and authorized person services related to alteration and addition works, as well as expert services. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong.

Metropolis Capital Holdings Limited engages in the provision of finance lease, factoring, and other services in the People's Republic of China. It offers customized vehicle finance leasing services to customers, as well as provides machinery and equipment finance leasing services to corporate customers. The company was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.

Huakang Biomedical Holdings Company Limited, a medical device company, engages in the research and development, manufacture, marketing, and sale of in-vitro diagnostic (IVD) reagents in the People's Republic of China. It offers male and female fertility IVD, parasite antibody detection, and EBV antibody detection reagents; and auxiliary reproductive supplies and equipment. The company was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.

Orange Tour Cultural Holding Limited, an investment holding company, provides marketing services in the People's Republic of China. The company acts as an event manager and develops plans for various cultural, artistic, recreational, and corporate promotional events. It also designs, produces, and sells various sketches, graphics, and other marketing materials, such as photo albums, leaflets, Website aesthetics, packaging, posters, advertisements, books, and magazines. The company serves government authorities, residents' committees, state-owned enterprises, real estate corporations, automobile dealers, crafts companies, artists, and other corporate customers. Orange Tour Cultural Holding Limited was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Wuxi, the People's Republic of China.

Sun Kong Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the sale and transportation of diesel oil and diesel exhaust fluid in Hong Kong. It serves logistics companies. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Yuen Long, Hong Kong. Sun Kong Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Fully Fort Group Limited.

Novacon Technology Group Limited, an investment holding company, develops and provides financial trading solutions in Hong Kong, Indonesia, Malaysia, Australia, Japan, Cyprus, and internationally. Its financial trading solutions enables trading of OTC-traded financial instruments, stock exchange-traded financial instruments, and fund management. The company also provides licensing and maintenance services; initial set up and customization services; and system protection and hosting services, as well as sells computer hardware and software. In addition, it is involved in the development and supply of resource allocation, planning, scheduling, and management of software and services. It serves financial institutions, including brokerage firms and wealth management companies. Novacon Technology Group Limited was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong.

Ying Hai Group Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, operates as a wholesale licensed travel agent that focuses on the provision of business-to-business domestic travel services to other travel agents. It is involved in the sales and distribution of air tickets and hotel rooms; provision of vehicle leasing and limousine services; and sales and provision of ancillary travel-related products and services, such as entertainment tickets, buffet tickets, transportation tickets, travel insurance, and visa applications. The company was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Macau. Ying Hai Group Holdings Company Limited is a subsidiary of Silver Esteem Limited.
longName: Ying Hai Group Holdings Company Limited

longBusinessSummary: Alibaba Group Holding Limited, through its subsidiaries, provides online and mobile commerce businesses in the People's Republic of China and internationally. It operates in four segments: Core Commerce, Cloud Computing, Digital Media and Entertainment, and Innovation Initiatives and Others. The company operates Taobao Marketplace, a mobile commerce destination; Tmall, a third-party platform; Alibaba Health pharmaceutical e-commerce and consumer healthcare platforms; Alimama, a monetization platform; 1688.com, an online wholesale marketplace; Alibaba.com, an online wholesale marketplace; AliExpress, a retail marketplace; Lazada, an e-commerce platform; and Tmall Global, an import e-commerce platform. It also operates Lingshoutong, a digital sourcing platform; Cainiao Network logistic services platform; Ele.me, a delivery and local services platform; Koubei, a restaurant and local services guide platform; and Fliggy, an online travel platform. In addition, the company offers pay-for-performance and display marketing services; and Taobao Ad Network and Exchange, a real-time bidding online marketing exchange. Further, it provides elastic computing, database, storage, virtualization network, large scale computing, security, and management and application, big data analytics, machine learning platform, and Internet of Things and other services for enterprises; and payment and escrow services; and movies, television series, variety shows, animations, and other video content. Additionally, the company operates Youku, an online video platform; UC Browser, a mobile browser; Alibaba Pictures and other content platforms that provide online videos, films, live events, news feeds, literature, music, and others; Amap, a mobile digital map, navigation, and real-time traffic information app; DingTalk, a business efficiency app; and Tmall Genie, an AI-powered smart speaker. The company was founded in 1999 and is based in Hangzhou, the People's Republic of China.
